        <h1><span style='font-family:宋体'>城南旧事</span></h1>

        <p class=MsoNormal><span lang=EN-US><img border=0 width=113 height=150 id="图片 4" src="书籍素材.files/image004.jpg"
                    alt="http://www.99lib.net/book/cover.pic/cover_1433.jpg"></span></p>

        <h2><span style='font-family:宋体'>惠安馆传奇</span></h2>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#171414'>一</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#171414'>太阳从大玻璃窗透进来，照到大白纸糊的墙上，照到三屉桌上，照到我的小床上来了。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#171414'>我醒了，还躺在床上，看那道太阳光里飞舞着的许多小小的、小小的尘埃。宋妈过来掸窗台，掸桌子，随着鸡毛掸子的舞动，那道阳光里的尘埃加多了，飞舞得更热闹了，我赶忙拉起被来蒙住脸，是怕尘埃把我呛得咳嗽。</span>
        </p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#171414'>宋妈的鸡毛掸子轮到来掸我的小床了，小床上的棱棱角角她都掸到了，掸子把儿碰在床栏上，咯咯地响，我想骂她，但她倒先说话了：</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>还没睡够哪！</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>说着，她把我的被大掀开来，我穿着绒褂裤的身体整个露在被外，立刻就打了两个喷嚏。她强迫我起来，给我穿衣服。印花斜纹布的棉袄棉裤，都是新做的；棉裤筒多可笑，可以直立放在那里，就知道那棉花够多厚了。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#171414'>妈正坐在炉子边梳头，倾着身子，一大把头发从后脖子顺过来，她就用篦子篦呀篦呀的，炉子上是一瓶玫瑰色的发油，天气冷，油凝住了，总要放在炉子上化一化才能搽。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#171414'>窗外很明亮，干秃的树枝上落着几只不怕冷的小鸟。我在想，什么时候那树上才能长满叶子呢？这是我们在北京过的第一个冬天。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#171414'>妈妈还说不好北京话，她正在告诉宋妈，今天买什么菜。妈不会说</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#171414'>买一斤猪肉，不要太肥。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#171414'>她说：</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#171414'>买一斤租漏，不要太回。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#171414'>宋妈梳完了头，用她的油手抹在我的头发上，也给我梳了两条辫子。我看宋妈提着篮子要出去了，连忙喊住她：</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>宋妈，我跟你去买菜。</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#171414'>宋妈说：</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:
"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#171414'>你不怕惠难馆的疯子？</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#171414'>宋妈是顺义县的人，她也说不好北京话，她说成</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#171414'>惠难馆</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#171414'>，妈说成</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#171414'>灰娃馆</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#171414'>，爸说成</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#171414'>飞安馆</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#171414'>，我随着胡同里的孩子说</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#171414'>惠安馆</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#171414'>，到底哪一个对，我不知道。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#171414'>我为什么要怕惠安馆的疯子？她昨天还冲我笑呢！她那一笑真有意思，要不是妈紧紧拉着我的手，我就会走过去看她，跟她说话了。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#171414'>惠安馆在我们这条胡同的最前一家，三层石台阶上去，就是两扇大黑门凹进去，门上横着一块匾，路过的时候爸爸教我念过：</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#171414'>飞安会馆</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#171414'>。爸说里面住的都是从</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#171414'>飞安</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#171414'>那个地方来的学生，像叔叔一样，在大学里念书。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>也在北京大学？</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>我问爸爸。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>北京的大学多着呢，还有清华大学呀！燕京大学呀！</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>可以不可以到飞安</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>——</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>不，惠安馆里找叔叔们玩一玩？</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>做晤得！做晤得！</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>我知道，我无论要求什么事，爸终归要拿这句客家话来拒绝我。我想总有一天我要迈上那三层台阶，走进那黑洞洞的大门里去的。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#171414'>惠安馆的疯子我看见好几次了，每一次只要她站在门口，宋妈或者妈就赶快捏紧我的手，轻轻说：</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#171414'>疯子！</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#171414'>我们便擦着墙边走过去，我如果要回头再张望一</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'> </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#171414'>下，她们就用力拉我的胳臂制止我。其实那疯子还不就是一个梳着油松大辫子的大姑娘，像张家李家的大姑娘一样！她总是倚着门墙站着，看来来往往过路的人。</span>
        </p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#171414'>是昨天，我跟着妈妈到骡马市的佛照楼去买东西，妈是去买搽脸的鸭蛋粉，我呢，就是爱吃那里的八珍梅。我们从骡马市大街回来，穿过魏染胡同，西草厂，</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'> </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#171414'>到了椿树胡同的井窝子，井窝子斜对面就是我们住的这条胡同。刚一进胡同，我就看见惠安馆的疯子了，她穿了一身绛紫色的棉袄，黑绒的毛窝，头上留着一排刘海</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'> </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#171414'>儿，辫子上扎的是大红绒绳，她正把大辫子甩到前面来，两手玩弄着辫梢，愣愣地看着对面人家院子里的那棵老洋槐。干树枝子上有几只乌鸦，胡同里没什么人。</span>
        </p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#171414'>妈正低头嘴里念叨着，准是在算她今天一共买了多少钱的东西，好跟无事不操心的爸爸报账，所以妈没留神已经走到了</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#171414'>灰娃馆</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#171414'>。我跟在妈的后面，一直看</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'> </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#171414'>疯子，竟忘了走路。这时疯子的眼光从洋槐上落下来，正好看到我，她眼珠不动地盯着我，好像要在我的脸上找什么。她的脸白得发青，鼻子尖有点红，大概是冷风</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'> </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#171414'>吹冻的，尖尖的下巴，两片薄嘴唇紧紧地闭着。忽然她的嘴唇动了，眼睛也眨了两下，带着笑，好像要说话，弄着辫梢的手也向我伸出来，招我过去呢。不知怎么，</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'> </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#171414'>我浑身大大地打了一个寒战，跟着，我就随着她的招手和笑意要向她走去。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>——</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#171414'>可是妈回过头来了，突然把我一拉：</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>怎么啦，你？</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>嗯？</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>我有点迷糊。妈看了疯子一眼，说：</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>为什么打哆嗦？是不是怕</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>——</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>是不是要溺尿？快回家！</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>我的手被妈使劲拖拉着。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#171414'>回到家来，我心里还惦念着疯子的那副模样儿。她的笑不是很有意思吗？如果我跟她说话</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>——</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#171414'>我说：</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#171414'>嗯！</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#171414'>她会怎么样呢？我愣愣地想着，懒得吃晚饭，实在也是八珍梅吃多了。但是晚饭后，妈对宋妈说：</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>英子一定吓着了。</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>然后给我沏了碗白糖水，叫我喝下去，并且命令我钻被窝睡觉。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>……</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#171414'>这时，我的辫子梳好了，追了宋妈去买菜，她在前面走，我在后面跟着。她的那条恶心的大黑棉裤，那么厚，那么肥，裤脚绑着。别人告诉妈说，北京的老妈</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'> </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#171414'>子很会偷东西，她们偷了米就一把一把顺着裤腰装进裤兜子，刚好落到绑着的裤脚管里，不会漏出来。我在想，宋妈的肥裤脚里，不知道有没有我家的白米？</span>
        </p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#171414'>经过惠安馆，我向里面看了一下，黑门大开着，门道里有一个煤球炉子，那疯子的妈妈和爸爸正在炉边煮什么。大家都管疯子的爸爸叫</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#171414'>长班老王</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#171414'>，长班就</span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'> </span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>是给会馆看门的，他们住在最临街的一间屋子。宋妈虽然不许我看疯子，但是我知道她自己也很爱看疯子，打听疯子的事，只是不许我听我看就是了。宋妈这时也向</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'> </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#171414'>惠安馆里看，正好疯子的妈妈抬起头来，她和宋妈两人同时说</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#171414'>吃了吗？您！</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#171414'>爸爸说北京人一天到晚闲着没有事，不管什么时候见面都要问吃了没有。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#171414'>出了胡同口往南走几步，就是井窝子，这里满地是水，有的地方结成薄薄的冰，独轮水车来一辆去一辆，他们扭着屁股推车，车子吱吱扭扭地响，好刺耳，我</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'> </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#171414'>要堵起耳朵啦！井窝子有两个人在向深井里打水，水打上来倒在一个好大的水槽里，推水的人就在大水槽里接了水再送到各家去。井窝子旁住着一个我的朋友</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>——</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#171414'>和</span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'> </span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>我一般高的妞儿。我这时停在井窝子旁边不走了，对宋妈说：</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>宋妈，你去买菜，我等妞儿。</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#171414'>妞儿，我第一次是在油盐店里看见她的。那天她两只手端了两个碗，拿了一大枚，又买酱，又买醋，又买葱，伙计还逗着说：</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#171414'>妞儿，唱一段才许你走！</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#171414'>妞儿眼里含着泪，手摇晃着，醋都要洒了，我有说不出的气恼，一下窜到妞儿身旁，插着腰问他们：</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>凭什么？</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#171414'>就这样，我认识了妞儿。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#171414'>妞儿只有一条辫子，又黄又短，像妈在土地庙给我买的小狗的尾巴。第二次看见妞儿，是我在井窝子旁边看打水。她过来了，一声不响地站在我身边，我们俩相对着笑了笑，不知道说什么好。等一会儿，我就忍不住去摸她那条小黄辫子了，她又向我笑了笑，指着后面，低低的声音说：</span>
        </p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>你就住在那条胡同里？</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>嗯。</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>我说。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>第几个门？</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#171414'>我伸出手指头来算了算：</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>一，二，三，四，第四个门。到我们家去玩。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#171414'>她摇摇头说：</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>你们胡同里有疯子，妈不叫我去。</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>怕什么，她又不吃人。</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#171414'>她仍然是笑笑地摇摇头。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#171414'>妞儿一笑，眼底下鼻子两边的肉就会有两个小漩涡，很好看，可是宋妈竟跟油盐店的掌柜说：</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>这孩子长得俊倒是俊，就是有点薄，眼睛太透亮了，老像水汪着，你看，眼底下有两个泪坑儿。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#171414'>我心里可是有说不出的喜欢她，喜欢她那么温和，不像我一急宋妈就骂我的：</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#171414'>又跳？又跳？小暴雷。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#171414'>那天她跟我在井窝子边站了一会儿，就小声地说：</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#171414'>我要回去了，我爹等着我吊嗓子。赶明儿见！</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#171414'>我在井窝子旁跟妞儿见过几次面了，只要看见红棉袄裤从那边闪过来，我就满心的高兴，可是今天，等了好久都不见她出来，很失望，我的绒褂子口袋里还藏着一小包八珍梅，要给妞儿吃的。我摸摸，发热了，包的纸都破烂了，黏糊糊的，宋妈洗衣服时，我还得挨她一顿骂。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#171414'>我觉得很没意思，往回家走，我本来想今天见妞儿的话，就告诉她一个好主意，从横胡同穿过到我家，就用不着经过惠安馆，不用怕看见疯子了。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#171414'>我低头这么想着，走到惠安馆门口了。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>嘿！</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#171414'>吓了我一跳！正是疯子。咬着下嘴唇，笑着看我。她的眼睛里透亮，一笑眼底下</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>——</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#171414'>就像宋妈</span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'> </span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>说的，怎么也有两个泪坑儿呀！我想看清楚她，我是多么久以前就想看清楚她的。我不由得对着她的眼神走上了台阶。太阳照在她的脸上，常常是苍白的颜色，今天</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'> </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#171414'>透着亮光了。揣在短棉袄里的手伸出来拉住我的手，那么暖，那么软。我这时看看胡同里，没有一个人走过。真奇怪，我现在怕的不是疯子，倒是怕人家看见我跟疯</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'> </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#171414'>子拉手了。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>几岁了？</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>她问我。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>嗯</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>——</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>六岁。</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>六岁！</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>她很惊奇地叫了一声，低下头来，忽然撩起我的辫子看我的脖子，在找什么。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#171414'>不是。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#171414'>她喃喃地自己说话，接着又问我：</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>看见我们小桂子没有？</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>小桂子？</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>我不懂她在说什么。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#171414'>这时大门里疯子的妈妈出来了，皱着眉头怪着急地说：</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>秀贞，可别把人家小姑娘吓着呀！</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#171414'>又转过脸来对我说：</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>别听她的，胡说呢！回去吧！等回头你妈不放心。嗯</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>——</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#171414'>听见没有？</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#171414'>她说着，用手扬了扬，叫我回去。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#171414'>我抬头看着疯子，知道她的名字叫秀贞了。她拉着我的手，轻摇着，并不放开我。她的笑，增加了我的勇气，我对老的说：</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>不！</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>小南蛮子儿！</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>秀贞的妈妈也笑了，轻轻地指点着我的脑门儿，这准是一句骂我的话，就像爸爸常用看不起的口气对妈说</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#171414'>他们这些北仔鬼</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#171414'>是一样的吧！</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>在这儿玩不要紧，你家来了人找，可别赖是我们姑娘招的你。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>我不说的啦！</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>何必这么嘱咐我？什么该说，什么不该说，我都知道。妈妈打了一只金镯子，藏在她的小首饰箱里，我从来不会告诉爸爸。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>来！</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>秀贞拉着我往里走，我以为要到里面那一层一层很深的院子里去找上大学的叔叔们玩呢，原来她把我带进了他们住的门房。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#171414'>屋里可不像我家里那么亮，玻璃窗小得很，临窗一个大炕，中间摆了一张矮炕桌，上面堆着活计和针线盒子。秀贞从桌上拿起了一件没做完的衣服，朝我身上左比右比，然后高兴地对走进来的她的妈妈说：</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>妈，您瞧，我怎么说的，刚合适！那么就开领子吧。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#171414'>说着，她又找了一根绳子，绕着我的脖子量，我由她摆布，只管看墙上的那张画，画儿是一个白胖大娃娃，没有穿衣服，手里捧着大元宝，骑在一条大大的红鱼上。</span>
        </p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#171414'>秀贞转到我的面前来，看我仰着头，她也随着我的眼光看那张画，满是那么回事地说：</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>要看炕上看去，看我们小桂子多胖，那阵儿才八个月，骑着大金鱼，满屋里转，玩得饭都不吃，就这么淘</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>……”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>行啦行啦！不</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>——</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>害</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>——</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>臊！</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>秀贞正说得高兴，我也听得糊里糊涂，长班老王进来了，不耐烦地瞪了秀贞一眼说她。秀贞不理会她爸爸，推着我脱鞋上炕，凑近在画下面，还是只管说：</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>饭不吃，衣服也不穿，就往外跑，老是急着找她爹去，我说了多少回都不听，我说等我给多做几件衣服穿上再去呀！今年的衬褂倒是先做好了，背心就差缝</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'> </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#171414'>钮子了。这件棉袄开了领子马上就好。可急的是什么呀！真叫人纳闷儿，到底是怎么档子事儿</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>……”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#171414'>她说着说着不说了，低着头在想那纳闷儿的事，一直发愣。我</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'> </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#171414'>想，她是在和我玩</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#171414'>过家家儿</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#171414'>吧？她妈不是说她胡说吗？要是过家家儿，我倒是有一套玩意儿，小手表、小算盘、小铃铛，都可以拿来一起玩。所以我就说：</span>
        </p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>没关系，我把手表送给小桂子，她有了表就有一定时候回家了。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#171414'>可是，</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>——</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#171414'>这时我倒想起妈会派宋妈来找我，就又说</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#171414'>我也要回家了。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#171414'>秀贞听我说要走，她也不发愣了，一面随着我下了炕，一面说：</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#171414'>那敢情好，先谢谢你啦！看见小桂子叫她回来，外头冷，就说我不骂她，不用怕。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#171414'>我点了点头，答应她，真像有那么一个小桂子，我认识的。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#171414'>我一边走着一边想，跟秀贞这样玩儿，真有意思；假装有一个小桂子，还给小桂子做衣服。为什么人家都不许他们的小孩子跟秀贞玩儿呢？还管她叫疯子？我想着就回头去看，原来秀贞还倚着墙看我呢！我一高兴就连跑带跳地回家来。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#171414'>宋妈正在跟一个老婆子换洋火，房檐底下堆着字纸篓、旧皮鞋、空瓶子。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#171414'>我进了屋子就到小床前的柜里找出手表来。小小圆圆的金表，镶着几粒亮亮的钻石，上面的针已经不能走动了，妈妈说要修理，可一直放着，我很喜欢这手表，常拿来戴在手上玩，就归了我了。我正站在三屉桌前玩弄着，忽然听见窗外宋妈正和老婆子在说什么，我仔细听，宋妈说：</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>后来呢？</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>后来呀，</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>换洋火的老婆子说，</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>那学生一去到如今晚儿就没回来！临走的时候许下的，回到他老家卖田卖地，过一个月就回来明媒正娶她。好嘛！这一等就是六年啦！多傻的姑娘，我眼瞧着她疯的。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>……”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>说是怎么着？还生了个孩子？</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>是呀！那学生走的时候，姑娘她妈还不知道姑娘有了，等到现形了，这才赶着送回海甸义地去生的。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>义地？</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>就是他们惠安义地，惠安人在北京死了就埋在他们惠安义地里。原来王家是给义地看坟的，打姑娘的爷爷就看起，后来才又让姑娘她爹来这儿当长班，谁知道出了这么档子事儿。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>他们这家子倒是跟惠难有缘，惠难离咱们这儿多远哪？怎么就一去不回头了呢？</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>可远喽！</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>那么生下来的孩子呢？</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>孩子呀，一落地就裹包裹包，趁着天没亮，送到齐化门城根底下啦！反正不是让野狗吃了，就是让人捡去了！</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>姑娘打这儿就疯啦？</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>可不，打这儿就疯了！可怜她爹妈，这辈子就生下这么个姑娘，唉！</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#171414'>两个人说到这儿都不言语了，我这时已经站到屋门口倾听。宋妈正数着几包丹凤牌的红头洋火，老婆子把破烂纸往她的大筐里塞呀塞呀！鼻子里吸溜着清鼻涕。宋妈又说：</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>下回给带点刨花来。那</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>——</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>你跟疯子她们是一地儿的人呀？</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>老亲喽！我大妈娘家二舅屋里的三姐算是疯子她二妈，现在还在看坟，他们说的还有错儿吗？</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#171414'>宋妈一眼看见了我，说：</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>又听事儿，你。</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>我知道你们说谁。</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>我说。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>说谁？</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>小桂子她妈。</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>小桂子她妈？</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>宋妈哈哈大笑，</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>你也疯啦？哪儿来的小桂子她妈呀？</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#171414'>我也哈哈笑了，我知道谁是小桂子她妈呀！</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#171414'>二</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#171414'>天气暖和多了，棉袄早就脱下来，夹袄外面早晚凉就罩上一件薄薄的棉背心，又轻又软。我穿的新布鞋，前头打了一块黑皮子头，老王妈</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>——</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#171414'>秀贞她妈，看见我的新鞋说：</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>这双鞋可结实呦</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>——</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>把我们家的门槛儿踢烂了，你这双鞋也破不了！</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#171414'>惠安馆我已经来熟了，会馆的大门总是开着一扇，所以我随时可以溜进来。我说溜进来，因为我总是背着家里的人偷着来的，他们只知道我常常是随着宋妈买菜到井窝子找妞儿，一见宋妈进了油盐店，我就回头走，到惠安馆来。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#171414'>我今天进了惠安馆，秀贞不在屋里。炕桌上摆着一个大玻璃缸，里面是几条小金鱼，游来游去。我问王妈：</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>秀贞呢？</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>跨院里呢！</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>我去找她。</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>我说。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>别介，她就来，你这儿等着，看金鱼吧！</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#171414'>我把鼻子顶着金鱼缸向里看，金鱼一边游一边嘴巴一张一张地在喝水，我的嘴也不由得一张一张地在学鱼喝水。有时候金鱼游到我的面前来，隔着一层玻璃，我和鱼鼻子顶牛儿啦！我就这么看着，两腿跪在炕沿上，都麻了，秀贞还不来。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#171414'>我翻腿坐在炕沿上，又等了一会，还不见秀贞来，我急了，溜出了屋子，往跨院里去找她。那跨院，仿佛一直都是关着的，我从来也没见过谁去那里。我轻轻</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'> </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#171414'>推开跨院门进去，小小的院子里有一棵不知道什么树，已经长了小小的绿叶子了。院角地上是干枯的落叶，有的烂了。秀贞大概正在打扫，但是我进去时看见她一手</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'> </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#171414'>拿着扫帚倚在树干上，一手掀起了衣襟在擦眼睛，我悄悄走到她跟前，抬头看着她。她也许看见我了，但是没理会我，忽然背转身子去，伏着树干哭起来了，她说：</span>
        </p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>小桂子，小桂子，你怎么不要妈了呢？</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#171414'>那声音多么委屈，多么可怜啊！她又哭着说：</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>我不带你，你怎么认得道儿，远着呢！</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#171414'>我想起妈妈说过，我们是从很远很远的家乡来的，那里是个岛，四面都是水，我们坐了大轮船，又坐大火车，才到这个北京来。我曾问妈妈什么时候回去，妈</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'> </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#171414'>说早着呢，来一趟不容易，多住几年。那么秀贞所说的那个远地方，是像我们的岛那么远吗？小桂子怎么能一个人跑了去？我替秀贞难过，也想念我并不认识的小桂</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'> </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#171414'>子，我的眼泪掉下来了。在模模糊糊的泪光里，我仿佛看见那骑着大金鱼的胖娃娃，是什么也没穿啊！</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#171414'>我含着眼泪，大大地倒抽了一口气，为的不让我自己哭出来，我揪揪秀贞裤腿叫她：</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>秀贞！秀贞！</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#171414'>她停止了哭声，满脸泪蹲下来，搂着我，把头埋在我的前胸擦来擦去，用我的绵绵软软的背心，擦干了她的泪，然后她仰起头来看看我笑了，我伸出手去调顺她的揉乱的刘海儿，不由得说：</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>我喜欢你，秀贞。</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#171414'>秀贞没有说什么，吸溜着鼻涕站起来。天气暖和了，她也不穿绑腿棉裤了，现在穿的是一条肥肥的散腿裤。她的腿很瘦吗？怎么风一吹那裤子，显得那么晃荡。她浑身都瘦，刚才蹲下来伏在我的胸前时，我看那块后脊背，平板儿似的。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#171414'>秀贞拉着我的手说：</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>屋里去，帮着拾掇拾掇。</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#171414'>小跨院里只有这么两间小房，门一推吱扭扭的一串尖响，那声音不好听，好像有一根刺扎在人心上。从太阳地里走进这阴暗的屋里来，怪凉的。外屋里，整整</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'> </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#171414'>齐齐地摆着书桌、椅子、书架，上面满是灰土，我心想，应该叫我们宋妈来给掸掸，准保扬起满屋子的灰。爸爸常常对妈说，为什么宋妈不用湿布擦，这样大掸一</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'> </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#171414'>阵，等一会儿，灰尘不是又落回原来的地方了吗？但是妈妈总请爸爸不要多嘴，她说这是北京规矩。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#171414'>走进里屋去，房间更小一点，只摆了一张床，一个茶几。床上有一口皮箱，秀贞把箱子打开来，从里面拿出一件大棉袍，我爸爸也有，是男人的。秀贞把大棉袍抱在胸前，自言自语地说：</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>该翻翻添点棉花了。</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#171414'>她把大棉袍抱出院子去晒，我也跟了去。她进来，我也跟进来。她叫我和她把箱子抬到院子太阳底下晒，里面只有一双手套，一顶呢帽和几件旧内衣。她很仔细地把这几件零碎衣物摊开来，并且拿起一件条子花纹的褂子对我说：</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>我瞧这件褂子只能给小桂子做夹袄里子了。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>可不是。</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>我翻开了我的夹袄里给秀贞看：</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#171414'>这也是用我爸爸的旧衣服改的。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>你也是用你爸爸的？你怎么知道这衣服就是小桂子她爹的？</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#171414'>秀贞微笑着瞪眼问我，她那样子很高兴，她高兴我就高兴，可是我怎么会知道这是小桂子她爹的？她问得我答不出，我斜着头笑了，她逗着我的下巴还是问：</span>
        </p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>说呀！</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#171414'>我们俩这时是蹲在箱子旁，我很清爽地看着她的脸，刘海儿被风吹倒在一边，她好像一个什么人，我却想不出。我回答她说：</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>我猜的。那么</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>——”</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>我又低声地问她，</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>我管小桂子她爹叫什么呀？</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>叫叔叔呀！</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>我已经有叔叔了。</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>叔叔还嫌多？叫他思康叔叔好了，他排行第三，叫他三叔也行。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>思康三叔。</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>我嘴里念着，</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>他几点钟回家？</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>他呀，</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>秀贞忽然站起来，紧皱着眉毛斜起头在想，想了好一会儿才说：</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#171414'>快了。走了有个把月了。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#171414'>说着她又走进屋，我再跟进去，弄这弄那，又跟出来，搬这搬那，这样跟出跟进忙得好高兴。秀贞的脸这时粉嘟嘟的了，鼻头两边也抹了灰土，鼻子尖和嘴唇上边渗着小小的汗珠，这样的脸看起来真好看。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#171414'>秀贞用袖子抹着她鼻子上的汗，对我说：</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>英子，给我打盆水来会不会？屋里要擦擦。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#171414'>我连忙说：</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>会，会。</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#171414'>跨院的房子原和门房是在一溜沿的，跨院多了一个门就是了，水缸和盆就放在门房的房檐下。我掀开水缸的盖子，一勺勺地往脸盆里舀水，听见屋里有人和秀贞的妈说话：</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>姑娘这程子可好点了吗？</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>唉！别提了，这程子又闹了，年年开了春就得闹些日子，这两天就是哭一阵子笑一阵子的，可怎么好！真是</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>……”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>这路毛病就是春天犯得凶。</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#171414'>我端了一盆水，连晃连洒，泼了我自己一身水，到了跨院屋里，也就剩不多了。把盆放在椅子上，忽然不知哪儿飘来炒菜香，我闻着这味儿想起了一件事，便对秀贞说：</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>我要回家了。</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#171414'>秀贞没听见，只管在抽屉里翻东西。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#171414'>我是想起回家吃完饭还要到横胡同去等妞儿，昨天约会好了的。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#171414'>又凉又湿的裤子，贴在我的腿上，一进门妈妈就骂了：</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>就在井窝子玩一上午？我还以为你掉到井里去了呢？看弄这么一身水！</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#171414'>妈一边给我换衣服，一边又说：</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#171414'>打听打听北京哪个小学好，也该送进学堂了，听说厂甸那个师大附小还不错。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#171414'>妈这么说着，我才看见原来爸爸也已经回来了，我弄了一身水，怕爸爸要打骂我，他厉害得很，我缩头看着爸爸，准备被挨打的姿势，还好他没注意，抽着烟卷儿在看报，漫应着说：</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>还早呢，急什么。</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>不送进学堂，她满街跑，我看不住她。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>不听话就打！</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>爸的口气好像很凶，但是随后却转过脸来向我笑笑，原来是吓唬我呢！他又说：</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#171414'>英子上学的事，等她叔叔来再对他说，由他去管吧！</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#171414'>吃完饭我到横胡同去接了妞儿来，天气不冷了，我和妞儿到空闲着的西厢房里玩，那里堆着拆下来的炉子、烟筒，不用的桌椅和床铺。一只破藤箱子里，养了</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'> </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#171414'>最近买的几只刚孵出来的小油鸡，那柔软的小黄绒毛太好玩了，我和妞儿蹲着玩弄箱里的几只小油鸡。看小鸡啄米吃，总是吃，总是吃，怎么不停啊！</span>
        </p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#171414'>小鸡吃不够，我们可是看够了，盖上藤箱，我们站起来玩别的。拿两个制钱穿在一根细绳子上，手提着，我们玩踢制钱，每一踢，两个制钱打在鞋帮上</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#171414'>嗒嗒</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#171414'>地响。妞儿踢时腰一扭一扭的，显得那么娇。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#171414'>这一下午玩得好快乐，如果不是妞儿又到了她吊嗓子的时候，我们不知道要玩到多么久。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#171414'>爸爸今天买来了新的笔和墨，还有一叠红描字纸。晚上，在煤油灯底下，他教我描红模字，先念那上面的字：</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#171414'>一去二三里，烟村四五家，亭台六七座，八九十枝花。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#171414'>爸爸说：</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>你一天要描一张，暑假以后进小学，才考得上。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#171414'>早上我去惠安馆找秀贞，下午妞儿到西厢房里来找我，晚上描红字，我这些日子就这么过的。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#171414'>小油鸡的黄毛上长出短短的翅膀来了，我和妞儿喂米喂水又喂菜，宋妈说不要把小鸡肚子撑坏了，也怕被野猫给叼了去，就用一块大石头压住藤箱盖子，不许我们随便掀开。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#171414'>妞儿和我玩的时候，嘴里常常哼哼唧唧的，那天一高兴，她竟扭起来了，她扭呀扭呀比来比去，嘴里唱着：</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“……</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#171414'>开哀开门嗯嗯儿，碰见张秀才哀哀</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>……”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>你唱什么？这就是吊嗓子吗？</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#171414'>我问</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>我唱的是打花鼓。</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>妞儿说。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#171414'>她的兴致很好，只管轻轻地唱下去，扭下去，我在一旁看傻了。她忽然对我说：</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#171414'>来！跟我学，我教你。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>我也会唱一种歌。</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>不知怎么，我想我也应当露一露我的本事，一下子想起了爸爸有一回和客人谈天数唱的一首歌，后来爸曾教了我，妈还说爸爸教我这种歌真是没大没小呢！</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>那你唱，那你唱。</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>妞儿推着我，我却又不好意思唱了，她一定要我唱，我只好结结巴巴地用客家话念唱起来：</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>你听着</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>——</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>想来么事想心肝，紧想心肝紧不安！我想心肝心肝想，正是心肝想心肝</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>……”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#171414'>我还没数完呢，妞儿已经笑得挤出了眼泪，我也笑起来了，那几句词儿可真是拗嘴。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>谁教你的？什么心肝想心肝，心想心肝想的，哈哈哈！你唱的这是哪国的歌儿呀！</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#171414'>我们俩搂在一堆笑，一边瞎说着心肝心肝的，也闹不清是什么意思。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#171414'>我们真快乐，胡说胡唱胡玩，西厢房是我们的快乐窝，我连做梦都想着它。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#171414'>妞儿每次也是玩得够不够的才看看窗外，忽然叫道：</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#171414'>可得回去了！</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#171414'>说完她就跑，急得连</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#171414'>再见</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#171414'>都来不及说。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#171414'>忽然一连几天，横胡同里接不到妞儿了，我是多么的失望，站在那里等了又等。我慢慢走向井窝子去，希望碰见她，可是没有用。下午的井窝子没那么热闹了，因为送水的车子都是上午来，这时只有附近人家自己推了装着铅桶的小车子来买井水。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#171414'>我看见长班老王也推了小车子来，他一趟一趟来好几趟了，见我一直站在那里，奇怪地问我：</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>小英子，你在这儿发什么傻？</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#171414'>我没有说什么，我自己心里的事，自己知道。我说：</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>秀贞呢？</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>我想如果等不到妞儿，就去找秀贞，跨院里收拾得好干净了。但是老王没理我，他装满了两桶水，就推走了。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#171414'>我正在犹豫着怎么办的时候，忽然从西草厂口上，转过来一个熟悉的影子，那正是妞儿，我多高兴！我跑着迎上去，喊她：</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#171414'>妞儿！妞儿！</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#171414'>她竟不理我，就</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'> </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#171414'>像不认识我，也像没听见有人叫她。我很奇怪，跟在她身边走，但她用手轻轻赶开我，皱着眉头眨眼，意思叫我走开。我不知道是怎么回事，但见她身后几步远有一</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'> </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#171414'>个高大的男人，穿着蓝布大褂，手提着一个脏了的长布口袋，袋口上露出来我看见是一把胡琴。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#171414'>我想这一定是妞儿的爸爸。妞儿常说</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>我怕我爹打</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>、</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>我怕我爹骂</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>的话，我现在看那样子就知道，我不跟妞儿再说话了，就转身走回家，心里好难受。我</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'> </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#171414'>口袋里有一块滑石，可以在砖上写出白字来，我掏出来，就不由得顺着人家的墙上一直画下去，画到我家的墙上。心里想着如果没有妞儿一起玩，是多么没有意思</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'> </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#171414'>呢！</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#171414'>我刚要叫门，忽然听见横胡同里咚咚咚有人跑步声，原来是妞儿气喘着跑来了，她匆匆忙忙神色不安地说：</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#171414'>我明儿再来找你。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#171414'>没等我回答，她就又跑回横胡同了。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#171414'>第二天早晨，妞儿来找我，我们在西厢房里，蹲下来看小油鸡。掀开藤箱盖子，我们俩都把手伸进去摸小油鸡的羽毛，这样摸着摸着，谁也没说话。我本来是</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'> </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#171414'>要说话的，但是没有出声，只是心里在问她：</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#171414'>妞儿，为什么好多天没来找我？</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#171414'>妞儿，是你爸爸很厉害不许你来吗？</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#171414'>妞儿，昨天为什么不许我跟你说话？</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>” “</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#171414'>妞儿，你一定有什么难受的事吧？</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#171414'>真奇怪，这些话都是我心里想的，并没有说出口，可是她怎么知道的，竟用眼泪来回答我？她不说话，也不用袖子去抹眼，就</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'> </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#171414'>让眼泪滴答滴答落在藤箱里，都被小油鸡和着小米吃下去了！</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#171414'>我不知怎么办好了，从侧面正看见她的耳朵，耳垂上扎了洞用一根红线穿过去，妞儿的耳朵没有洗干净，边沿上有一道黑泥。我再顺着她的肩膀向下看，手腕</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'> </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#171414'>上有一条青色的伤痕，我伸手去撩起她的袖口看，她这才惊醒了，吓得一躲闪，随着就转过头来向我难过地笑笑。早晨的太阳，正照到西厢房里，照到她的不太干净</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'> </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#171414'>的脸上，又湿又长的睫毛，一闪动，眼泪就流过泪坑淌到嘴边了。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#171414'>忽然，她站起来，撩开袖口，撩起裤角，轻轻地说：</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>看我爸爸打的！</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#171414'>我是蹲着的，伸出手正好摸到她腿上那一条条肿起的伤痕。我轻轻地摸，倒惹得她哭出声音来了。她因为不敢放声，嘤嘤地小声哭，真是可怜。我说：</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>你爸爸干吗打你？</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#171414'>她当时说不出话来，哭了好一会儿才说：</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>他不许我出来玩。</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>是因为在我家待太久了？</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#171414'>妞儿点点头。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#171414'>因为在我家玩久了，害得她挨打，我又难过，又害怕，想到那个高大的男人，我不由得说：</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>那么你快回去吧！</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>她站着不动，说：</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>他一早出去还没回来。</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>那么你妈呢？</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>我妈也拧我，她倒不管我出来的事。爸爸也打她。打了她，她就拧我，说是我害的。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#171414'>妞儿哭了一阵子好些了，又跟我说这说那的，我说我从来没见过她的妈妈，妞儿说她的妈妈有点跛，一天到晚就是坐在炕头上给人缝补衣服赚钱。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#171414'>我告诉妞儿，我们从前不住在北京，是从一个很远的岛上来的，她也说：</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>我们从前也不住在这儿，我们住在齐化门那边。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>齐化门？</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>我点点头说，</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>我知道那地方。</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>你怎么会也知道齐化门呢？</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#171414'>妞儿奇怪地问我。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#171414'>我想不出我是怎么知道的，但我的确知道，好像有什么人大清早曾带我去过那里，而且我也像看见了那里的样子似的，不，不，不是，我所看见的很模糊，也许那是一个梦吧？因此我就回答妞儿说：</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>我梦见过那个地方，有没有城墙？有一天，有一个女人抱着一个包袱，大清早上，偷偷地向城墙走去</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>……”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>你是讲故事吧？</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>也许是故事。</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>我斜着头又深深地想了想，</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#171414'>反正我知道齐化门就是了。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#171414'>妞儿笑了笑，手伸过来搂着我的脖子，我的手也伸过去搂住她的。但当我捏住她的肩头，她轻喊了一声：</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#171414'>痛！痛！</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#171414'>我的手连忙松开，她又皱着眉说：</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>连这儿都给我抽肿了！</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>什么抽的？</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>掸子。</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>停了一下她又说，</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>我爸，还有我妈，他们</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>——”</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>但她顿住不说下去了。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>他们怎么样？</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>不说了，下回再跟你说。</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>我知道，你爸爸教你唱戏，要你赚钱给他们花。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#171414'>这是我听宋妈跟妈妈讲过的，所以一下子就给说出来了。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#171414'>要你赚钱还打你，凭什么！</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#171414'>我说到后来气愤起来了。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>喝喝，你瞧你什么都知道，我不是要跟你说唱戏的事，你哪儿知道我要跟你说什么呀！</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>到底要说什么呢？说嘛！</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>你这么猴急，我就不说了。你要是跟我好，我有好多话要跟你说，就是不许你跟别人说，也别告诉你妈。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>我不会，我们小声地说。</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#171414'>妞儿犹豫了一会儿，伏在我的耳旁小声而急快地说。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>我不是我妈生的，我爸爸也不是亲的。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#171414'>她说得那样快，好像一个闪电过去那么快，跟着就像一声雷打进了我的心，使我的心跳了一大跳。她说完后，把附在我耳旁的手挪开，睁着大眼睛看我，好像在等着看我听了她的话，会怎么个样子。我呢，也只是和她对瞪着眼，一句话也说不出来。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#171414'>我虽然答应妞儿不讲出她的秘密，可是妞儿走了以后，我心里一直在想着这件事，我越想越不放心，忽然跑到妈妈面前，愣愣地问：</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>妈，我是不是你生的？</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>什么？</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>妈奇怪地看了我一眼，</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>怎么想起问这话？</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>你说是不是就好了。</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>是呀，怎么会不是呢？</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>停一下妈又说，</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>要不是亲生的，我能这么疼你吗？像你这样闹，早打扁了你了。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#171414'>我点点头，妈妈的话的确很对，想想妞儿吧！</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#171414'>那么你怎么生的我？</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#171414'>这件事，我早就想问的。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>怎么生的呀，嗯</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>——”</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>妈想了想笑了，胳膊抬起来，指着胳肢窝说：</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>从这里掉出来的。</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#171414'>说完，她就和宋妈大笑起来。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#171414'>三</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#171414'>我手里拿着一个空瓶子和一根竹筷子，轻轻走进惠安馆，推开跨院的门，院里那棵槐树，果然又垂着许多绿虫子，秀贞说是吊死鬼，像秀贞的那几条蚕一样，</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'> </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#171414'>嘴里吐着一条丝，从树上吊下来。我把吊死鬼一条条弄进我的空瓶里，回家去喂鸡吃，每天都可以弄一瓶。那些吊死鬼装在小瓶里，咕噜咕噜地动，真是肉麻，我拿</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'> </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#171414'>着装了吊死鬼的瓶子，胳膊常常觉得痒麻麻的，好像吊死鬼从瓶里爬到我的手上了，其实并没有。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#171414'>我在把一条吊死鬼往瓶里装的时候，忽然想到了妞儿，心里很不安。她昨天又挨揍了，拿了两件衣服偷偷地来找我，进门就说：</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>我要找我亲爹亲妈去！</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>她的脸有一边被打得红肿了。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>他们在哪儿呢？</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>我不知道，到齐化门，再慢慢地找。</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>齐化门在哪儿呢？</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>你不是说你也知道那地方吗？</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>我是说我好像做梦梦见过那地方的。</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#171414'>妞儿把两件衣服塞在西厢房的空箱子里，很有主意地抹干了眼泪，恨恨地说：</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>我非找着我亲爹不可。</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>你知道他长得什么样子吗？</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#171414'>我真佩服她，但觉得这是一件太大太大的事。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>我一天一天地找，就会找到我亲爹跟我亲娘。他们的样子我心里知道。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>那么</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>——”</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>我也不知道要说什么，因为我一点主意也没有。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#171414'>妞儿临走的时候说，她不定哪天就要偷偷地走，但是一定会先来这里跟我说一声，并且带走存在这里的两件衣服。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#171414'>我昨天一直在想妞儿的事，心里很不舒服，晚上就吃不下饭了，妈妈摸摸我的头说：</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>好像有点热，不吃也好，早点去睡。</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#171414'>我上了床，心里还是不舒服，又说不出，就哭起来了，妈妈很奇怪，她说：</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>哭什么？哪儿不舒服？</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>我不知怎么一来竟哭着说：</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>妞儿她爸爸啊</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>……”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>妞儿她爸爸？怎么啦？她爸爸怎么着你啦？</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#171414'>宋妈也过来了，她说：</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>那个不是东西的，准是骂了我们英子了，还是打了你啦？</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>不是！</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>我忽然觉出我是说了什么糊涂话，便撒赖地哭喊：</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#171414'>我要找我爸爸！</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>是要找你爸爸呀！唉！吓人！</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#171414'>宋妈和妈妈都笑了。妈妈说：</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>你爸爸今天去看你叔叔，回来得晚点，你先睡吧！</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#171414'>她又对宋妈说：</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#171414'>英子一生下来，她爸爸就给惯的，一不舒服，爸爸就抱着睡。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>羞不羞？</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>宋妈用一个手指头划我的脸，我不理她，转过脸冲着墙闭上眼睛。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#171414'>今天我早晨起来就好得多了，不像昨天那样不安心。但是现在又想起妞儿，手里不由得停止了捉虫子的工作，呆呆地想，不知道什么时候，妞儿就会离开我。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#171414'>我把瓶子扔在树下，站起来走到窗下向里看。秀贞正在里屋床前的一把杌凳上坐着，面向着床，我只看到她那小平板儿似的背影，辫子也没梳好。她比手画脚，又扬手轰苍蝇，其实哪儿有苍蝇？我轻轻地走进屋里，在外屋桌旁靠着，傻看她在干什么，只听她说：</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>我准知道你昨儿晚上没吃饭就睡觉了，是不是？那怎么行！</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#171414'>咦！真奇怪，秀贞怎么知道我昨晚没吃饭就睡觉了呢？我倚在里屋的门框说：</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>谁告诉你的？</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>啊？</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>她回过头来看见我愁眉不展的样子，很正经地对我说：</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>还用人告诉我吗？这碗粥一动也没动呀！</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#171414'>说完指着床旁茶几上的一个碗和一双筷子。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#171414'>我这才知道秀贞说的不是我。自从天气暖和了，打开一向深闭的跨院门以后，秀贞就一天到晚在这两间屋里出出进进，说着那我又懂、又不懂的话。最先我以为是秀贞跟我玩</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#171414'>过家家儿</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#171414'>，后来才又觉得并不是假装的事情，它太像真事了！</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#171414'>秀贞又向着那空床发呆看了一会儿，转过头来，轻手轻脚地拉着我走到屋外来，小声地说：</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>睡着了，让他睡去吧！这一场病也真亏他，没亲没故的！</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#171414'>外屋书桌上摆着那缸春天买的金鱼，已经死了几条，可是秀贞还是天天勤着换水，玻璃缸里还加了几根水草，红色的鱼在绿色的水草中钻来钻去，非常好玩。</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'> </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#171414'>我怎么知道鱼是红的草是绿的呢？妈妈教过我，她说快考小学了，老师要问颜色，要问住在哪儿，要问家里有几个人。秀贞还养了一盒蚕，她对我说过：</span>
        </p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>你要上学，我们小桂子也该上学了，我养点蚕，吐了丝，好给小桂子装墨盒用。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#171414'>有几条蚕已经在吐丝了，秀贞另外把它们放在一个蒙了纸的茶杯上，就让它们在那纸上吐丝。真有趣，那些蚕很乖，就不会爬到茶杯下面来。另外的许多蚕还在吃桑叶。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#171414'>秀贞在打扫蚕屎，她把一粒粒的蚕屎装进一个铁罐里，她已经留了许多，预备装成一个小枕头，给思康三叔用。因为他每天看书眼睛得保养，蚕屎是明目的。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#171414'>我在旁边静静地看着鱼缸，看着吐丝。院子里的树，正靠在窗下，这屋里阴凉得很，我们俩都不敢大声说话，就像真的屋里躺着一个要休息的病人。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#171414'>秀贞忽然问我：</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>英子，我跟你说的事记住没有？</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#171414'>我一时想不起是什么事，因为她对我说过的事，真真假假的太多了。她说将来要我跟小桂子一块儿去上学，小桂子也要考厂甸小学。她又告诉我从厂甸小学回</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'> </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#171414'>家，顺着琉璃厂直到厂西门，看见鹿犄角胡同雷万春的玻璃窗里那对大鹿犄角，一拐进椿树胡同就到家了。可是她又说过，她要带小桂子去找思康三叔，做了许多衣</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'> </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#171414'>服和鞋子，行李都打点好了。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#171414'>我最记得秀贞说过的话，还是她讲的生小桂子的那回事。有一天，我早早溜到这里找秀贞，她看见我连辫子都没梳，就端出梳头匣子来，从里面拿出牛角梳</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'> </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#171414'>子、骨头针和大红头绳，然后把我的头发散开来，慢慢地梳。她是坐在椅子上的，我就坐在小板凳上，夹在她的两腿中间，我的两只胳膊正好架在她的两腿上，两只</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'> </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#171414'>手摸着她的两膝盖，两块骨头都成了尖石头，她瘦极了。我背着她，她问我：</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>英子，你几月生的？</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>我呀？青草长起来，绿叶发出来，妈妈说，我生在那个不冷不热的春天。小桂子呢？</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#171414'>秀贞总把我的事情和小桂子的事情连在一起，所以我也就一下子想起小桂子。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>小桂子呀，</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>秀贞说，</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>青草要黄了，绿叶快掉了，她是生在那不冷不热的秋天。那个时光，桂花倒是香的，闻见没有？就像我给你搽的这个桂花油这么香。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#171414'>她说着，把手掌送到我的鼻前晃一晃。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>小</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>——</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>桂</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>——</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>子。</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>我吸了吸鼻子，闻着那油味，不由得一字字地念出来，我好像懂得点那意思。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#171414'>秀贞很高兴地说：</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>对了，小桂子，就是这么起的名儿。</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>我怎么没看见桂花树？这里哪棵树是桂花？</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#171414'>我问。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>又不是在这屋子里生的！</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>秀贞已经在编我的辫子了，编得那么紧，拉着我的头发根怪痛的，我说：</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>为什么用这么大的力气呀？</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>我当时要是有这么大力气倒好了。我生了小桂子，浑身都没劲儿，就昏昏沉沉地睡，睡醒了，小桂子不在我身边了。我睡觉时还听见她哭，怎么醒了就没有</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'> </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#171414'>了呢？我问，孩子呢？我妈要说什么，我婶儿接过去了，她瞥了我妈一眼，跟我和和气气地说：你的身子微，孩子哭，在你身边吵，我抱到我屋去了。我说，噢。我</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'> </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#171414'>又睡着了。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#171414'>秀贞说到这儿停住了，我的辫子已经扎好，她又接着说：</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>仿佛我听我妈对我婶说：不能让她知道。真让人纳闷儿，到底是怎么档子事儿？我怎么到这儿就接不下去了呢？是她们把孩子给</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>——</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#171414'>？还是扔</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>——</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#171414'>？绝不能够！绝不能够！</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#171414'>我已经站起来，脸冲着秀贞看，她皱着眉头，正呆呆地想。她说话常常都会忽然停住了，然后就低声地说</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#171414'>真让人纳闷儿，到底是怎么档子事儿</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#171414'>的话。她收梳头匣子的时候，我看见我送小桂子的手表在匣子里，她拿起手表，放在掌心里，又说：</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>小桂子她爹也有个大怀表，可是死了当了，当了那个表，他才回的家，这份穷，就别提了！我当时就没告诉他我有了，反正他去个把月就回来。他跟我妈</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'> </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#171414'>说，放心，他回家卖了山底下的白薯地，就到北京来娶我。千山万水，去一趟也不容易，我要是告诉他我有了，不也让他惦记着！你不知道他那情意多深！我也没告</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'> </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#171414'>诉我妈我有了，说不出口，反正人归了他了，等嫁了再说也不迟</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>……</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#171414'>。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>有了什么？</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>我不明白。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>有了小桂子呀！</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>你不是刚说什么没有了吗？</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#171414'>我更不明白。</span>
        </p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>有了，没了，有了，没了，小英子，你怎么跟我乱扰？你听我给你算。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#171414'>她把我给小桂子的表收起来，然后用手指捏着算给我听：</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>他是春天走的。他走的那天，天儿多好，他提着那口箱子，都没敢多看我，他的同乡同学，有几个送他到门口儿的，所以他就没好再跟我说什么。他在头天</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'> </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#171414'>晚上我给他收拾箱子的时候，我们俩也说得差不多了。他说，惠安的日子很苦，有办法的都到海外谋生去了，那儿的地不肥，不能种什么，白薯倒是种了不少。他们</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'> </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#171414'>家，常年吃白薯，白薯饭、白薯粥、白薯干、白薯条、白薯片，能叫外头去的人吃出眼泪来。所以，他就舍不得让我这个北边人去吃那个苦头儿。我说可不是，我妈</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'> </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#171414'>就生我独一个女儿，跟你去吃白薯，她怎么舍得！他说，你是个孝女，我也是个孝子，万一我母亲扣住了我，不许我再到北京来了呢？我说，那我就追你去。</span>
        </p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>送他到门口，看他上了洋车，抬头看看天，一块白云彩，像条船，慢慢地往天边儿上挪动，我仿佛上了船，心是飘的，就跟没了主儿似的。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>我送他出去，回到屋里来，恶心要吐，头也昏，有点儿后悔没告诉他这件事，想追出去，也来不及了。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>日子一天天地挨，他就始终没回来，我肚子大了，瞒不住我妈，她急得盘问我，让我说不出道不出的，可是我也顾不得害臊了，就告诉了我妈。我说，他总</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'> </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#171414'>有一天回来，他不回来，我去！我妈听了拿手堵住我的嘴，直说：姑娘，可别这么说了，这份丢人呀！他真要是不回来，咱们可不能嚷嚷出去。就这样，把我送回了</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'> </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#171414'>海甸。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:
11.5pt;color:#171414'>小桂子生下来，真不容易，我一点劲儿都没有，就闻着窗户外头那棵桂花树吹进来的一阵阵香气，我心说，生个女的就叫小桂子。接生的姥娘婆叫我咬住了辫子，使劲，使劲，总算落了地，呱呱呱，哭声好大呀！</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:18.75pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#171414'>秀贞说到这儿，喘了一大口气，她的脸色变青了，故事接不下去，就随便说了，她说：</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.0pt;margin-left:0cm;
