                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>?”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　蒋一轮说：</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>你就把地好好扫一扫，地太脏了。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>不，我要参加汇操。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>汇操人够了</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>汇操不是每个人都要参加的吗？</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>说了，你明天就在教室里呆着。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>为什么</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>?”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　蒋一轮用眼睛瞥了一下秃鹤的头。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　秃鹤低下头朝办公室外边走。在将要走出办公室时，他用脚将门</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>咚</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>地狠踢了一下。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　第二天早上，其他四所小学校的学生们，在老师们的严厉监督下，从不同的方向朝油麻地小学的操场鱼贯而入。歌声此起彼伏，在寒冷的冬天，硬是渲染出一番热气腾腾的景象。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　蒋一轮走到教室里，，并没有看到秃鹤，就问班上同学：</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>见到陆鹤没有</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>?”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　有同学说：</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>他在操场的台子上。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”<br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　蒋一轮听罢，立即奔到操场，果然见到秃鹤正坐在本是给那些学校的校长们预备下的椅子上。他立即走上那个土台，叫道：</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>陆鹤</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　秃鹤不回头。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　蒋一轮提高了嗓门：</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>陆鹤</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　秃鹤勉强转过头去，但看了一眼蒋一轮，又把脸转过去朝台下那些来自外校的学生们望。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　台下的学生们正朝秃鹤指指点点，并在嘻嘻嘻地笑。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　蒋一轮拍了一下秃鹤的肩膀：</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>走，跟我回教室。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　秃鹤决不让步：</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>我要参加汇操。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>你也要参加汇操</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>?”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>蒋一轮不自觉地在喉咙里笑了一声。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　这一声笑刺痛了秃鹤，使秃鹤变得很怪，他站起来，走到台口去，朝下面的同学呲着牙，故意地傻笑。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　蒋一轮连忙追到台口：</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>跟我回教室，你听到没有</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>?”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>我要参加汇操！</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　蒋一轮只好说：</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>好好好，但你现在跟我回教室</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>!”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>说着，连拖带拉地将他扯下了台。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>我要参加汇操</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>!”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　蒋一轮说：</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>那你必须戴上帽子。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>我没有帽子。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>我去给你找帽子。你先站在这里别动。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>蒋一轮急忙跑回宿舍，将自己的一顶闲置的棉帽子从箱子里找出来，又匆匆忙忙跑回来给秃鹤戴上了。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　秃鹤将棉帽摘下，摸了摸自己的脑袋，又将棉帽戴上，然后讥讽而又带了点恶毒地一笑，站到了已经集合好的队伍里去了。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　汇操开始了，各学校的校长们</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>一</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>字坐到了台上，露出一对对自得与挑剔的目光。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　各学校都是精心准备好了到油麻地小学来一决雌雄的，一家一家地进行，一家一家都显得纪律严明，一丝不苟。虽说那些孩子限于条件，衣服难免七长八短，或过于肥大又或过于短促，但还是整洁的。低年级的孩子，十有八九，裤子下垂，仿佛随时都有可能当众滑落，在寒冬腊月里露出光腚，但眼睛却是瞪得溜圆，一副认真到家的样子。各家水平相近，外行人不大看得出差异。但那些校长们却很快就在心里写出了分数。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　油麻地小学是东道主，最后一家出场。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　当第四所小学进行到一半时，桑乔脸上就已露出一丝让人觉察不到的笑容。因为就他所见到的前四家的水平，油麻地小学在这一次的汇操中拿第一，几乎已是囊中取物。桑乔早把油麻地小学吃透了，很清楚地知道它在什么水平上。他不再打算看完人家的表演，却把目光转移开去，望着场外正准备入场、跃跃欲试的油麻地小学的大队伍。桑乔对荣誉是吝啬的，哪怕是一点点小荣誉，他也绝不肯轻易放过。</span><span
