            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　第四所小学表演一结束，油麻地小学的队伍风风火火迅捷地占领了偌大一个操场。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　操场四周种植的都是白杨树。它们在青灰色</span><span
