                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>的天空下，笔直地挺立着。脱尽叶子而只剩下褐色</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>*</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>树干之后的白杨，显得更为劲拔。</span><span lang=EN-US
