            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　蒋一轮说：</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>谁告诉你们，他与你们就是一个小组的呢？瞎传什么！</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”<br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　蒋一轮等把这几个孩子打发走之后，用铅笔把秃鹤的名字一圈，然后又划了一道杠，将他插</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>*</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>进了另一个小组。那道杠，就象一根绳子拽着秃鹤，硬要把他拽到另一个地方去。这个小组的同学又知道了秃鹤被分给他们了，就学上面的那个小组的办法，也都来找蒋一轮。就这么搞来搞去的，秃鹤成了谁也不要的人。其实，大多数人对秃鹤与他们分在一个小组，倒也觉得无所谓，但既然有人不要了，他们再要，就觉得是捡了人家不稀罕要的，于是也不想要了。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　蒋一轮将秃鹤叫到办公室：</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>你自己打算分在哪一个组？</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　秃鹤用手指抠着办公桌。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>你别抠办公桌。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　秃鹤就把手放下了。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>愿意在哪一个组呢？</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　秃鹤又去抠办公桌了。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>让你别抠办公桌就别抠办公桌。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　秃鹤就又把手放下了。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>你自己选择吧。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　秃鹤没有抬头：</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>我随便。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>说完，就走出了办公室。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　秃鹤没有回教室。他走出校园，然后沿着河边，漫无目标地往前走，一直走到那个大砖窑。当时，砖窑顶上还在灌水。一窑的砖烧了三七二十一天，现在都已烧熟了。再从顶上慢慢地灌上七天的水，就会落得一窑的好青砖。熟坯经了水，就往外散浓烈的热气，整个窑顶如同被大雾弥漫了。从西边吹来的风，又把这乳白色</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>*</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>的热气往东刮来。秃鹤迎着这热气，一步一步地走过去。后来，他爬到了离窑不远的一堆砖坯上。他完全被笼罩在了热气里。偶尔吹来一阵大风，吹开热气，才隐隐约约地露出他的身体。谁也看不到他，他也看不到别人。秃鹤觉得这样挺好。他就这么坐着，让那湿润的热气包裹着他，抚摸着他</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>……<br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　六春节即将来临，油麻地小学接到上头的通知：春节期间，将举行全乡四十三所中小学的文艺汇演。这种汇演，基本上每年一次。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　油麻地小学自从由桑乔担任校长以来，在每年的大汇演中都能取得好的名次。如今，作为办公室的那幢最大的草房子里，已挂满了在大汇演中获得的奖状。每逢遇到汇演，油麻地小学就不得安宁了。各班级有演出才能的孩子，都被抽调了出来，在临时辟作排练场地的另一幢草房子里，经常成日成夜地排练。那些孩子有时累得睁不开眼睛，桑乔就用鼓槌猛烈地敲打鼓边，大声叫着：</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>醒醒！醒醒！</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>于是那些孩子就一边揉着惺忪的眼睛，一边又迷迷糊糊地走上场，想不起台词或说错台词的事常有。说得驴头不对马嘴时，众人就爆笑，而在爆笑声中，那个还未清醒过来的孩子就会清醒过来。桑乔除了大声吼叫，在大多数情况之下，又是小心翼翼地呵护着这些能够为油麻地小学争得荣誉的孩子的。其他同学要经常参加学校的劳动，而这些孩子可以不参加。每学期评奖，这些孩子总会因为参加了油麻地小学的文艺宣传队而讨一些便宜。夜里排练结束后，他会让老师们统统出动，将这些孩子一一护送回家。他本人背着孩子走过泥泞的乡村小道或走过被冰雪覆盖的独木小桥，也是常有的事情。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑桑和纸月都是文艺宣传队的。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　因为是年年争得好名次，因此，对油麻地小学来说，再争得好名次，难度就越来越大了。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>今年必须争得小学组第一名！</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>桑乔把蒋一轮等几个负责文艺宣传队的老师们召到他的办公室，不容商量地说。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>没有好本子。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>蒋一轮说。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>没有好本子，去找好本子。找不到好本子，就自己写出好本子。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>桑乔说。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　蒋一轮去了一趟县城，找到县文化馆，从他的老同学那里取回来一些本子。油麻地小学的策略是：大人的戏，小孩来演，会收到意想不到的效果。桑乔说：</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>你想想，一个八九岁的小男孩，戴顶老头帽，叼着一支烟袋，躬着个身子在台上走，一个八九岁的小女孩，穿一件老大妈的蓝布褂儿，挎着个竹篮子，双手互相扣着在台上走，这本身就是戏。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>他让蒋一轮们今年还是坚持这一策略。因此，蒋一轮从县文化宫取回来的，全是大人的戏。他把这些本子看过之后，又交给桑乔看。桑乔看后，又与蒋一轮商量，从中选了两个小戏。其中一个，是桑乔最看得上的，叫《屠桥》。屠桥是个地名。剧情实际上很一般：屠桥这个地方一天来了一连伪军，他们在这里无恶不作，欺压百姓，那天夜里来了新四军，将他们全都堵在了被窝里。桑乔看上这个本子的原因是因为这个本子里头有许多让人不得不笑的场面。几个主要角色</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>*</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>很快分配好了，新四军队长由杜小康扮演，十八岁的姑娘由纸月扮演，伪军连长由柳三下扮演。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　蒋一轮刻钢板，将本子印了十几份，都分了下去。下面的环节，无非是背台词、对台词、排练、彩排，直至正式演出。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　一切都很顺利。杜小康是男孩里头最潇洒、又长得最英俊的，演一身英气的新四军队长，正合适。纸月演那个秀美的有点让人怜爱的小姑娘，让人无话可说，仿佛这个纸月日后真的长成一个十八岁的姑娘时，也就是那样一个姑娘。柳三下演得也不错，一副下流坯子的样子，也演出来了。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　等到彩排了，蒋一轮才发现一件事没有考虑到：那个伪军连长，在剧本里头是个大秃子。他必须是个秃子，因为里头许多唱词与道白，都要涉及到秃子，甚至剧情都与秃子有关。如果他不是一个秃子，这个剧本也就不成立了。反过来说，这个剧本之所以成立，也正是因为这个连长不是一般的连长，而是一个秃子连长。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑乔这才发现，他当时所看好的这个本子具有令人发笑的效果，原来全在于这个连长是个大秃子。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>这怎么办？</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>蒋一轮问。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>不好办。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>就当柳三下是个秃子吧。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>你拉倒吧，他那一头好头发，长得像杂草似的茂盛。他一上台，别人不看他的脸，就光看他的头发了。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>桑乔想像着说，</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>他往台上这么一站，然后把大盖帽一甩，道：</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>‘</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>我杨大秃瓢，走马到屠桥</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>……’”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　蒋一轮</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>噗哧</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>笑了。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑乔说：</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>老办法，去找个猪尿泡套上。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>哪儿去找猪尿泡？</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>找屠夫丁四。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>丁四不好说话。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>我去跟他说。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　第二天，桑乔就从丁四那里弄来了一个猪尿泡。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　柳三下闻了闻，眉头皱成一把：</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>骚！</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑乔说：</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>不骚，就不叫猪尿泡了。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>他拿过猪尿泡来，像一位长官给他的一位立功的下属戴一顶军帽那样，将那个猪尿泡慢慢地套在了柳三下的头上。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　柳三下顿时成了一个秃子。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　于是，大家忽然觉得，《屠桥》这个本子在那里熠熠生辉。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　彩排开始，正演到节骨眼上，猪尿泡爆了，柳三下的黑头发露出一绺来。那形象，笑倒了一片人。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑乔又从丁四那里求得一个猪尿泡，但用了两次，又爆了。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>跟丁四再要一个。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>蒋一轮说。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑乔说：</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>好好跟丁四求，他倒也会给的。但，我们不能用猪尿泡了，万一汇演那天，正演到一半，它又爆了呢？</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>你是想让柳三下剃个大光头？</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>也只有这样了。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　蒋一轮对柳三下一说，柳三下立即用双手捂住了自己的头：</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>那不行，我不能做秃鹤。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>仿佛不是要剃他的发，而是要割他的头。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>校长说的。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>校长说的也不行。他怎么不让他家桑桑也剃个秃子呢？</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>桑桑拉胡琴，他又不是演员。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>反正，我不能剃个秃子。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”<br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑乔来做了半天工作，才将柳三下说通了，但下午上学时，柳三下又反口了：</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>我爸死活也不干。他说再过几天就要过年了，我怎么能是个秃头呢？</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”<br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑乔只好去找柳三下的父亲。柳三下的父亲是这个地方上有名的一个固执人，任你桑乔说得口干舌苦，他也只是一句话：</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>我家三下，谁也不能动他一根汗毛！</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”<br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　眼看着就要汇演了，油麻地小学上上下下就为这么一个必须的秃头而苦恼不堪。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>只好不演这个本子了。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>桑乔说。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>不演，恐怕拿不了第一名，就数这个本子好。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>蒋一轮说。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>没办法，也只能这样了。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　很快，油麻地小学的学生们都传开了：</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>《屠桥》不演了。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>都很遗憾。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　秃鹤在一旁静静地听着，不说话。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　傍晚，孩子们都放学回去了，秃鹤却不走，在校园门口转悠。当他看到桑桑从家里走出来时，连忙过去：</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>桑桑。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>你还没有回家？</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>我马上就回去。你给我送个纸条给蒋老师好吗？</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>有什么事吗？</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>你先别管。你就把这个纸条送给他。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>好吧。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>桑桑接过纸条。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　秃鹤转身离开了校园，不一会工夫就消失在苍茫的暮色</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>*</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>里。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　蒋一轮打开了秃鹤的纸条，那上面工工整整地写着：</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　蒋老师：</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　我可以试一试吗？</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　陆鹤</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　蒋一轮先是觉得有点好笑，但抓纸条的双手立即微微颤抖起来。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　当桑乔看到这个纸条时，也半天没有说话，然后说：</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>一定让他试一试。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”<br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　秃鹤从未演过戏。但秃鹤决心演好这个戏。他用出人意料的速度，就将所有台词背得滚瓜烂熟。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　不知是因为秃鹤天生就有演出的才能，还是这个戏在排练时秃鹤也看过，他居然只花一个上午就承担起了角色</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>*</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　在参加汇演的前两天，所有参加汇演的节目，先给油麻地小学的全体师生演了一遍，当秃鹤上场时，全场掌声雷动，孩子们全无一丝恶意。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　秃鹤要把戏演得更好。他把这个角色</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>*</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>要用的服装与道具全都带回家中。晚上，他把自己打扮成那个伪军连长，到院子里，借着月光，反反复复地练着：</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　小姑娘，快快长，</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　长大了，跟连长，</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　有得吃，有得穿，</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　还有花不完的现大洋</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>……<br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　他将大盖帽提在手里，露着光头，就当纸月在场，驴拉磨似地旋转着，数着板。那个连长出现时，是在夏日。秃鹤就是按夏日来打扮自己的。但眼下却是隆冬季节，寒气侵入肌骨。秃鹤不在意这个天气，就这么不停地走，不停地做动作，额头竟然出汗了。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　到灯光明亮的大舞台演出那天，秃鹤已胸有成竹。《屠桥》从演出一开始，就得到了台下的掌声，接下来，掌声不断。当秃鹤将大盖帽甩给他的勤务兵，秃头在灯光下锃光瓦亮时，评委们就已经感觉到，桑乔又要夺得一个好名次了。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　秃鹤演得一丝不苟。他脚蹬大皮靴，一只脚踩在凳子上，从桌上操起一把茶壶，喝得水直往脖子里乱流，然后脑袋一歪，眼珠子瞪得鼓鼓的：</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>我杨大秃瓢，走马到屠桥</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>……”<br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　在与纸月周旋时，一个凶恶，一个善良；一个丑陋，一个美丽，对比得十分强烈。可以说，秃鹤把那个角色</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>*</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>演绝了。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　演出结束后，油麻地小学的师生们只管沉浸在胜利的喜悦之中，而当他们忽然想到秃鹤时，秃鹤早已不见了。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　问谁，谁也不知道秃鹤的去向。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>大家立即分头去找。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>桑乔说。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　是桑桑第一个找到了秃鹤。那时，秃鹤正坐在小镇的水码头的最低的石阶上，望着被月光照得波光粼粼的河水。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑桑一直走到他跟前，在他身边蹲下：</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>我是来找你的，大家都在找你。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑桑听到了秃鹤的啜泣声。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　油麻地小学的许多师生都找来了。他们沿着石阶走了下来，对秃鹤说：</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>我们回家吧。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑乔拍了拍他的肩：</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>走，回家了。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”<br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　秃鹤用嘴咬住指头，想不让自己哭出声来，但哭声还是克制不住地从喉咙里奔涌而出，几乎变成了号啕大哭。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　纸月哭了，许多孩子也都哭了。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　纯静的月光照着大河，照着油麻地小学的师生们，也照着世界上一个最英俊的少年</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>……</span></p>

        <h2 style='margin-left:56.25pt;text-indent:-56.25pt'><span lang=EN-US>第二章<span
                    style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span
                style='font-family:宋体'>纸月</span></h2>

        <p class=MsoNormal><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>一</span><span lang=EN-US><a
                    href="http://www.xyyuedu.com/mz/baomugouyinmou/37139.html"><span lang=EN-US
                        style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#3C3B3B'><span
                            lang=EN-US>纸月</span></span></a></span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:
宋体;color:#171414'>的外婆用手拉着</span><span lang=EN-US><a href="http://www.xyyuedu.com/mz/baomugouyinmou/37139.html"><span
                        lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#3C3B3B'><span
                            lang=EN-US>纸月</span></span></a></span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>，出现在桑桑家的院子里时，是那年秋天的一个下午。那时，桑桑正在喂它的那群纯一色</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>*</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>的白鸽。白鸽受了陌生人的惊扰，呼啦一声飞了起来。这时，桑桑一眼看到了纸月：她被白鸽的突然起飞与那么强烈的翅响惊得紧紧搂住外婆的胳膊，靠在外婆的身上，微微缩着脖子，还半眯着眼睛，生怕鸽子的翅膀会打着她似的。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　白鸽在天上盘旋着，当时正是一番最好的秋天的阳光，鸽群从天空滑过时，满空中泛着迷人的白光。这些小家伙，居然在见了陌生人之后，产生了表演的欲望，在空中潇洒而优美地展翅、滑翔或作集体性</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>*</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>的俯冲、拔高与互相穿梭。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑桑看到了外婆身旁一张微仰着的脸、一对乌黑乌黑的眼睛。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　白鸽们终于象倒转的旋风，朝下盘旋，然后又纷纷落进院子里，发出一片</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>咕咕</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>声。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　纸月慢慢地从受了惊吓的状态里出来，渐渐松开外婆的胳膊，新鲜而又欢喜地看着这一地雪团样的白鸽。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>这里是桑校长家吗？</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>纸月的外婆问。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑桑点点头。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>你是桑桑？</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>纸月的外婆拉着纸月往前走了一步。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑桑点点头，但用疑惑的目光望着纸月的外婆：你是怎么知道我叫桑桑的？</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>谁都知道，桑校长家有个长得很俊的男孩人叫桑桑。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”<br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑桑突然不安起来，因为，他看到了自己的样子：没有穿鞋人两只光脚脏兮兮的；裤子被胯骨勉强地挂住个一只裤管耷拉在脚面，而另一只裤管却卷到了膝盖以上；褂子因与人打架，缺了钮扣，而两只小口袋，有一只也被人撕下了，还有一点点连着。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>你爸爸在家吗？</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>纸月的外婆问。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>在。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>桑桑趁机跑进屋里，</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>爸，有人找。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”<br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑乔走了出来。他认识纸月的外婆，便招呼纸月的外婆与纸月进屋。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　纸月还是拉着外婆的手，一边望着鸽子，一边轻手轻脚地走着，生怕再惊动了它们。而鸽子并不怕纸月，其中一只，竟然跑到了纸月的脚下来啄一粒玉米，纸月就赶紧停住不走，直到外婆用力拉了她一下，她才侧着身子走过去。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑桑没有进屋，但桑桑很注意地听着屋子里的对话</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>——<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>这丫头叫纸月。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>这名字好听。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>我想把纸月转到您的学校来上学。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>那为什么呢？</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　停顿了一阵，纸月的外婆说：</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>也不为什么，只是纸月这孩子不想再在板仓小学念书了。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>这恐怕不行呀。上头有规定，小孩就地上学。纸月就该在板仓小学上学。再说，孩子来这儿上学也很不方便，从板仓走到油麻地，要走三里路。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>她能走。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　屋里没有声了。过了一会，父亲说：</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>您给我出难题了。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>让她来吧。孩子不想在那儿再念书了。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>纸月，</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>父亲的声音，</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>这么远的路口你走得动吗？</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　停了停，纸月说：</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>我走得动。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　过了一会，父亲说：</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>我们再商量商量吧。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>我和纸月谢谢您了。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑桑紧接着听到了父亲吃惊的声音：</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>大妈，别这样别这样！</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>桑桑走到门口往屋里看了一眼，只见外婆拉着纸月正要在父亲面前跪下来，被父亲一把扶住了。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　随即，桑桑听到了外婆与纸月的轻轻的啜泣声。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑桑蹲在地上，呆呆地看着他的鸽子。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　父亲说：</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>再过两天就开学了，您就让孩子来吧。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”<br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　纸月和外婆走出屋子，来到院子里，正要往外走时，桑桑的母亲挎着竹篮从菜园里回来了。桑桑的母亲一见了纸月，就喜欢上了：</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>这小丫头，真体面。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　几个大人，又说起了纸月转学的事。母亲说：</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>遇到刮风下雨天，纸月就在我家吃饭，就在我家住。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>母亲望着纸月，目光里满是怜爱。当母亲忽然注意到桑桑时，说：</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>桑桑，你看看人家纸月，浑身上下这么干干净净的，你看你那双手，剁下来狗都不闻。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”<br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑桑和纸月都把手藏到了身后。桑桑藏住的是一双满是污垢的黑乎乎的手，纸月藏住的却是一双白净的细嫩如笋的手。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　纸月和她的外婆走后，桑桑的父亲与母亲就一直在说纸月家的事。桑桑就在一旁听着，将父亲与母亲支离破碎的话连成了一个完整的故事：</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　纸月的母亲是这一带长得最水灵的女子。后来，她怀孕了，肚皮一日一日地隆起来。但谁也不知道这孩子是谁的。她也不说，只是一声不吭地让孩子在她的肚子里一天一天地大起来。纸月的外婆似乎也没有太多地责备纸月的母亲，只是做她应该做的事情。纸月的母亲在怀着纸月的时候，依然还是那么的好看，只是脸色</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>*</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>一天比一天的白，眼窝一天比天地深陷下去。她不常出门，大多数时间就是在屋子里给将要出生的纸月做衣服做鞋。她在那些衣服与裤子上绣上了她最喜欢的花，一针一线的，都很认真。秋天，当田野间的野菊花开出一片黄的与淡紫的小花朵时，纸月出世了。一个月后，纸月的母亲在一天的黄昏离开了家门。两天后，人们在四周长满菖蒲的水塘里找到了她。从此，纸月的外婆，既作为纸月的外婆，又作为纸月的母亲，一日一日地，默默地将小小的纸月养活着。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　关于纸月为什么要从板仓小学转到油麻地小学来读书，桑桑的父亲的推测是：</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>板仓小学那边肯定有坏孩子欺负纸月。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑桑的母亲听到了，就倚在门框上，长长地叹了一口气</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>……<br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　二桑桑向母亲提出他要有一件新褂子，理由是马上就要开学了，他应该有一件新褂子。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　母亲说：</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>这是太阳从西边出来了，你也知道要新衣服了。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>就很快去镇上扯回布来，领着桑桑去一个做缝纫活的人家量了身长，并让人家尽快将活做出来。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　开学头一天下午，桑桑跑到水码头，将衣服脱了扔在草上，然后撩着河水洗着身子。秋后的河水已经很凉了，桑桑一激灵一激灵的，在水码头上不停地跳，又不停地颤颤抖抖地把那些乡谣大声叫唤出来：</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　姐姐十五我十六，</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　妈生姐姐我煮粥，</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　爸爸睡在摇篮里，</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　没有奶吃向我哭，</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　记得外公娶外婆，</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　我在轿前放爆竹。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　就有人发笑，并将桑桑的母亲从屋里叫出来：</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>看你家桑桑在干什么呢。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”<br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑桑的母亲走到河边上，不知是因为桑桑的样子很好笑，还是因为桑桑大声嚷嚷着的乡谣很好笑，就绷不住脸笑了：</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>小猴子儿冻死你！</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”<br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑桑转身对着母亲，用肥皂将自己擦得浑身是沫，依然不住声地大叫着。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑桑的母亲过来要拉桑桑，桑桑就趁机往后一仰，跌进了河里。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑桑觉得自己总算洗得很干净了，才爬上岸。现在，桑桑的母亲见到的桑桑，是一个浑身被清洌的河水洗得通红、没有一星污垢的桑桑。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑桑穿好衣服，说：</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>我要去取我的白褂子。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>说着就走了。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑桑的衣服被搁下了，还没有做好，桑桑就坐在人家门槛上等，人家只好先把手里的活停下来做他的白褂子。桑桑直到把白褂子等到手才回家。那时天都黑了，村里人家都已亮灯了。回到家，桑桑的脑袋被正在吃饭的母亲用筷子敲了一下：</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>这孩子，像等不及了。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”<br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　第二天，桑桑上学路过办公室门口时，首先是正在往池塘边倒药渣的温幼菊发现了桑桑，惊讶地：</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>喔哟，桑桑，你要想干吗？</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”<br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　那时，各班老师都正准备往自己的教室走。见了平素整日泥猴一样甚至常不洗脸的桑桑，今日居然打扮成这样，都围过来看。六年级的语文老师朱恒问：</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>桑桑，是有相亲的要来吗？</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑桑说：</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>去你的。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>他自己也感觉到，他的小白褂子实在太白了，赶紧往自己的教室走。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑桑进了教室，又遭到同学们一阵哄笑。不知是谁有节奏地喊了一声</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>小白褂</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>，随即全体响应：</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>小白褂！小白褂！</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>……”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　眼见着桑桑要变恼了，他们才停止叫唤。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　上课前一刻钟，正当教室里乱得听不见人语时，蒋一轮领着纸月出现在门口。教室里顿时安静下来，大家都在打量纸月：纸月上身穿着袖口大大的紫红色</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>*</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>褂子，下身穿着裤管微微短了一点的蓝布裤子，背着一只墨绿色</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>*</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>的绣了一朵红莲花的书包，正怯生生地看着大家。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>她叫纸月，是你们的新同学。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>蒋一轮说。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　</span><span lang=EN-US
