                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>桑桑，你下来吧，下来吧。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>再比如说桑桑顺手从地里拔了根胡萝卜，在袖子上搓擦了几下，就</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>咯吱咯吱</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>地吃起来时，纸月见了，就会令人觉察不到地皱一下眉头，嘴微微地张着看了一眼桑桑，这时，桑桑假如看到了这双眼睛，就会听出：</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>桑桑，不洗的萝卜也是吃得的吗？</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>再比如说桑桑把时间玩光了，来不及去抠算术题了，打算将邻桌的作业本抓过来抄一通时，纸月看见了，就会把眼珠转到眼角上来看桑桑，这时，假如桑桑看到了这双眼睛，就会听出：</span><span
