                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>哥哥不再抢我的饼吃了。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”<br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　三初冬的一天下午，北风越刮越大，到了快放学时，天气迅捷阴</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>*</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>沉下来，桑桑家的那些在外觅食的鸽子受了惊吓，立即离开野地，飞上乱云飞渡的天空，然后象被大风吹得乱飘的枯叶一般，飘飘忽忽地飞回草</span><span
                lang=EN-US><a href="http://www.xyyuedu.com/jdwenz/renshenggw/26143.html"><span lang=EN-US
                        style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#3C3B3B'><span
                            lang=EN-US>房子</span></span></a></span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:
宋体;color:#171414'>。白杨在大风里鸣响，旗杆上的麻绳一下子一下子猛烈地鞭打着旗杆，发出</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>叭叭</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>声响。孩子们兴奋而略带恐怖地坐在教室里，早已听不下课去，只在心里想着</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>怎么回家去呢</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>?</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>桑乔走出办公室，呛了几口北风，系好领扣，看了看眼看就要压到头上的天空，便跑到各个教室说</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>现在就放学</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>!”<br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　不一会，各个教室的门都打开了，孩子们只管将书本与文具胡乱地塞进书包，叫喊着，或互相呼唤着同路者的名字，纷纷往校园外面跑，仿佛马上就有一场劫难。</span><span
