            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　纸月收拾好自己的书包时，教室里就几乎只剩她一个人了。她朝门外看了看，一脸的惶恐与不安。因为，她马上想到了</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>未等到她回到家中，半路上就会有暴风雨的。那时，前不着村后不着店，她可怎么办呢</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>?<br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑桑的母亲正在混乱的孩子群中朝这边走着，见着站在风中打哆嗦的桑桑问</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>纸月呢</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>?”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑桑</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>在教室里。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑桑的母亲急忙走到了教室门口</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>纸月。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　纸月见了桑桑的母亲，学着外婆的叫法，叫了一声</span><span
