            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　纸月说</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>我还是回家吧。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑桑的母亲说</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>你会被雨浇在半路上的。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>说罢，就过来拉住纸月冰凉的手，</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>走吧，外婆那边肯定会知道的。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”<br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　当纸月跟着桑桑的母亲走出教室时，纸月不知为什么低下了头，眼睛里汪了泪水。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　一直在不远处站着的桑桑，见母亲领着纸月正往这边走，赶紧回头先回家了。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　纸月来到桑桑家不久，天就下起雨来，一开头就很猛烈。桑桑趴在窗台上往外看时，只见四下里白茫茫的一片，油麻地小学的草房子在雨幕里都看不成形了，虚虚幻幻的。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　柳柳听说纸月要在她家过夜，异常兴奋，拉住纸月的手就不肯再松下，反复向母亲说</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>我跟纸月姐姐一张床。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　纸月的神情不一会就安定自如了。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　在柳柳与纸月说话，纸月被柳柳拉着在屋里不住地走动时，桑桑则在一旁，不住地给两只小鸽子喂食，忙着做晚饭的母亲，在弥漫于灶房里的雾气中说</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>你是非要把这两只小鸽子撑死不可。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”<br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑桑这才不喂鸽子。可是桑桑不知道做什么好。他只好又趴到窗台上去，望外面的天气</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>天已晚了，黑乎乎的，那些草房子已几乎看不见了。但桑桑通过檐口的雨滴声，至少可以判断出离他家最近的那两幢草房子的位置。桑桑的耳朵里，除了稠密的雨声，偶尔会穿插</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>*</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>进来柳柳与纸月的说笑声。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　隐隐约约地，从屋后的大河上，传来打鱼人因为天气从而心情便略带了些悲伤的歌声。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　纸月果然被桑桑的母亲安排和柳柳一张床。柳柳便脱了鞋，爬到床上高兴地蹦跳。母亲就说</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>柳柳别闹。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>但柳柳却蹦得更高。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　母亲及时地在屋子中央烧了一个大火盆。屋外虽是凉风凉雨，但这草房子里，却是一派暖融融的。柳柳与纸月的脸颊被暖得红红的。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　不住地作睡前忙碌的母亲，有时会停住看一眼纸月。她的目光里，总是含着一份丢不下的怜爱。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑桑睡在里间，纸月了和柳柳睡在外间。里间与外间，是隔了一道薄薄的用芦苇杆编成的篱笆。因此，外间柳柳与纸月的说话声，桑桑都听得十分分明一一</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　纸月教柳柳一句一句地念着</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　一树黄梅个个青，</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　打雷落雨满天星，</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　三个和尚四方坐，</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　不言不语口念经。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　柳柳一边念一边乐得咯咯笑。学完了，又缠着纸月再念一个。纸月很乐意</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　正月梅花香又香，</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　二月兰花盆里装。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　三月桃花红十里，</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　四月蔷薇靠短墙。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　五月石榴红似水，</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　六月荷花满池塘。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　七月桅子头上戴，</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　八月桂花满树黄。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　九月菊花初开放，</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　十月芙蓉正上妆。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　十一月水仙供上案，</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　十二月腊梅雪里香。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑桑睁着一双大眼，也在心里默默地念着。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　母亲将一切收拾停当，在里屋叫道</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>柳柳，别再总缠着姐姐了，天不早了，该睡觉了。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　灯一盏一盏地相继熄灭。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　两个女孩在一条被窝里睡着，大概是互相碰着了，不住地咯咯地笑。过不一会，柳柳说</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>纸月姐姐，我和你一头睡行吗</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>?”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　纸月说</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>你过来吧。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”<br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　柳柳就象一只猫从被窝里爬了过来。当柳柳终于钻到了纸月怀里时，两个女孩又是一阵</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>咯咯咯</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>地笑</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　就听见里屋里母亲说了一句</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>柳柳疯死了。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”<br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　柳柳赶紧闭嘴，直往纸月怀里乱钻着。但过不一会，桑桑就又听见柳柳跟纸月说话。这回声音小，好像是两个人都钻到被窝里去了。但桑桑依然还是隐隐约约地听清了一一是柳柳在向纸月讲他的坏话一一</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　柳柳</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>好多年前，好多年前，我哥哥</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>……”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　纸月</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>怎么会好多年前呢</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>?”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　柳柳</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>反正有好几年了。那天，我哥哥把家里的一口锅拿到院子里，偷偷地砸了。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　纸月</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>砸锅干什么</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>?”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　柳柳</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>卖铁呗。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　纸月</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>卖铁干什么</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>?”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　柳柳</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>换钱观。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　纸月</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>换钱干什么</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>?”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　柳柳</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>换钱买鸽子呗。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　纸月</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>后来呢</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>?”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　柳柳</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>后来妈妈烧饭，发现锅没有了，就找锅，到处找不着，就问哥哥看见锅没有</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>?</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>哥哥看着妈妈就往后退。妈妈明白了，就要去抓住哥哥</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>……”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　纸月</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>他跑了吗</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>?”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　柳柳</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>跑了。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　纸月</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>跑哪儿啦</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>?”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　柳柳</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>院门正好关着呢，他跑不了，就爬到猪圈里去了。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　纸月</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>爬到猪圈里去了</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>?”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　柳柳</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>爬到猪圈里去了。老母猪就哼哼哼地过来咬他</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>……”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　纸月有点紧张</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>咬着了吗</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>?”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　柳柳</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>哥哥踩了一脚猪屎，又爬出来了</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>……”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　纸月躲在被窝里笑了。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　柳柳</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>我哥可脏了。他早上不洗脸就吃饭</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>!”<br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑桑听得咬牙切齿，恨不能从床上蹦下来，一把将柳柳从热烘烘的被窝里抓出来，然后踢她一脚。幸好，柳柳渐渐困了，又糊糊涂涂地说了几句，就搂着纸月的脖子睡着了。不一会，桑桑就听到了两个女孩细弱而均匀的鼾声。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　窗外，雨还在浙沥浙沥地下着。有只鸽子，大概是被雨打湿了，</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>咕咕</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>叫着，但想到这也是很平常的事，叫了两声，也就不叫了。桑桑不久也睡着了。后半夜，风停了，雨停了天居然在飘散了三两丛乌云之后，出来了月亮。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　夜行的野鸭，疲倦了，就往大河里落。落到水面上，大概是因为水里有大鱼好奇吸吮了它们的脚，惊得</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>呱呱</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>一阵叫。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑桑醒来了。桑桑的第一个念头，就是想撒尿。但桑桑不能撒尿。因为桑桑想到自己如果要撒尿，就必须从里间走出，然后穿过外间走到门外去，而从外间走过时，必须要经过纸月的床前。桑桑只好忍着。他感觉到自己的小肚子正在越来越严重地鼓胀起来。他有点懊悔晚上不该喝下那么多汤的。可是当时，他只想头也不抬地喝。幸亏就那么多汤。如果盆里有更多的汤，这下就更糟糕了。桑桑不想一个劲地想着撒尿，就让自己去想点其它的事情。他想到了住在校园里的秦大奶奶</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>现在，她是睡着呢，还是醒着呢</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>?</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>听父母亲说，她一个人过了一辈子。这么长的夜晚，就她一个人，不觉得孤单吗</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>?</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>他又想到了油麻地第一富庶人家的儿子杜小康。他在心里说</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>你傲什么</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>?</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>你有什么好傲的</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>?</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>但桑桑又不免悲哀地承认一年四季总是穿着白球鞋的杜小康，确实是其它孩子不能比的一一他的样子，他的成绩，还有很多很多方面，都是不能和他比的。桑桑突然觉得杜小康傲，是有理由的。但桑桑依然不服气，甚至很生气</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>……<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　小肚的胀痛，打断了桑桑的思路。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑桑忽然听到了纸月于梦中发出的叹气声。于是桑桑又去很混乱地想纸月</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>纸月从田埂上走过来的样子、纸月读书的声音、纸月的毛笔字、纸月在舞台上舞着大红绸</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>……<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　后来，桑桑又睡着了。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　第二天早上，母亲在收拾桑桑的床时，手突然感觉到了潮湿，打开被子一看，发现桑桑夜里尿床了，，很惊诧</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>桑桑还是五岁前尿过床，怎么现在十多岁了又尿床了</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>?</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>她一边将被子抱到院子里晾着，一边在心里疑问着</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　早晨的阳光十分明亮地照着桑桑的被子。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　温幼菊进了院子，见了晾在绳子上的被，问</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>是谁呀</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>?”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　母亲说</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>是桑桑。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”<br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　那时，纸月正背着书包从屋里出来。但纸月只看了一眼那床被子，就走出了院子。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑桑一头跑进了屋子。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　过了一刻钟，桑桑出来了，见院子里无人，将被子狠狠地从绳子上扯下来，扔到了地上。而当时的地上，还留着夜间的积水。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　母亲正好出来看到了，望着已走出院门的桑桑</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>你找死哪</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>?”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑桑猛地扭过头来看了母亲一眼，抹了一把眼泪，跑掉了。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　四这天，纸月没有来上学。她的外婆来油麻地小学请假，说纸月生病了。纸月差不多有一个星期没有来上学。蒋一轮看看纸月拉下了许多作业，就对桑桑说</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>你跑一趟板仓，将作业本给纸月带上，把老师布置的题告诉她，看她能不能在家把作业补了。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”<br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑桑点头答应了，但桑桑不愿一个人去，就拉了阿恕一起去。可是走到半路上，遇到了阿恕的母亲，硬把阿恕留下了，说她家的那趟鸭子不知游到什么地方去了，让阿恕去找鸭子。桑桑犹豫了一阵，就只好独自一人往板仓走。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑桑想象着纸月生病的样子。但天空飞过一群鸽子，他就仰脸去望。他把那群鸽子一只一只地数了。他见了人家的鸽群，总要数一数。若发现人家的鸽群大于他的鸽群，他就有些小小的嫉妒，若发现人家的鸽群小于他的鸽群，他就有些小小的得意。现在，头上的这个鸽群是小于他的鸽群的，他就笑了，并且蹦起来，去够头上的树枝，结果把纸月的作业本震落了一地。他只好蹲下来收拾作业本，并把作业本上的灰擦在裤子上。鸽群还在他头上飞，他沉浸在得意感里，早把纸月忘了。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　离板仓大约一里地，有条大河。大河边上有一大片树林，在林子深处，有一座古寺，叫浸月寺。鸽群早已消失了，桑桑一边走，一边想那座古寺。他和母亲一起来过这座古寺。桑桑想</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>我马上就要见到那座古寺了。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑桑走到了大河边，不一会，就见到了那片林子。不知为什么，桑桑并不想立即见到纸月。因为他不知道自己在见了纸月以后，会是什么样子。桑桑是个一与女孩子说话就会脸红的男孩。越走近板仓，他就越磨蹭起来。他走进了林子，他想看看浸月寺以后再说。有一条青石板的小道，弯弯曲曲地隐藏在林子间，把桑桑往林子深处引着。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　正在冬季里，石板小道两边，无论是枫树、白杨还是银杏，都赤条条的，风并不大，但林子还是呼呼呼地响着，渲染着冬季的萧条。几只寒鸦立在晃动的枝头，歪脸看着天空那轮冬季特有的太阳。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　浸月寺立在坡上。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑桑先听到浸月寺风铃的清音，随即就看到了它的一角。风铃声渐渐大起来。桑桑觉得这风铃声很神秘，很奇妙，也很好听。他想</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>如果有一种鸽哨，也能发出这种声音，从天空中飘过，这会怎样</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>?</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>桑桑的许多想法，最后都是要与他的那群鸽子汇合到一起去。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　拐了一道弯，浸月寺突然整个放在了桑桑的眼前。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　立在深院里的寺庙，四角翘翘，仿佛随时都要随风飞去。寺庙后面还是林子，有三两株高树，在它的背后露出枝条来。寺前是两株巨大的老槐，很少枝条，而偶尔剩下的几根，在风中轻轻摇动，显得十分苍劲。风略大一些，四角垂挂的风铃一起响起，丁丁当当，衬得四周更是寂静。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　独自一人来到寺前的桑桑，忽然觉得被一种肃穆与庄严压迫着，不禁打了一个寒噤，小小的身体收缩住，惶惶不安地望着，竟不敢再往前走了。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>往回走吧，去纸月家。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>桑桑对自己说。但他却并未往回走，反而往上走来了。这时，桑桑听到老槐树下传来了三弦的弹拨声。桑桑认得这种乐器。弹拨三弦的人，似乎很安静，三弦声始终不急躁，单纯得十分。在桑桑听来，这声音是单调的，并且是重复的。但桑桑又觉得它这清纯的、缓慢的声音是好听的，象秋天雨后，树枝上的雨滴落在池塘里那么好听。桑桑是油麻地小学文艺宣传队的胡琴手，桑桑多少懂得一点音乐。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　三弦声总是这么响着，仿佛在许多许多年前，它就响了，就这么响的，它还会永远响下去，就这么地响下去。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑桑终于怯怯地走到了寺院门口。他往里一看，见一个僧人正坐在老槐树下。那三弦正在他怀里似有似无地响着。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑桑知道，这就是父亲常常说起的慧思和尚。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　关于慧思和尚的身世，这一带人有多种说法。但桑桑的父亲却只相信一种</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>这个人从前是个教书先生，并且是一个很有学问的教书先生，后来也不知是什么原因，突然地出家当和尚了。父亲实际并无充足的理由，只是在见过慧思和尚几次之后，从他的一手很好的毛笔字上，从他的一口风雅言辞上，从他的文质彬彬且又带了几分洒脱的举止上，便认定了许多种说法中的这一种。父亲后来也曾怀疑过他是一个念书已念得很高的学生。是先生也好，是学生也罢，反正，慧思和尚不是乡野之人。慧思和尚显然出生于江南，因为只有江南人，才有那副清秀之相。慧思和尚是一九四八年来浸月寺的。据当时的人讲，慧思那时还不足二十岁，头发黑如鸦羽，面白得有点像个女孩子，让一些乡下人觉得可惜。后来，这里的和尚老死的老死了，走的走了，就只剩他一个独自守着这座也不知是建于哪年的古寺。因为时尚的变迁与政府的限制，浸月寺实际上已很早就不再像从前那样香烟缭绕了，各种佛事也基本上停止。浸月寺终年清静。不知是什么原因，慧思和尚却一直留了下来。这或许是因为他已无处可去，古寺就成了他的家。他坚持着没有还俗，在空寂的岁月中，依然做他的和尚。他象从前一样，一年四季穿着棕色</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>*</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>的僧袍。他偶尔出现在田野上，出现在小镇上，这倒给平淡无奇的乡野增添了一道风景。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　老槐树下的慧思和尚感觉到有人站在院门口，就抬起头来。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　就在这一刹那间，桑桑看到了一双深邃的目光。尽管这种目光里含着一种慈和，但桑桑却像被一股凉风吹着了似的，微微震颤了一下。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　慧思和尚轻轻放下三弦，用双手捏住僧袍，然后站起来，轻轻一松手，那僧袍就像一道幕布滑落了下去。他用手又轻轻拂了几下僧袍，低头向桑桑作了一个揖，便走了过来。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑桑不敢看慧思和尚的脸，目光平视。由于个头的差异，桑桑的目光里，是两只摆动的宽大的袖子。那袖子是宽宽地卷起的，露出雪白的里子。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>小施主，请进。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”<br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑桑壮大了胆抬起头来。他眼前是副充满清爽、文静之气的面孔。桑桑长这么大，还从未见过这样的面孔。他朝慧思和尚笑了笑，但他不知道他这么笑究竟是什么意思，只是觉得自己应该这么笑一笑。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　慧思和尚微微弯腰，做了一个很恭敬的让桑桑进入僧院的动作。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑桑有点不自然。因为，谁也没有对他这样一个几年前还拖着鼻涕的孩子如此庄重过。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑桑束手束脚地走进了僧院。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　慧思和尚闪在一侧，略微靠前一点引导着桑桑往前走。他问桑桑</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>小施主，有什么事吗</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>?”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑桑随口说</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>来玩玩。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>但他马上觉得自己的回答很荒唐。因为，这儿不是小孩玩的地方。他的脸一下胀红起来。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　然而，慧思和尚并没有对他说</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>这不是玩的地方</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>，只是很亲切地</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>噢，噢</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>……”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>仍在微微靠前的位置上引导着桑桑。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑桑不好再退回去，索性</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>*</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>硬着头皮往前走。他走到了殿门。里面黑沉沉的。桑桑第一眼看里面时，并没有看到具体的形象，只觉得黑暗里泛着金光。他站在高高的门槛外面，不一会就看清了那尊莲座上的佛像。佛的神态庄严却很慈祥。佛的上方，是一个金色</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>*</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>的宵顶，于是佛像又显得异常的华贵了。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑桑仰望佛像时，不知为什么，心里忽然有点惧怕起来，便不由自主地往后退了几步，随即转身就要往院外走。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　慧思和尚连忙跟了出来。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　在桑桑走出院门时，慧思和尚问了一句</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>小施主从哪儿来</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>?”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑桑答道</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>从油麻地。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　慧思和尚又问道</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>小施主，往哪儿去</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>?”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑桑答道</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>去板仓。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>板仓</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>?”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑桑点点头</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>我去板仓找纸月。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>纸月</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>?”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>我的同学纸月。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>你是桑桑</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>?”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑桑很吃惊</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>你怎么知道我是桑桑</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>?”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　慧思和尚顿了一下，然后一笑道</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>听人说起过，桑校长的公子叫桑桑。你说你是从油麻地来的，我想，你莫不就是桑桑。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑桑沿着青石板小道，往回走去。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　慧思和尚竟然一定要送桑桑。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑桑无法拒绝。桑桑也不知道如何拒绝，就呆头呆脑地让慧思和尚一直将他送到大河边。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>慢走了。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>慧思和尚说。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑桑转过身来看着慧思和尚。当时，太阳正照着大河，河水反射着明亮的阳光，把站在河边草地上的慧思和尚的脸照得非常清晰。慧思和尚也正望着他，朝他微笑。桑桑望着慧思和尚的脸，凭他一个孩子的感觉，他突然无端地觉得，他的眼睛似乎像另外一个人的眼睛，反过来说，有另外一个人的眼睛，似乎像慧思和尚的眼睛。但桑桑却想不出这另外一个人是谁，一脸的困惑。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　慧思和尚说</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>小施主，过了河，就是板仓了，上路吧。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑桑这才将疑惑的目光收住，朝慧思和尚摆摆手，与他告别。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑桑走出去一大段路以后，又回过头来看。他看到慧思和尚还站在河边的草地上。有大风从河上吹来</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　他的僧袍被风所卷动，像空中飘动的云一样。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　五纸月病好之后，又像往常一样上学回家。但这样过了两个星期之后，不知道是什么原因，纸月几乎每天上学迟到。有时，上午的第一节课都快结束了，她才气喘吁吁地赶到教室门口，举着手喊</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>报告</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>。开始几回，蒋一轮也没有觉得什么，只是说</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>进。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>这样的情况又发生了几次之后，蒋一轮有点生气了</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>纸月，你是怎么搞的</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>?</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>怎么天天迟到</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>?”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　纸月就把头垂了下来。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>以后注意。到座位上去吧</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>!”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>蒋一轮说。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　纸月依然垂着头。纸月坐下之后，就一直垂着头。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　有一回，桑桑偶然瞥了纸月一眼，只见有一串泪珠从纸月的脸上，无声地滚落了下来，滴在了课本上。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　这一天，桑桑起了个大早，对母亲说是有一只鸽子昨晚未能归巢，怕是被鹰打伤了翅膀，他得到田野上去找一找，就跑出了家门。桑桑一出家门就直奔板仓。桑桑想暗暗地搞清楚纸月到底是怎么了。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑桑赶到大河边时，太阳刚刚出来，河上的雾气正在飘散。河上有一只渡船，两头都拴着绳子，分别连结着两岸。桑桑拉着绳子，将船拽到岸边，然后爬上船去，又去拉船那一头的绳子，不一会就到了对岸。桑桑上了岸，爬上大堤，这时，他看到了通往板仓的那条土路。他在大堤上的一棵大树下坐了下来，悄悄地等待着纸月走出板仓。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　当太阳升高了一截，大河上已无一丝雾气时，桑桑没有看到纸月，却看到土路上出现了三个男孩。他们在土路上晃荡着，没有走开的意思，好像在等一个人。桑桑不知道，这三个男孩都是板仓小学的学生。其中一个，是板仓校园内有名的恶少，名叫刘一水，外号叫</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>豁嘴大茶壶</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>。其他两个，是豁嘴大茶壶的跟屁虫，一个叫周德发，另一个叫吴天衡。桑桑更不知道，他们三个人呆在路上是等待纸月走过来的。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　过不一会，桑桑看到板仓村的村口，出现了纸月。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　纸月迟迟疑疑地走过来了。她显然已经看到了刘一水。有一小阵，纸月站在那儿不走了。但她看了看东边的太阳，还是走过来了。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　刘一水直挺挺地横躺在路上，其他两个则坐在路边。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑桑已经看出来了，他们要在这里欺负纸月。桑桑听父亲说过</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>(</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>父亲是听板仓小学的一位老师说的</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>)</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>，板仓小学有人专门爱欺负纸月，其中为首的一个叫</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>豁嘴大茶壶</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>。板仓小学曾几次想管束他们，但都没有什么效果，因为</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>豁嘴大茶壶</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>是个无法无天的恶少。桑桑想</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>这大概就是豁嘴大茶壶他们。桑桑才看到这儿，就已经明白纸月为什么总是天天迟到了。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　纸月离刘一水们已经很近了。她又站了一阵，然后跳进了路边的麦地。她要避开刘一水们。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　刘一水们并不去追纸月，因为，在他们看来，纸月实际上是很难摆脱他们的。他们看见纸月在坑坑洼洼的麦地里走着，就咯咯咯地笑。笑了一阵，就一起扯着嗓子喊</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　呀呀呀，呀呀呀，</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　脚趾缝里漏出一小丫，</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　没人搀，没人架，</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　刚一撩腿就跌了个大趴叉。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　这小丫，找不到家，</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　抹着眼泪胡哇哇</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>……<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　他们一面叫，一面劈劈啪啪地拍抓着屁股来作伴奏。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　纸月现在只惦记着赶紧上学，不理会他们，斜穿麦地，往大堤上跑。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　刘一水们眼见着纸月就要上大堤了，这才站起来也往大堤上跑去。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑桑不能再在一旁看着了，他朝纸月大声叫道</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>纸月，往我这儿跑</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>!</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>往我这儿跑</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>!”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　纸月在麦地里站住了，望着大堤上的桑桑。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑桑叫着</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>你快跑呀，你快跑呀</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>!”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　纸月这才朝大堤上跑过来。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　在纸月朝大堤上跑过来时，桑桑一手抓了一块半截砖头，朝那边正跑过来的刘一水们走过去。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　纸月爬上了大堤。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑桑回头说了一声</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>你快点过河去</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>，继续走向刘一水们。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　纸月站在那儿没有动。她呆呆地望着桑桑的背影，担忧而恐惧地等待着将要发生的殴斗。她想叫桑桑别再往前走了。但她没有叫。因为她知道，桑桑是不肯回头的。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑桑心里其实是害怕的。他不是板仓的人，他面对着的又是三个看上去都要比他大比他壮实的男孩。但桑桑很愿意当着纸月的面，好好地与人打一架。他在心里颤栗地叫喊着</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>你们来吧</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>!</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>你们来吧</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>!”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>两条细腿却如寒风中的枝条，索索地抖。他甚至想先放下手中的砖头，到大树背后撒泡尿，因为，他感觉到他的裤子已经有点潮湿了。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>桑桑</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>……”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>纸月终于叫道。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑桑没有回头，一手抓着一块半截砖头，站在那儿，等着刘一水他们过来。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　刘一水先跑过来了，望着桑桑问</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>你是谁</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>?”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>我是桑桑</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>!”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>桑桑是什么东西</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>?”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>刘一水说完，扭过头来朝周德发和吴天衡笑着。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑桑把两块砖头抓得紧紧的，然后说</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:‘</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>你们再往前走一步，我就砸了</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>!”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　刘一水说</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>你砸不准。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑桑说</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>我砸得准。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>他吹起牛来，</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>我想砸你的左眼，就绝不会砸到你的右眼上去。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>但他随即觉得现在吹这一个牛很可笑，就把腿叉开，摆出一副严阵以待的架势。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　刘一水们互相搂着肩，根本就不把桑桑放在眼里，摆成一条线，大摇大摆地走过来了。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑桑举起了砖头，并侧过身子，作出随时投掷的样子。刘一水们不知是因为害怕桑桑真的会用砖头砸中他们，还是因为被桑桑的那副凶样吓唬住了，便暂时停了下来。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　而这时，桑桑反而慢慢地往后退去。他在心里盘算着</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>当纸月登上渡船的一刹那间，他将砖头猛烈地投掷出去，然后也立即跳上渡船，将这一头的绳子解掉，赶紧将渡船拉向对岸。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　纸月似乎明白了桑桑的意图，就往大堤下跑，直奔渡船。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑桑就这么抓着砖头，一边瞪着刘一水们，一边往后退着。刘一水们还真的不敢轻举妄动，只是在一定的距离内，一步一步地逼过来。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑桑掉头看了一眼。当他看到纸月马上就要跑到水边时，他突然朝前冲去，吓得刘一水们掉头往后逃窜。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　而桑桑却在冲出去几步之后，掉头往大堤下冲去。桑桑一边冲，一边很为他的这一点点狡猾得意。刘一水们终于站住，转身反扑过来。桑桑朝纸月大声叫着</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>快上船</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>!</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>快上船</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>!”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>纸月连忙上了船桑桑已退到水边。当他看到刘一水们已追到跟前时，心里说</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>我不怕砸破了你们的头</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>!”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>猛地将一块砖头投掷出去。然而用力过猛，那砖头竟落到刘一水们身后去了。不过倒也把刘一水们吓了一跳。这时，桑桑趁机跳上了船。当桑桑看到刘一水们正要去抓拴在大树上的绳子时，就又将手中的另一块砖头也投掷了出去。这回砸到了吴天衡的脚上，疼得他瘫在地上</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>哎哟哎哟</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>地叫唤。但就在桑桑要去解绳子时，刘一水却已抓住了绳子，把正被纸月拉向对岸的船，又拉了回去。绳子系得太死，桑桑费了很大的劲，才将它解开，而这时，船已几乎靠岸了。刘一水飞跑过来，不顾桑桑的阻拦，一步跳到了船上。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　纸月用力地将船向对岸拉去。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　刘一水朝纸月扑过来，想从纸月手里摘掉绳子。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑桑双手抱住了刘一水的腰，两人在船舱里打了起来。桑桑根本不是刘一水的对手，勉强纠缠了一阵，就被刘一水打翻在船舱，让刘一水骑在了胯下。刘一水擦了一把汗，望着桑桑</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>从哪儿冒出来个桑桑</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>!”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>说完，就给了桑桑一拳。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑桑觉得自己的鼻梁一阵锐利的酸疼，随即，鼻孔就流出血来。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑桑看到了一个野蛮的面孔。他想给刘一水重重一击，但他根本无法动弹。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　刘一水又给了桑桑几拳。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　纸月放下了绳子，哭着</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>你别再打他了，你别再打他了</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>……”<br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　刘一水眼看渡船已离岸很远，将桑桑扔下了，然后跑到船头上，趴下来卷起袖子，用手将船往回划着。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑桑躺在舱底动也不动地仰望着冬天的天空。他从未在这样一个奇特的角度看过天空。在这样的角度所看到的天空，显得格外的高阔。他想</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>如果这时，他的鸽子在天空飞翔，一定会非常好看的。河上有风，船在晃动，桑桑的天空也在晃动。桑桑有一种说不出来的晕眩感。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　纸月坐在船头上，任刘一水将船往回拉去。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑桑看到了一朵急急飘去的白云，这朵白云使桑桑忽然有了一种紧张。他慢慢爬起来，然后朝刘一水爬过去。当渡船离岸还有十几米远时，桑桑突然一头撞过去。随即，他和纸月都听到了扑通一声。他趴在船帮上，兴奋地看着一团水花。过不一会，刘一水从水中挣扎到水面上。桑桑站起来，用手擦着鼻孔下的两道血流，俯视着在冬天河水中艰难游动着的刘一水。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　纸月将船朝对岸拉去。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　当刘一水游回岸边，因为寒冷而在岸边哆哆嗦嗦地不住地跳动时，桑桑和纸月也已站在了河这边柔软的草地上。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　六刘一水跑回家换了衣裳，快近中午时，就觉得浑身发冷，乌了的嘴唇直打颤，放学后勉强回到家中。刘一水着凉生病了。刘一水的家长就闹到了油麻地小学，就闹到了桑乔家。这么一闹，就把事情闹大了，事情一闹大了，事情也就好收拾了。到处都有桑乔的学生。桑乔赔了礼之后，联合了板仓小学，甚至联合了地方政府，一起出面，将刘一水等几个孩子连同他们的家长找到一起，发出严重警告</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>假如日后再有一丝欺负纸月的行为，学校与地方政府都将对刘一水们以及刘一水等人的家长们给予老实不客气的制裁。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　这天，桑乔对纸月说，</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>纸月，板仓那边，已没有人再敢欺负你了，你还是回那边读书吧。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　纸月低着头，不吭声。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>你跟你外婆好好商量一下。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　纸月点点头，回教室去了。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑桑的母亲说</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>就让她在这儿念书吧。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑乔说</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>这没有问题，就怕这孩子跑坏了身体。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　那一天，纸月坐在课堂上，没有一点心思听课，目光空空的。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　第二天一早，纸月和外婆就出现在桑桑家门口。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　外婆对桑乔说</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>她只想在油麻地读书。你就再收留她吧。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑乔望着纸月</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>你想好了</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>?”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　纸月不说话，只是点点头。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　在一旁喂鸽子的桑桑，就一直静静地听着。等外婆与纸月走后，他将他的鸽子全都轰上了天空，鸽子们飞得高兴时，劈劈啪啪地击打双翅，仿佛满空里都响着一片清脆的掌声。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　一切，一如往常。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　但不久，桑桑感觉到有几个孩子，在用异样的目光看他，看纸月。并且，他们越来越放肆了。比如，上体育课，当他正好与纸月分在一个小组时，以朱小鼓为首的那帮家伙，就会莫名其妙地</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>嗷</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>地叫一声。恼羞的桑桑，已经揪住一个孩子的衣领，把他拖到屋后的竹林里给了一拳了。但桑桑的反应，更刺激了朱小鼓们。他们并无恶意，但一个个都觉得这种哄闹实在太来劲了。他们中间甚至有桑桑最要好的朋友。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑桑这种孩子，从小就注定了要成为别人哄闹的对象。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　这天下午是作文课。桑桑的作文一直是被蒋一轮夸奖的。而上一回做的一篇作文，尤其做得好，整篇文章差不多全被蒋一轮圈杠了。这堂作文课的第一个节目就是让桑桑朗读他的作文。这是事先说好了的。上课铃一响，蒋一轮走上讲台，说</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>今天，我们请桑桑同学朗读他的作文《我们去麦地里》。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　但桑桑却在满头大汗地翻书包</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>他的作文本不见了。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　蒋一轮说</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>别着急，慢慢找。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　慢慢找也找不到。桑桑失望了，站在那儿抓耳挠腮。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　蒋一轮朝桑桑咂了一下嘴，问道</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>谁看到桑桑的作文本了</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>?”<br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　大家就立即去看自己的桌肚、翻自己的书包。不一会，就相继有人说</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>我这儿没有。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>我这儿没有。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　而当纸月将书包里的东西都取出来查看时，脸一下红了</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>在她的作文本下，压着桑桑的作文本。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　有一两个孩子一眼看到了桑桑的作文本，就把目光停在了纸月的脸上。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　纸月只好将桑桑的作文本从她的作文本下抽出，然后站起来</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>报告，桑桑的作文本在我这儿。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>她拿着作文本，朝讲台上走去。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　朱小鼓领头，</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>嗷</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>地叫了一声，随即，几乎是全教室的孩子，都跟着</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>瞰</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>起来。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　蒋一轮用黑板擦一拍讲台</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>安静</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>!”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　蒋一轮接过纸月手中的桑桑的作文本，然后又送到桑桑手上。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑桑开始读他自己的作文，但读得结结巴巴，仿佛那作文不是他写的，而是抄的别人的。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　写得蛮好的一篇作文，经桑桑这么吭哧吭哧地一读，谁也觉不出好来，课堂秩序乱糟糟的。蒋一轮皱着眉头，硬是坚持着听桑桑把他的作文读完。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　放学后，朱小鼓看到了桑桑，朝他诡秘地一笑。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑桑不理他，蹲了下来，装着系鞋带，眼睛却膘着朱小鼓。当他看到朱小鼓走到池塘边上去打算撅下一根树枝抓在手中玩耍时，他突然站起来。冲了过去，双手一推，将朱小鼓推了下去。这池塘刚出了藕，水倒是没有，但全是稀泥。朱小鼓是一头栽下去的。等他将脑袋从烂泥里拔出来时，除了两只眼睛闪闪发亮，其余地方，全都被烂泥糊住了。他恼了，顺手抓了两把烂泥爬了上来。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑桑没有逃跑。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　朱小鼓跑过来，把两把烂泥都砸在了桑桑的身上。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑桑放下书包，纵身一跳，进了烂泥塘，也抓了两把烂泥，就在塘里，直接把烂泥砸到了朱小鼓身上。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　朱小鼓在脸上抹去一把泥，也跳进烂泥塘里。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　孩子们闪在一边，无比兴奋地看着这场泥糊大战。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　纸月站在教室里，从门缝里悄悄向外看着。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　不一会工夫，桑桑与朱小鼓身上就再也找不出一块干净地方了。老师们一边大声制止着，却又一边看着这两个</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>泥猴</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>克制不住地笑着。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　孩子们无所谓站在哪一边，只是不住地拍着巴掌。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　蒋一轮终于板下脸来</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>桑桑，朱小鼓，你们立即给我停住</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>!”<br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　两人也没有什么力气了，勉强又互相砸了几把烂泥，就弯下腰去，在烂泥塘里到处找自己的被烂泥拔了去的鞋袜。孩子们就过来看，并指定烂泥塘的某一个位置叫道</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>在那边</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>!</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>在那边</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>!”<br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑桑爬上来时，偶然朝教室看了一眼。他看到了藏在门后的纸月的眼睛。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　两天后，天下起了入冬以来最大的一场大雪。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　教室后面的竹林深处，躲避风雪的一群麻雀，卿卿喳喳地叫着，闹得孩子们都听不清老师讲课。仅仅是一堂课的时间，再打开教室门时，门口就已堆积了足有一尺深的雪。到了傍晚放学时，一块一块的麦地，都已被大雪厚厚覆盖，田埂消失了，眼前只是一个平坦无边的大雪原。然而，大雪还在稠密生猛地下着。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　孩子们艰难地走出了校园，然后像一颗颗黑点，散落雪野上。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑桑的母亲站在院门口，在等纸月。中午时，她就已与纸月说好了，让她今天不要回家，放了学就直接来这儿。当她看到校园里已剩下不多的孩子时，便朝教室走来。路上遇到了桑桑，问</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>纸月呢</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>?”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>桑桑指着很远处的一个似有似无的黑点</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>她回家了。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>你没有留她</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>?”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑桑站在那儿不动，朝大雪中那个向前慢慢蠕动的黑点看着</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>——</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>整个雪野上，就那么一个黑点。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑桑的母亲在桑桑的后脑勺上打了一巴掌</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>你八成是欺负她了。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑桑突然哭起来</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>我没有欺负她，我没有欺负她</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>……”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>扭头往家走去。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑桑的母亲跟着桑桑走进院子</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>你没有欺负她，她怎么走了</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>?”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑桑一边抹眼泪，一边跺着脚，向母亲大叫</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>我没有欺负她</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>!</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>我没有欺负她</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>!</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>我哪儿欺负她了</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>?</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>！</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>………”<br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　他抓了两团雪，将它们檬结实，然后，直奔鸽笼，狠狠地向那些正缩着脖子歇在屋檐下的鸽子们砸去鸽子们被突如其来的攻击惊呆了，愣了一下，随即慌张地飞起。有几只钻进笼里的，将脑袋伸出来看了看，没有立即起飞。桑桑一见，又檬了两个雪球砸过去。鸽笼</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>咚</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>一声巨响，惊得最后几只企图不飞的鸽子，也只好飞进风雪里。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　鸽子们在天空中吃力地飞着。它们不肯远飞，就在草房子的上空盘旋，总有要立即落下来的心思。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑桑却见着什么抓什么，只顾往空中乱砸乱抡，绝不让它们落下。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　鸽子们见这儿实在落不下来，就落到了其它草房顶上。这使桑桑更恼火。他立即跑出院子，去追着砸那些企图落在其它草房顶上的鸽子。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　母亲看着跑得上气不接下气的桑桑</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>你疯啦</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>?”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑桑头一歪</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>我没有欺负她</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>!</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>我没有欺负她嘛</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>!”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>说着，用手背猛地抹了一把眼泪。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>那你就砸鸽子</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>!”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>我愿意砸</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>!</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>我愿意砸</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>!”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>他操了一根竹竿，使劲地朝空中飞翔的鸽子挥舞不止，嘴里却在不住地说，</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>我没有欺负她嘛</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>!</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>我没有欺负她嘛</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>!……”<br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　鸽子们终于知道它们在短时间内，在草房子上是落不下来了，只好冒着风雪朝远处飞去。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑桑站在那儿，看着它们渐渐远去，与雪混成一色</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>*</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>，直到再也无法区别。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑桑再往前看，朦胧的泪眼里，那个黑点已完全地消失在了黄昏时分的风雪里</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>……</span></p>

        <h2 style='margin-left:56.25pt;text-indent:-56.25pt'><span lang=EN-US>第三章<span
                    style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span
                style='font-family:宋体'>白雀（一）</span></h2>

        <p class=MsoNormal><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>一差不多每个地方上的文艺宣传队，都是由这个地方上的学校提供剧本并负责排练的。桑乔既是油麻地学校文艺宣传队的导演，也是油麻地地方文艺宣传队的导演</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑乔的导演不入流，但却很有情趣。他不会去自己做动作，然后让人学着做。因为他的动作总不能做到位，他嘴里对人说</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>瞧着我，右手这么高高地举起来。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>但实际上他的右手却并未高高地举起来，倒象被鹰击断了的鸡翅膀那么聋拉着。人家依样画葫芦，照他的样做了，他就生气。可人家说：</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>你就是这个样子。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>于是，桑乔就知道了，他不能给人做样子。这样一来，他倒走了大家的路子：不动手动脚，而是坐在椅子上或倚在墙上，通过说，让演员自己去体会，去找感觉。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑乔导演的戏，在这一带很有名气。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑乔既是一个名校长，又是一个名导演。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　农村文艺宣传队，几乎是常年活动的。农忙了，上头说要鼓劲，要有戏演到田头场头</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>;</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>农闲了，上头说，闲着没事，得有个戏看看，也好不容易有个工夫好好看看戏</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>;</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>过年过节了，上头说，要让大伙高高兴兴的，得有几场戏。任何一种情况，都是文艺宣传队活动的理由。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　油麻地地方文艺宣传队，在大多数情况之下，是与油麻地小学的文艺宣传队混合在一起的，排练的场所，一般都在油麻地小学的一幢草</span><span
                lang=EN-US><a href="http://www.xyyuedu.com/gushifl/ands/30247.html"><span lang=EN-US
                        style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#3C3B3B'><span
                            lang=EN-US>房子</span></span></a></span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:
宋体;color:#171414'>里。</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:
"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　排练是公开的，因此，实际上这地方上的人，在戏还没有正式演出之前，就早已把戏看过好几遍了。他们屋前屋后占了窗子，或者干脆挤到屋里，看得有滋有味。这时，他们看的不是戏，而是看的如何排戏。对他们来说看如何排戏，比看戏本身更有意思。一个演员台词背错了，只好退下去重来，这有意思。而连续上台三回，又同样退下去三回，这便更有意思。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　一场不拉看排练的是秦大奶奶。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　油麻地小学校园内，唯一一个与油麻地小学没有关系的住户，就是孤老婆子秦大奶奶。只要一有排练，她马上就能知道。知道了，马上就搬了张小凳拄着拐棍来看。她能从头至尾地看，看到深夜，不住地打纯了，也还坐在那儿老眼昏花地看。为看得明白一些，她还要坐到正面来。这时，她的小凳子，就会放到了离桑乔的藤椅不远的一块显著的地方。有人问她</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>称听明白了吗</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>?”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>她朝人笑笑，，然后说</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>听明白啦</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>他把一碗红烧肉全吃啦。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>要不就说</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>听明白啦</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>王三是个苦人，却找了一个体面媳妇。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>众人就乐，她也乐。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　今年的夏收夏种已经结束，油麻地地方文艺宣传队要很快拿出一台戏来，已在草</span><span
                lang=EN-US><a href="http://www.xyyuedu.com/gushifl/ands/30247.html"><span lang=EN-US
                        style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#3C3B3B'><span
                            lang=EN-US>房子</span></span></a></span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:
宋体;color:#171414'>里排练了好几日了，现在正在排练一出叫《红菱船》的小戏。女主角是十八岁的姑娘</span><span lang=EN-US><a
                    href="http://www.xyyuedu.com/mz/baomugouyinmou/37171.html"><span lang=EN-US
                        style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#3C3B3B'><span
                            lang=EN-US>白雀</span></span></a></span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　</span><span lang=EN-US><a
                    href="http://www.xyyuedu.com/mz/baomugouyinmou/37171.html"><span lang=EN-US
                        style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#3C3B3B'><span
                            lang=EN-US>白雀</span></span></a></span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:
宋体;color:#171414'>是油麻地的美人。油麻地一带的人说一个长得好看的女孩儿，常习惯用老戏里的话说是</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>美人</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　白雀在田野上走，总会把很多目光吸引过去。她就那么不显山不露水地走，但在人眼里，却有说不明白的耐看。她往那儿一站，象棵临风飘动着嫩叶的还未长成的梧桐树，亭亭玉立，依然还是很耐看。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　白雀还有一副好嗓子。不宏亮，不宽阔，但银子样清脆。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑乔坐在椅子上，把双手垂挂在扶手上，给白雀描绘着</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>一条河，河水很亮，一条小木船，装了一船红菱，那红菱一颗一颗的都很鲜艳，惹得人都想看一眼</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>;</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>一个姑娘，就像你这样子的，撑着这只小船往前走，往前走，船头就听见击水声，就看见船头两旁不住地开着水花</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>;</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>这个姑娘无心看红菱一一红菱是自家的，常看，不稀罕，她喜欢看的是水上的、两岸的、天空的好风景</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>;</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>前面是一群鸭，船走近了，才知道，那不是一群鸭，而是一群鹅</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>;</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>芦苇开花了，几只黄雀站在芦花顶上叫喳</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>P</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>查，一个摸鱼的孩子用手一拨芦苇，露出了脸，黄雀飞上了天</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>;</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>水码头上站着一个红衣绿裤的小媳妇，眯着对眼睛看你的船，说菱角也真红，姑娘也真白，姑娘你就把头低下去看你的红菱</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>;</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>看红菱不要紧，小木船撞了正开过来的大帆船，小船差点翻了，姑娘你差点跌到了河里，你想骂人家船主，可是没有道理，只好在心里骂自己</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>;</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>姑娘一时没心思再撑船，任由小船在水上漂</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>;</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>漂出去一二里，河水忽然变宽了，浩浩荡荡的，姑娘你心慌了，姑娘你脸红了一一你想要到的那个小镇，就立在前边不远的水边上</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>;</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>一色</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>*</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>的青砖，一色</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>*</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>的青瓦，好一个小镇子，姑娘你见到小镇时，已是中午时分，小镇上，家家烟囱冒了烟，烟飘到了水面上，像飘了薄薄的纱</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>;</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>你不想再让小船走了，你怕听到大柳树下笛子声一一大柳树下，总有个俊俏后生在吹笛子</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>……<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑乔的描绘，迷住了一屋子人。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　白雀的脸红了好几回，仿佛那船上的姑娘真的就是她。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　这出小戏，就只有一把笛子伴奏。吹笛子的是蒋一轮。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑桑最崇拜的一个人就是蒋一轮。蒋一轮长得好，笛子吹得好，篮球打得好，语文课讲得好</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>……</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>桑桑眼里的蒋一轮，是由无数个好加起来的一个完美无缺的人。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　蒋一轮长得很高，但高得不蠢，高得匀称、恰当。油麻地不是没有高个，但不是高得撑不住，老早就把背驼了，就是上身太长，要不又是两条腿太长，像立在水里的灰鹤似的。蒋一轮只让人觉得高得好看。蒋一轮的头发被他很耐心地照料着，一年四季油亮亮的，分头，但无一丝油腔滑调感，无一丝阔小开的味道，很分明的一道线，露出青白的头皮，加上鼻梁上架了一副眼镜，就把一股挡不住的文气透给人。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　蒋一轮的笛子能迷倒一片人。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　蒋一轮的笛子装在一只终年雪白的布套里。他取出笛子时，总是很有章法地将布套折好放到口袋里，绝不随便一团巴塞到裤兜里。在蒋一轮看来，，笛子是个人，那个布套就是这个人的外衣。一个人的外衣是可以随便团巴团巴乱塞一处的吗</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>?</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>蒋一轮在吹笛子之前，总要习惯地用修长的手指在笛子上轻轻抚摸几下，样子很像一个人在抚摸他所宠爱的一只猫或一条小狗。笛子横在嘴边时，是水平的。蒋一轮说，笛子吹得讲究不讲究，第一眼就看笛子横得水平不水平。蒋一轮的笛子横着时，上面放个水平尺去测试，水平尺上那个亮晶晶的水珠肯定不偏不倚地在当中。蒋一轮吹笛子从来不坐下来吹。这或许是因为蒋一轮觉得坐下来，会把他那么一个高个儿白白地浪费了。但蒋一轮说</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:‘</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>笛子这种乐器，就只能站着去吹。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>最潇洒时，是他随便倚在一棵树上或倚在随便一个什么东西上。那时，他的双腿是微微交叉的。这是最迷人的样子。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑桑每逢看见蒋一轮这副样子，便恨胡琴这种乐器只能一屁股瘫在椅子上拉。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　《红菱船》的曲子就是蒋一轮根据笛子这种乐器的特性</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>*</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>，自己作的，蒋一轮自然吹得得心应手。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑乔将《红菱船》已导演出来了点样子之后，就对蒋一轮与白雀说</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>差不多了，你们两个另找个地方，再去单练吧。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”<br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　二晚上，桑桑在花园里循声捉蟋蟀，就听见荷塘边的草地上有笛子声，隔水看，白雀正在笛子声里做动作。今晚的月亮不耀眼，一副迷离恍惚的神气。桑桑看不清蒋一轮与白雀，但又分明看得清他们的影子。蒋一轮倚在柳树上，用的是让桑桑最着迷的姿势</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>两腿微微交叉着。白雀的动作在这样的月光笼罩下，显得格外的柔和。桑桑坐在塘边，呆呆地看着，捉住的几只蟋蟀从盒子里趁机逃跑了。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　微风翻卷着荷叶，又把清香吹得四处飘散。几支尚未绽开的荷花立在月色</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>*</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>下像几支硕大的毛笔，黑黑地竖着。桑桑能够感觉到</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>它们正在一点一点地开放。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　夜色</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>*</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>下的笛子声不太像白天的笛子声，少了许多明亮和活跃，却多了些忧伤与神秘。夜越深越是这样。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　路过塘边的人，都要站住听一会，看一会。听一会，看一会，又走了。但桑桑却总在听，总在看。桑桑在想</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>有什么样的戏，只是在月光下演呢</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>?<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　不知是哪个促狭鬼，向池塘里投掷了一块土疙瘩，发一声</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>咚</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>的水响，把蒋一轮的笛音惊住了，把白雀的动作也惊住了。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑桑在心里朝那个投掷土疙瘩的人骂了一声</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>讨厌</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>!”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>但笛音又响起来了，动作也重新开始。如梦如幻。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　过了一个星期，彩排结束后，桑乔说</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>《红菱船》怕是今年最好的一出戏了。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”<br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　演出是在一个晴朗无风的夜晚。演出的消息几天前就已传出去了，来看演出的人很多。舞台就设在油麻地小学的操场上。在通往油麻地小学操场的各条路上，天未黑，人便一缕一缕地往这边走了。老头老太太，大多扛了张板凳，而孩子们心想</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>操场四周都是树，到时爬树上看吧。因此，他们大多就空了手，轻松地跑着，跳着，叫着。油麻地小学文艺宣传队与油麻地地方文艺队的演出水平，是这一带最好的，因此，来看演出的绝非仅仅只有油麻地的人，差不多，引来了方圆十里地的人。油麻地一些人家估计一些住在远处的亲戚也要过来，就多扛了一些凳子。因此，离演出还早，场地上就已放了无数张凳子了，看上去挺壮观。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　化妆室就设在用做排练场的那幢草房子里。来得早的人，就围在窗口门口看化妆。桑乔手掌上涂满了各色</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>*</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>油彩。演员们就从他手下，一个个地过着。若是个过场的或不重要的，桑乔就三下两下地将他们打发过去。若是一个重要角色</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>*</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>，桑乔就很认真，妆化得差不多了，就让那个演员往后退几步，他歪头看看，叫演员凑上来，让他再作仔细修改，就像一个作文章的人，仔细地修改他的文章一样。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　乐队在门外已开始调音、试奏。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑乔化妆着化妆着，心里老觉得今天好像有点什么事情，偶尔抬头看了一眼，一下看到了心神不宁的蒋一轮，他突然明白了</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>白雀还没化妆呢。他问道</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>白雀呢？</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>白雀还没有来。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>有人一旁答道。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑乔在嘴里嘀咕了一声</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>怎么搞的</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>?</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>该来了。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>心想离演出还有些时间，就依然去给那些演员化妆。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　蒋一轮屋里屋外不安地转悠已经好一会了，看看手表，离演出时间已不远了，终于走到桑乔身边，轻声说道</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>桑校长，她还没有来。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑乔无心再去仔细化妆手里的一个演员，说声</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>行了</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>，就丢下那个演员，对一个叫</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>‘</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>泣酸子</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>的演员说</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>二酸子，你去她家找找她。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　二酸子上路了。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑乔追出来</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>快点。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>唉</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>!”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>二酸子穿过人群跑起来。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　演员、乐队以及围观的人，不一会就都知道了白雀未到，就把一句话互相重复着</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>白雀还没有来呢。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>又过不一会，这话就传到了操场上，认识不认识的都在说</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>白雀还没有来呢。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>觉得事情似乎挺重大，于是也就感到有点莫名其妙的兴奋。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　二酸子过不一会回来了，对桑乔说</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>白雀他父亲不让她来。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑乔问</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>为什么</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>?”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　二酸子不知为什么看了蒋一轮一眼，转而回答桑乔</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>不知道为什么。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　还有两三个演员没化妆，桑乔说</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>自己化妆吧。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>又对宣传队的具体负责人说</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>唯时演出，我去白雀家一趟。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>说完就走，一句话一半留在门里，一半留在门外</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>谁都可以不来，但白雀不能不来。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　两盏汽油灯打足了气，</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>璞璞璞</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>地燃烧着，一旦高悬，立即将舞台照得一片光明。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　演出准时进行。但台下的人一边看演出，一边就在下面互相问</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>白雀来了吗</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>?”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>台后的演员也在互相问</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>白雀来了吗</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>?”<br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑桑看到蒋一轮在吹笛子时，不时拿眼睛往通往操场的路上膘。好几回，蒋一轮差一点把曲子吹错了，幸亏是合奏，很用心的桑桑用胡琴将这些小漏洞一一补住了。桑桑看到，蒋一轮用感激和夸奖的目光看了他好几回。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　幕间，人们在空隙里几乎将询问变成了追问</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>白雀来了没有</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>?”<br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　又一个节目开始时，人们的注意力就集中不起来，场上的秩序不太好。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　演员们开始抱怨白雀</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>这个白雀，搞得演出要演不下去了。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　演了三个小节目，白雀还未到。人们从</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>白雀偶然疏忽了，忘了演出时间了</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>的一般想法上移开去，在问</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>白雀为什么没有来</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>?”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>都认为是有原因的，便开始了猜测，心思就老不在台上演出的节目上。仿佛他们今天来这里，不是来看演出的，而是来专门研究</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>白雀为什么没有来</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>这样一个问题的。当他们听说白雀是被她的父亲白三拦在了家中时，猜测就变得既漫无边际，又十分具体了。台下一片卿卿喳喳，想看节目的人也听不太分明了，注意力反而被那些有趣的猜测吸引了。因此，这时台上的演出，实际上已没有太大的意义</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　台前台后的演员都很着急</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>白雀怎么还不来呢</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>?”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　忽然有人大声说</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>白雀来了</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>!”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　先是孩子们差不多一起喊起来</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:‘</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>噢</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>——</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>白雀来了</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>——”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>大人们看也不看，就跟着喊。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　众人都去望路上，台上的演员和乐队也都停住了望路上</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>——</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>月光下的路，空空荡荡。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>哪儿有白雀</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>?”“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>没有白雀。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>谁胡说的</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>?”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>一场的人，去哪儿找那个胡说的人</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>!</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>众人只当穿插</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>*</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>进来了一个节目，这个节目让他们觉到了一阵小小的冲动。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　台上的演出继续进行。台下的人暂时先不去想白雀，勉勉强强地看着，倒有了一阵好秩序。演员们也就情绪高涨。那个男演员，亮开喉咙大声吼，吼得人心一阵激动。本是风吹得树叶响，但人却以为是那个男演员的声音震得树叶</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>沙沙</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>响。桑桑把胡琴拉得摇头晃脑，揉弦揉走了音。只有蒋一轮，还是心不在焉，笛子吹得结结巴巴，大失往日的风采。人也没有从前一吹笛子就一副得意忘形的样子，显得有点僵硬。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　一个女演员做着花样，一摇一晃，风吹杨柳似地走上台来。她一直走到了台口，让人觉得她马上就要走下台来了。下面一个动作，是她远眺大河上有一叶白帆飘过来。她身子向前微侧，突然说出一句</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>那不是白雀吗</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>?”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>神情就像说的是戏里头的一句台词。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　众人起先反应不过来，还盯着她的脸看。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　她踞起脚，用手往路上一指</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>白雀</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>!”<br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　众人立即站起来，扭头往路上看，只见路上袅袅娜娜地走过来一个年轻女子。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>是白雀</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>!”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>就是白雀</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>!”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　众人就看着白雀不慌不忙地走过来。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　白雀并不着急。人们隐隐约约地看到，她一路走，还一路不时地伸手抓一下路边的柳枝或蹲下来采支花什么的。人们不生气，倒觉得白雀也真是不一般。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　靠近路口，不知是谁疑惑地说了一声</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>是白雀吗</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>?”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　很多人跟着怀疑</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>是白雀吗</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>?”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　话立即传过来</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>是周家的二丫</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>!”<br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　于是众人大笑。因为周家的二丫，是个脑子有毛病的姑娘，一个</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>二百五</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　二丫走近了，明亮的灯光下，众人清清楚楚地看清了是二丫。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　二丫见那么多人朝她笑，很不好意思，又袅袅娜娜地走进了黑暗的树荫里。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　台上那个女演员满脸通红，低下头往后台走。再重上台来时，就一直不大好意思，动作做没做到家，唱也没唱到家，勉强对付着。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　台下有人忽然学她刚才的腔调</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>那不是白雀吗</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>?”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　众人大笑。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　女演员没唱完，羞得赶紧往后台跑，再也没有肯上台。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　台下的秩序从此变得更加糟不可言。很多人不想演了。桑桑和其它孩子、大人、乐手坐在台上很尴尬，不知道是撤下台来还是坚持着在台上。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　台下的人很奇怪</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>非想见到白雀不可。其实，他们中间的大部分人，并不认识白雀，更谈不上对白雀演戏的了解。只是无缘无故地觉得，一个叫白雀的演员没有来，不是件寻常的事情。而互相越是说着白雀，就越觉得今天他们之所以来看戏，实际上就是来看白雀的，而看不到白雀，也就等于没有看到戏。这种情绪慢慢地演变成了对演出单位的恼火</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>让我们来看戏，而你们的白雀又没有来，这不是讴人么</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>?</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>这不是让我们白跑一趟吗</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>?</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>又等了等，终于有了想闹点事的心思。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　演员们说</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>不要再演了。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　宣传队的负责人说</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>桑校长没回来。演不演，要得到他的同意。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>桑校长怎么到现在还不回来呢</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>?”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>有几个演员走到路口去望，但没有望见桑乔。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　台下终于有人叫</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>我们要看白雀</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>!”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　很多人跟着喊</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>我们要看白雀</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>!”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　这时演员们即使想演，实际上也很难演下去了。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　演员与乐队都撤到了后台。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　台下乱哄哄的像个集市。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　蒋一轮站在一棵梧桐树的黑影里，一脸沮丧。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑乔终于回来。演员们连忙将他围住，就听他说了一声</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>我真想将白三这厮一脚瑞进大粪坑里</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>!”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　三宣传队临时解散了。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　蒋一轮一连十多天也没见着白雀，一有空就到河边上吹笛子。白雀的家就在河那边的村子里。他想，白雀一定能听到他的笛子声。蒋一轮什么曲子也不吹，就吹《红菱船》，从头到尾地吹。吹的时候，直让桑桑觉得，白雀也在，并且正在出神地做那些优美的动作。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　对岸，有人站到河边来听蒋一轮吹笛子，但没有一个知道蒋一轮的心思，听了一阵，都说</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>畴老师吹笛子吹得好。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>听得很高兴，仿佛那笛子是为他们吹的。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　蒋一轮吹笛子时，桑桑就站在自家水码头上看。但桑桑一直就没有看到白雀的影子。白雀仿佛永远地消失了。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　蒋一轮不屈不挠地吹着。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　但白雀就是没有出来。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　这是个星期天，蒋一轮一清早就去了河边上。蒋一轮今天的笛子吹得比以往任何时候都好，一往情深，如泣如诉。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　秦大奶奶既不知道蒋一轮吹笛子的用意，又不懂得音乐。她只是觉得这个蒋老师笛子吹得真苦，就颤颤巍巍地端来一碗水</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>歇歇，喝口水再吹。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”<br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　蒋一轮很感谢秦大奶奶一一蒋一轮现在很容易感谢人，喝了水，重新给笛子换了张竹膜。继续吹下去。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　蒋一轮直吹得人厌烦了，就听对岸有人说</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>健个蒋老师，有劲没处使了。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”<br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　蒋一轮的笛音就象一堆将要燃尽的火，慢慢地矮下去。他朝对岸望望，垂着双手离开了。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑桑突然地看到白雀朝河边走来了。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　白雀还是那个样子，只是好像清瘦了一些。她一出现在桑桑的视野里，桑桑就觉得天地间忽然地亮了许多。白雀走着，依然还是那样轻盈的步伐。她用双手轻轻抓着被放到了胸前的那根又黑又长的辫子，一方头巾被村巷里的风吹得飞扬了起来。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑桑看到，白雀走到岸边时，眼睛朝刚才发出笛音的那棵谏树下看了一眼。当她看到了谏树下已空无人影时，她向对岸到处张望了一下。而当她终于还是没有看到人影时，不免露出怅然若失的样子。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　白雀显然想在岸边多呆一会。她作出要到河边洗一洗手的样子，沿着石阶走向水边。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑桑立即朝蒋一轮的宿舍跑。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　蒋一轮鞋也不脱，正和他的笛子一起躺在床上。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>蒋老师</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>!”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>桑桑，有事吗</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>?”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>你快起来</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>!”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>起来干吗</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>?”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>去河边</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>!”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>去河边干吗</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>?”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>她在河边上。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>谁在河边上</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>?”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>白雀</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>!”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　蒋一轮将身体侧过去，把脸冲着墙</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>小桑桑，你也敢和你的老师开玩笑</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>!”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>接着，用手一拍木床，学老戏里的腔调，大声道</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>大胆</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>!”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>白雀真的在河边上</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>!”<br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　蒋一轮又转过脸来，见桑桑一副认真着急的表情，就站了起来。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>过一会，她就会走掉的。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”<br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　蒋一轮慌忙朝河边走。但立即意识到这是在桑桑面前，就将两手插</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>*</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>进裤兜里，作出很随意的样子。这样子在向桑桑说</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>见不见白雀，无所谓的。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>但脚步却是被什么急急地召唤着，走得很快。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑桑跟在后边。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　但桑桑看到的情景是</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>白雀的背影一忽闪，就消失在巷口，而白雀的父亲白三却倒背着双手，把后背长久地顽梗地停在河边上。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　以后的日子里，蒋一轮有时还到河边吹笛子，但越吹越没有信心，后来干脆就不吹了。他把笛子随意地扔在床里，都没有将它放进白布套里。白布套也被皱皱巴巴地扔在一旁。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　蒋一轮的课讲得无精打采，蒋一轮的蓝球打得无精打采</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>……</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>蒋一轮的整个日子都无精打采。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　蒋一轮变得特别能睡觉，一睡就要永远睡过去似的。蒋一轮天一黑就上床睡觉。蒋一轮上课总是迟到。蒋一轮的眼泡因过度睡眠而虚肿，嗓子因过度睡眠而嘶哑。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　女教师刘娅对他说</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>蒋老师，你莫非病了</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>?”<br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　蒋一轮自己也怀疑自己病了，去镇上医院做了检查。结果是没有任何病。但蒋一轮就是振作不起精神，只想拥了被子，昏昏睡去。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　期中的一个星期，这一片的五所学校照例互相检查教学情况，这一天，轮到了油麻地小学。先是听课，各班情况都很好，只有蒋一轮的课，大家不太满意。蒋一轮的课显然没有好好准备，头绪混乱，差错不断。本来，这样的课都是早准备好了的。阅读课文花多长时间，提问题花多长时间，讲解花多长时间，都是经过反复计算的，就像是演奏一部曲子，从开始到结束，都是掐好了时间的。说上课，就缓缓进入，说下课，就在钟声马上要响起之际，正好告一段落，然后干脆利落地宣布</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>今天的课就上到这儿。下课</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>!”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>话音刚落，铃声随即响起。蒋一轮真糟糕，距离下课还有十分钟，就弹尽粮绝。好一阵，就呆呆地望着学生和听课的诸位同仁，竟然无话可说。更糟糕的是，他的手表没有好好上弦，现在停住不动了。蒋一轮不知道离下课时间到底还有多远。想讲新课，又怕刚开了个头，下课铃就响了。就想</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>算了，就再等一会吧。可是左等右等，下课铃就是不响。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　陪同外校老师坐在后面的桑乔，一直冰冷着脸。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　孩子们起先还勉强坐着。但坐不多一会，就坐不住了，身上像爬虱子，开始不由自主地扭动起来，并开始小声说话。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　荒唐的是，蒋一轮也不知道脑子里在想些什么，竟然说出这么一句话来</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:‘</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>请大家再耐心等一会，马上就要下课了。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”<br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　外校的一个年轻女教师憋不住笑了。这笑声虽然是被努力控制了的，但孩子们还是听到了，大家互相瞧瞧，也傻乎乎笑了起来。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　蒋一轮满脸通红，额上出来汗珠，这才想起复习旧课。可刚等他说完</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>我们把课文翻到上一课</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>时，钟声却十分有力地敲响了。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　中午，由油麻地小学招待外校老师一顿饭。吃饭时，桑乔笑脸陪着客人，但始终笑得不大自然。那时，他就在心中暗暗指望着下午的作业检查，可为他捞回一点面子来。这一项，始终是油麻地小学的强项，是其他任何一所学校都无法与之抗衡的。况且，前三天，桑乔还专门召开了全体教师会议，特地强调了一下作业的问题</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>作业就是人的脸，既然是脸就要干净，脸不干净要洗干净，作业做得糊里糊涂的，没什么客气的，撕了重来，一次不行，再撕一次，不怕把作业本全撕了，大不了再换个新本</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>;</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>当天的作业，必须当天批改，不得过夜</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>……</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>。开会之后，桑乔再在各教室门口巡视，就听见一片沙沙沙的撕纸声，像急雨暴打地里的玉米叶子，把桑乔自己都听得心惊肉跳。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　吃了饭，老师们打了一会扑克，就开始检查作业。情况确实蛮好，外校的老师们都说</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>油麻地小学，学生们做的作业，干净得让人不忍看。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”<br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　下午四点钟，外校教师们在做清点时，发现作业架上没有四年级的作文本，就对桑乔说</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>桑校长，还差四年级的作文本。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑乔对本校的一位老师说</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>去问问蒋老师，四年级的作文本放在哪儿了。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>蒋老师不在。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑乔说</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>他总在宿舍里批改作业，可能把作文本放在宿舍了，去宿舍看看。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”<br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　是集体宿舍，其他老师也有钥匙，就打开门来，东找西找的，在蒋一轮的床头找到了那攘作文本，看也不看，就立即将它们搬到了办公室。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　外校老师一打开作文本，互相对了个眼神，，然后对桑乔说</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>桑校长，你自己看一下吧。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”<br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑乔看了一本，又看了几本，然后一句话也没说。他所看到的作文本，字是写得一塌糊涂，其中一本，还洒上了水，字漫</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>i</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>得几乎看不清一个。最要命的是，蒋一轮已有两周没有批改作业了。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　这次互查，油麻地小学插</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>*</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>了一面黑旗。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑乔将外校教师送走后，在办公室暴跳如雷</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>健个蒋一轮，简直昏了头</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>!”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　蒋一轮等到天已黑透，才回学校。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑乔一直在自己的办公室等着，见蒋一轮回来了</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　走出办公室，给他留下一句话来</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>明天晚上，你在全体教师会上作检查。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>说完回家去了。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　蒋一轮作了检查之后，坐在桌前不知写什么，几乎一夜没睡觉。第二天早上，他见到了桑桑，很诡秘地将桑桑叫到树林里，将一封信交到桑桑手上</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:‘</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>桑桑，把这封信交给白雀。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑桑点点头。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>悄悄的。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>我知道。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>现在就去。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”<br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑桑把信揣到怀里。桑桑走出树林时，忽然觉得自己是电影里的地下工作者了。他有一种神秘感、神圣感，还外加一种让他战战兢兢的紧张感。他上路时，还探头探脑，四下张望了一下。这完全没有必要，因为周围根本无人，即便有人，谁会去注意他呢</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>?<br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　四在不到一周的时间里，桑桑就在蒋一轮与白雀之间传递了四封信，并即将促成一次幽会。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑桑对大人之间的事充满了好奇心。他好像一个爱东张西望的人，忽然看到了一道门缝。他渴望着能从这道门缝里看到大人的世界</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>—</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>一个不可思议的世界。他在蒋一轮与白雀之间来回穿梭时，经常沉浸在一种夸张的感觉里。当他走进深深而空寂的村巷，当他面对一条用两只眼睛紧紧盯住他的黄狗，当他在黑暗里迎面遇到几个人而装成一副游玩的样子时，他觉得他是一个机智绝顶、可以做成大事的孩子。他并不很了解蒋一轮与白雀之间的通信究竟是什么意思。但他很愿意为他们跑腿送信。因为他觉得他也介入了这个世界，成了这个世界的一部分。他有了一种拿了入场券，穿过熙熙攘攘的人群而提前进入了场内的优越与得意。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑桑甚至在那天看荷塘边上蒋一轮与白雀于月光下排练时，就已在心里觉得，蒋一轮和白雀应该在一起</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>——</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>他们才应该在一起呢</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>!<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　这天天黑之后，桑桑把一条木船摇到了河那边的一棵大树下。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　船上坐着蒋一轮。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　木船静静地停在岸边。没有月亮，只有风。风吹得两岸的芦苇乱晃，吹得水起波浪，一下一下子拍打着河岸。树上有鸟，偶然叫一声，知道是风的惊忧，又安静下来。村子里，偶然传来一阵呼鸡唤狗的声音。到处是一个意思</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>天已晚了，夜间的寂寞马上就要来了。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　蒋一轮也像桑桑一样，在体验着一种紧张。但他在桑桑面前还要必须做出一个老师的样子来。他要给桑桑一个平静的而不是激动的样子，并且还要给桑桑一个印象</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>他与白雀之间，是世上最美好，最纯洁的友谊。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑桑听到了脚步声，从船上站了起来。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　白雀来了，白雀没有一点慌张的样子，像是要去做一件大家都知道的事情。她上了船，然后坐了下来，把双腿垂挂在船舱里，与同样姿态的蒋一轮正好面对面。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑桑摇着船，船在夜色</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>*</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>下往前行。桑桑像所有水乡的小孩一样，八九岁时就能撑小船，而到十几岁时，就能摇楷，把一个较大的船运行起来。水乡的水面上，常见一个与船极不等称的孩子摇楷。那孩子埋着屁股，一仰一合，居然把楷摇出很大的水花来。要是在白天，桑桑会很得意地向两岸的人表演他的摇楷。那时，他会把动作做得很有节奏，很有模样。但现在他知道，谁也看不见他摇楷，就不去在乎动作一一他现在只想将船摇得快一些，早点让船进入芦苇荡里。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　岸上有人问</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>谁在摇船</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>?”<br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑桑不回答。蒋一轮与白雀自然更不会回答。船依然走它的路，谁也不去理会岸上的人。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　村庄与学校都渐渐地远去了，船正在接近大河口。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>他们可以说话了。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>桑桑想。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　可是蒋一轮与白雀并不说话。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑桑很纳闷</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>好不容易在一块儿，怎不说话呢</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>?”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　蒋一轮与白雀却就是不说话，那么面对面地坐着。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　天空有嘎嘎声。桑桑知道，那是夜行的野鸭子。桑桑能想像出，那队野鸭子，正在天空下整齐地飞着，但一个个样子都很滑稽</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>—</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>野鸭总是那么一副笨样子。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　船出了大河口，水面忽然一下开阔了。月亮从东边的树林里升上来了，水面上就有了一条晃动不定的银色</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>*</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>的路。这条银色</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>*</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>的路，直伸向远方，突然地就断了。桑桑顺着这条银色</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>*</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>的路望去，已隐隐约约地看到了那个芦苇荡。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　水面一宽，加上风大了一些，船便开始晃动。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　蒋一轮与白雀依旧不说话。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑桑想</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>也不知他俩干什么来了</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>?</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>大人的行为很古怪，让人想不明白。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　船到了芦苇荡。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　这是一片很大的芦苇荡，月光下一望无际。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　蒋一轮先上了岸。桑桑看到，蒋一轮伸过手来，本来是想拉一下白雀的，但白雀没有用他帮忙，自己跳到了岸上。他们面对着似乎无限深远的芦苇荡，一阵脚橱，很长时间站在那儿，不敢往深处走去。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑桑说</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>我一个人就走进去过很远很远。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　蒋一轮和白雀一前一后往前走了几步，蒋一轮回头问</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>桑桑，你呢</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>?”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑桑说</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>我要看船。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”<br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　蒋一轮与白雀继续往前走。站在船上的桑桑看到，他们走着走着，就并排走了，并且渐渐地挨到了一起。当时，月亮很亮地照着他们。桑桑觉得他们的身影要比白天的长。后来，芦苇越来越稠密，直至完全地遮挡住了他们。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑桑坐了下来。他朝天空望去，天空干净得如水洗刷过一般。月亮像是静止的，又像是飘动的。他猜测着蒋一轮和白雀</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>他们是坐着呢，还是站着呢</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>?</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>他们在说些什么</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>?</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>桑桑猜测不出来，就不去猜测了。他依然去看天空。他忽然地觉得一个人独自守着船很孤单。他想让自己给自己唱一首歌。但还未等他唱，一缕笛音从芦苇深处响了起来，在十月的夜空下传送着。蒋一轮与白雀并未说话。这使桑桑很遗憾</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>难道就是为了到这儿来吹笛子的吗</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>?<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　就是。笛子响起之后，就一直没有停止。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑桑躺到了船舱里。隔着一层船板，他听到了流水声，叮叮咚咚的，像是在给蒋一轮的笛子伴奏。后来，桑桑迷迷瞪瞪地睡着了。当凉风将他吹醒时，他猛地激灵了一下</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>我睡了多久啦</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>?</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>四周空无一人，只有天和水，他有点害怕起来，立即起身，循着依然还在响着的笛音走过去。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　月光下，桑桑远远地看到了蒋一轮和白雀。蒋一轮倚在一棵谏树上，用的还是那个最优美的姿势。白雀却是坐在那儿。白雀并没有看着蒋一轮，用双手托着下巴，微微仰着头，朝天空望着。月亮照得芦花的顶端银泽闪闪，仿佛把蒋一轮与白雀温柔地围在了一个梦幻的世界里。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑桑拨着芦苇杆，想再朝前走几步。沙沙声惊动了蒋一轮与白雀。他们忽然意识到了时间的流动，抬头望了眼天空，就听见蒋一轮</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>哦</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>了一声，接着白雀说</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>天不早了。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　木船回到村前的大河时，村子已在月光下早已睡熟了。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　五桑桑充当了一个可笑的角色</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>*</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>。但人家桑桑愿意。温幼菊说</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>桑桑是蒋一轮的谍报人员</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>。桑桑的母亲说</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>桑桑是蒋老师花钱雇的一个跑腿的</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>。桑桑不管别人怎么说，照样地做他愿意做的事。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　唯一使桑桑感到遗憾的是，那些信只是在他身边稍微作了一下停留，就不再属于他，而被送到了蒋一轮的或白雀的手上。那是一个又一个的小秘密。而这些小秘密，只是在他眼前晃一晃，便消失了。就仿佛有人总往他的口袋里塞进一块糖，可还是很快又被人家掏走了。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑桑在心里记着他给蒋一轮和白雀一共传了多少封信。而当这个数量变得越来越大时，他就在心底里慢慢地生长出一个念头</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>我也可以看看吗</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>?</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>就这一个念头，就惊得他东张西望了好一阵。但这个念头很顽固，竟不肯放过桑桑。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　这是一个星期天。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑桑又走进了深深的小巷。从走进小巷的那一刻起，桑桑就觉得白雀会从家里走出来，然后她回头看看，见没有父亲白三的影子，就会把一封信从袖笼里抽出来交给他。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑桑开始唱歌。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　白雀果然出来交给了桑桑一封信。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑桑把信揣到怀里，依然唱着歌，但唱得颤颤的，像是穿着单衣走在寒冷的大风里。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑桑出了小巷，就飞快地往学校跑。几乎每回都是这样。他总想立即把信交给蒋一轮。他喜欢看到蒋一轮在接过信时的那种两眼熠熠发亮的样子。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　蒋一轮被桑乔叫走，到镇上购买办公用品去了。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑桑有点扫兴。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑桑一边走，一边从怀里掏出白雀的信，将它举起来，在阳光下照着。他什么也没有看到，只是看到一块神秘黑影。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　正往池塘里倒药渣的温幼菊在一旁笑着</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:‘</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>桑桑，你在偷看蒋老师的信。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑桑说</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>谁看啦</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>?</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>我没有看。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>你想看。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>温幼菊说。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>我才不想看呢。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>桑桑把信重新放进怀里，立即逃走了。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑桑搬了张梯子，从鸽笼里掏出一对羽毛未完全丰满的鸽子，双手将它们一只一只地抛到空中。其中，一只直接就飞到了房顶上，另一只却在飞起来之后不知道该往哪儿落，竟然晃晃悠悠地飞了好几圈，最后落到了河边上的草垛上。桑桑在下面赶它，未能赶得了它，就爬上了草垛顶。那只鸽子见了桑桑，就矮下身子，几次要做出飞的样子，可又没有飞，直到桑桑马上就要抓住它了，它才一拍翅膀飞到了房顶上。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑桑今天没有什么事情好做，就在草垛顶上躺下了。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　大草垛很高，桑桑一躺下，谁也看不见他。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑桑躺在草垛顶上，看天看云看过路的几只别人家的鸽子。他的手无意中碰到了那封信。他把信拿出来，又对着阳光照着，并且是长久地照着。当然还是什么也没瞧着。而越是什么也没看见，他就越想看见。他坐了起来，低下头向四处看了看，见空无一人，心禁不住一阵慌慌乱跳。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　河边大树的树顶上蹲着一只灰黄色</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>*</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>的鸟，歪着头，看着草垛顶上的桑桑。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>我就看一眼，只看一眼</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>!”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>他吐出了湿流流的舌头，用舌尖上的唾沫反复地浸润着信口。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　那只鸟</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>呀</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>地叫了一声。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑桑一惊，将信立即扔在了草垛顶上。他抬头看到了那只鸟。他觉得那只歪着脖子的鸟也很想看这封信。他把信又捡了起来。唾沫涂得太多，在信封口漫开来，留下一片湿印。他又顺手从草垛上拔下一根草，用草茎将信封口轻轻剔开了。他又看了一眼那只鸟，将信封口朝下，这么轻轻一磕，将里面的信倒了出来。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　那只鸟拍着翅膀飞开了。它飞的样子很奇特</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>往前一窜一窜，每一窜都很有力迅捷，并且是不住地往高空中窜，像枚多节火箭，不一会就变成了一个几乎看不见的黑点。而这时，它在高空非常清脆地叫响了，声音象清风吹进玻璃瓶口时发出的声音。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑桑抖抖索索地将信打开了。厚厚地，大概有三四张纸。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑桑正要去念信时，听到了鸟翅声，抬头一看，那只鸟居然又回来了，并且还是站在刚才那根柔软的枝条上。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑桑刚看了个开头，脸就刷地通红，并且立即闭上了眼睛。他感觉到阳光透过眼皮时，他的眼前是淡红色</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>*</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>的。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　风吹着手中的信纸，发出一种扰人的声响。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑桑的眼睛慢慢睁开了，但桑桑没有去看信，却去看了一眼枝头上的那只鸟。那只鸟半闭着眼睛，似乎无心想知道信的内容，在打纯儿。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　接下来，桑桑看一阵，就闭一阵眼睛。他觉得那些话说得都很奇怪。他还从没听过这样柔和的语言。桑桑是作文高手。桑桑觉得那些句子，都是挺美的。放在往常，桑桑每次在看到书中一段他认为写得很美的句子或段子时，都会将它们摘抄下来。桑桑觉得白雀的信中的每一个句子，都是可以摘录到笔记本里的。但他又拿不太准，这是否也属于那种可以摘录到笔记本里的的句子。他以前没有见过这样一种美句子。不管怎么说，桑桑觉得这些句子确实挺美的。桑桑想</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>是不是这样的信，都是用这样的语言写成的呢</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>?<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　白雀写得一手清秀的字。信干干净净的。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑桑的手出汗了。桑桑的手一直不算干净。因此，桑桑在信上留下了黑黑的手指印。这使桑桑到很羞愧。他把信放在草垛上，把双手拿到裤子上，仔细搓擦起来。他哪里想到，正在这时，来了一阵风，哗啦一下将信吹了起来。他惊得用双手去乱抓在空中飘着的，并用身体去乱扑正在草垛顶上翻卷着的，这才勉勉强强地将信与信封抓住了，压住了。但还是有一页纸被风吹跑了。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　这一页纸，象是一窝小鸟里头最调皮的一只，居然独自一个脱离了鸟群先飞远了。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑桑趴在那儿不敢动，因为他的腹下压着另外几页纸。他只能先眼巴巴地看着那张纸在空中一晃一晃地轻轻地飘动着。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　枝头上的那只鸟，见了那张飘忽的纸，大概以为也是一只鸟，就从枝头飞下来，与那张纸在空中翻上翻下地旋舞起来，很像是一对空中的舞伴。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　那一页纸进到风口里去了，看样子，一会半会还没有落下的心思。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑桑一边用眼睛盯住，一边小心翼翼地将腹下所压的其它几页纸，一页一页地捉住。他看到那页纸越飞越低，越飞越低，正向河里飘去，也来不及去整理那几页纸，只是胡乱地将它们揣进怀里，跳下了草垛，直向那页纸追过去。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　那页纸越是接近地面，下落得就越迅捷，像是飞不动了。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑桑跑到离它还有十米远的地方时，它突然被一股气流压住，几乎垂直地掉在了河边上的一个烂泥塘里。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑桑将它捡起一瞧，只见上面沾满了泥水。他提着这页纸，一脸沮丧。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑桑突然起了立即摆脱这封信的念头，将怀里的那几页纸掏了出来，慌忙地将它们连同那一页掉在泥塘里的纸一起，都扔到了河里。他看了一眼横七竖八地在水上飘着的纸，赶紧逃离了河边，就像一个罪犯逃离犯罪现场一样。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑桑回到了自家的院子里，忐忑不安地坐在门槛上。那几页纸总在他眼前飘动着。他开始编织谎言。然而被那几页纸的飘动所干扰，老也编不下去。他低头时，偶尔看到了还未扔掉的信封。这时，他就有一种看见了一只出尽了小鸟而空留在枝叉上的鸟巢时的感觉。他把信封使劲抖了抖，终于什么也没有抖出来。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>它们大概已经漂远了。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>桑桑想。他感到不安，仿佛是他的几只鸽子，被他抛弃了似的。他起身又来到了河边。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　那几页纸居然没有漂远，却聚拢到了码头上。他看到，那张沾了泥水的纸，在水面上这么漂了一会，已经干干净净了。桑桑就很懊悔，当时，将它在水里洗洗，晒干了不就行了</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>?</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>他连忙跑到水边上，将那些纸又都捞了上来。他找了一个有阳光、但没有人的地方，很小心地将它们一页一页地剥离开来，晾在了几根低垂的树枝上，然后就在一旁守着，等它们被太阳晒干后，好抹抹平再装进信封里去。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　这时，桑桑听见了脚步声。他探头一看，见温幼菊正朝这边走来，并且只剩下几步远了。他连忙从树枝上摘下那些纸。在摘的过程中，纸被树枝勾住，有两页被撕破了。桑桑怕被温幼菊看见，这一回，索性</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>*</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>将它们团成一个疙瘩远远地扔到了河里，然后拔腿他跑掉了蒋一轮回来后，在桑桑家院门口站了一下。桑桑看见了蒋一轮，但没有过来，看他的鸽子去蒋一轮想，桑桑今天没有给他带来白雀的信，也就走了。桑桑没有想到，白雀的这封信，是封很要紧的信。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　六关于白三的脾气，油麻地人有最确切的评价</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>嘴里叼根屎撅子，拿根麻花都不换。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”<br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　白三平衡能力很差，走一座独木桥时，走了三分之二，掉到了河里。但白三并不朝只剩下三分之一距离的对岸游去，而是调转头，重新游回岸这边。他不信就走不过这座独木桥去</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>!</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>白三水淋淋地又站到了桥头上。当时，村里正有个人撑船经过这里，说</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>我用船把你送过去。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>白三说</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>不</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>!</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>老子今天一定要走过这座桥</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>!”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>他又去走那根独木。这回比上回难走，因为他一边走，一边往独木上淋水，把独木淋滑了。他努力地走着，并在嘴里嘟嘟嚷嚷地骂个不停，既骂独木，也骂自己。结果，只走了三分之一，就又掉进了河里。他爬上岸来再走。撑船的那个好心人，一笑，说了声</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>这个白三</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>，也不管他，把船撑走了。白三连连失败，最后大恼，搬起那根独木，将它扔进水中，然后抱住它游到对岸。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　白三现在坚决反对白雀与蒋一轮来往。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　白三瞧不上蒋一轮。白三就白雀这么一个女儿。他要把她交给一个他看得上的人。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　但白雀看得上的人就是蒋一轮。白雀走到哪儿，眼睛里都有蒋一轮，总能听见他的笛音。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　白三说</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>那个蒋一轮，一个穷教书的，有什么好的</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>!”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　白雀不理白三，梳她的头，照她的镜子。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　白三很恼火，就把她的镜子扔在地上</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>他老子是个大地主，他是小老婆养的</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>!”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　白雀哭起来</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>小老婆养的又怎么啦</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>?</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>小老婆也是老婆。有老婆总比没老婆的强。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”<br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　白三操起扁担来要打白雀。因为白雀的话象把利刀戳在了白三的心上</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>白三没老婆，白三的老婆在白雀还不满一岁时跟人跑到江南去了，白三一直是个光棍。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　白雀知道白三不会打她，哭着，梗着脖子，肩一耸一耸地抽动着，站在那儿不动。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　白三明白</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>白雀大了，有心想飞了。但白三无法改变自己的看法。他要请人给白雀另找个男人，他就是不能把白雀交给蒋一轮。邻居张胜家早看上了白雀，想把白雀说给他的外甥谷苇。谷苇是镇上的文书。白三见过这个白净的一副书生气的谷苇。张胜知道了白三的心思，说</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>这是好事。让两个孩子先见见面。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>白三就让白雀跟那个谷苇见面。白雀没有充足的理由不见谷苇，白雀似乎也在哪儿见过谷苇。白雀没有坚决地拒绝白三。她想让蒋一轮帮她坚决起来。于是就写了那封信，问蒋一轮怎么办，还约了蒋一轮在村后的大磨坊旁见面。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　到了约定的时间，白雀装着到自家菜地干活的样子，挎着一只篮子去了大磨坊旁。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　没有收到信的蒋一轮，当然不会出现在这里。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　白雀就站在黄昏的风中等蒋一轮，一直等到天黑。她有点害怕了，只好往家走，路上就生了蒋一轮的气</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>商量这么要紧的事，他也敢耽误。但白雀想到了在过去的日子里，蒋一轮从未失约过，甚至每次都是他先到场，就怀疑自己把日子记错了。是黄昏，这一点肯定没有错。但，是哪一天的黄昏，她不敢肯定了。因此，第二天黄昏，白雀又来到了大磨坊旁。其情形与昨日一样。这回白雀另想原因了</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>他才不在乎呢</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>!</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>白雀一路上就在心里说</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>我也不在乎，我明天就见谷苇</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>!</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>回到家，她真的对白三说</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>不是让我见谷苇吗</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>?</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>我见。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”<br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　蒋一轮一直等不到白雀的信，又惶惶不安起来，又去河边上吹笛子。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　白雀听见了，但白雀并不去想主意摆脱白三的眼睛，到河边上去看蒋一轮。白雀已见过谷苇了。白雀见过谷苇之后，有一种说不清楚的感觉。她似乎有点后悔见谷苇。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　心里最不安宁的是桑桑。他那天打开信，实际上只看了几行字。他想</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>那信里肯定有要紧的事，我把他们的事耽误了。一见到蒋一轮那副魂不守舍的样子，他就低下头去。蒋一轮讲课时又心不在焉了。桑桑听课，更是听得心不在焉。他的脑子里，老是那几页纸在哗啦哗啦地翻动。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑桑想从白雀那儿再等得一封信。这天，他又出现在巷子里，唱起了歌。他一边用地上随便捡起的瓦片在沿巷而立的墙上划着道，一边唱。从巷头唱到巷尾，又从巷尾唱到巷头。走到白雀家门口时，就把声音放大了唱。但却总不见白雀出来。他想可能是白雀睡觉没有听见。他看了看墙上被他划下的一道道印迹，决定不唱了，改成大叫</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　一颗星，</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　挂油瓶</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>!<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　油瓶漏，</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　炒黑豆</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>!<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　黑豆香，</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　卖生姜</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>!<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　生姜辣，</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　叠宝塔</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>!<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　宝塔尖，</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　戳破天</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>!<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　天哎天，</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　地哎地，</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　三拜城隆和土地</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>!<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　土地公公不吃荤，</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　两个鸭子回圈吞</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>!<br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　他几乎是站在白雀家门口叫唤的。但即便是这样，白雀也没出来。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>白雀姐，是不想理蒋老师了，也不想理我了。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>他低垂着头，离开了白雀家门口。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　当天晚上，桑桑推开了蒋一轮宿舍的门，说</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>那天白雀姐给过我一封信，我把它弄坏了，就把它扔了</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>……”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　蒋一轮</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>哎呀</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>了一声，双手抱住脑袋，就地转了一圈，然后扑通把自己放到床上，又咚咚咚地捶了几下床板，又用双脚互相将脚上的皮鞋一一蹬下，滴笃两声，落在了地上</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>我的桑桑吔</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>!”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑桑笔直地站在门口。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　蒋一轮歪过头来，朝桑桑苦笑了一下。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑桑走了，但他没有走多远，蒋一轮将他叫住了</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>桑桑，你过一会来找我。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”<br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　当桑桑双手接过蒋一轮抢写出的一封信，后脑勺被蒋一轮富有意味地拍了一下之后，几天来一直惶惶不安的他，如释重负地向校门口跑去。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　白雀家的大门已经关上了。桑桑屋前屋后地绕来绕去，既无法进屋，也无法看到白雀。他要有补过的表现。他必须于今晚将信送到白雀手上。但他又确实无计可施。他想敲开门。但开门的肯定是白三，而不会是白雀。白雀住在里屋，白三住在外屋，走到白雀房前去，必须穿过白三的前屋。今晚上见到白雀，简直是不可能的事情。桑桑失望地站在黑洞洞的巷子里。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑桑走出巷子时，看到了大河那边的油麻地小学，并且很快看到对岸立着一条长长的人影</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>蒋一轮在等待他送信的消息。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑桑又转身走进了巷子。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑桑爬上了矮墙，又从矮墙上爬到了白雀家的房顶上。他趴在天窗上往里看，首先看到了一只半明半暗的小马灯挂在木柱上。接下来，他就看清楚了</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>这间大屋里，既睡着白三，还歇着一条大公水牛。一是天冷，二是怕牛拴在外边被人偷了，白三像这个地方上的许多人家一样，将牛牵到了屋子里。此刻，白三已经在一张老床上睡熟了，而大水牛却还在墙角里慢慢地吃草，两只大眼在昏暗的马灯光下闪着亮光。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑桑望着白三模模糊糊的面孔，忽然对白三生起气来</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>所有这一切事情的发生，全是因为他</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>!</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>桑桑起了一个恶毒的念头</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>拉开天窗，然后站起来，解开裤带，让裤子落在脚面上，对着天窗口撒尿，直撒到白三的脸上，惊得他叫起来</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>哦哟，屋漏雨了</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>!”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>桑桑想像着白三被</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>雨</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>淋了的时候的样子，坐在屋脊上傻笑起来。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑桑终于没有办法，只好从屋顶上下来。而就在他双脚刚从矮墙溜下，一接触到地面时，他忽然由刚才的撒尿造雨的念头引发出一个主意。他到处乱转着，终于在一个人家的门口发现了一只铁壶。他拿了铁壶，到河边上提了一铁壶水，然后带着这一铁壶水吃力地又重新爬到屋脊上。他趴在天窗口，仔细观察了白三，认定他已经睡死，就轻轻地拨开了天窗。水牛差不多就在天窗下的位置上。他在屋脊上一笑，慢慢地倾斜着水壶，水从壶嘴流了出来。随即，他听到了水落在地面上时发出的噼哩啪啦的声响。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　白三动了动身子。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　噼哩啪啦的水声大起来。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　白三连忙翻身起来，衣服都未来得及披，下了床，操起一只早准备好了的带木柄的硕大木桶，送到了牛的腹下去接尿。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　水牛安闲地嚼草并无动静。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　白三耐心地等了一会，并未接到尿，对牛骂了一声</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>畜牲</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>，抖抖索索地上床去了。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑桑等了一会，又开始往下倒水。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　还未暖了身子的白三大骂一声</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>这畜牲</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>，只好又赶紧下床，端起木桶去接尿。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　无尿好接。白三左等右等，未等得一滴，很恼火，扔下木桶，在牛屁股上狠扇了一巴掌</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>找死哪</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>!”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>上床去了。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑桑把事情做得很有耐心。他等白三差不多又快迷糊上再也不想醒来时，又开始往下撒尿</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>—</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>桑桑当时的感觉就是撒尿。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　嚼哩啪啦的声音很大，是大雨谤沱时檐口的水流声。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　白三一拍床，骂了一句脏话，坐了起来，看那牛在嘴里说着</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>我看你尿，我看你尿</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>……”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　牛不尿，只嚼草。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　白三骂骂咧咧地穿衣起了床，解了牛绳，牵着它就向门外走</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>畜牲，活活冻死你</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>!”<br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑桑立即伏在了屋脊上。他在听到吱呀一阵开门声之后不一会，就看见白三牵着牛走进了巷子里，然后朝巷子后面自家的大草垛牵去</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>——</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>那是白天拴牛的地方</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　白三和牛走远了。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑桑不管铁壶了，赶紧从屋上下来，跑进了白雀家，拍响了白雀的门。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　白雀居然没睡，拉开门，见了桑桑，吃了一惊</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>桑桑</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>?</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>是你</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>?</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>你怎么进来的</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>?”<br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑桑什么也不说，把信从怀里掏出来，交到白雀手上，转身就跑。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑桑出了巷子，一路胡乱叫喊，闹得好几个人从睡梦里醒来，含糊不清地问</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>谁家的孩子在外面喊什么</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>?”<br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　七蒋一轮与白雀又见面了。白雀自然不再生气。但白雀与蒋一轮之间，似乎有点生分。白雀也说不出原因来</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　这一天，谷苇到油麻地来了。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　油麻地的人就装着去白雀家借东西或路过这里的样子，往屋里看谷苇。看完了，他们就在巷头或地头说</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>白雀家来的那个男的，人样子长得不错。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　白雀几乎没有露面，就呆在自己的房间里。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　谷苇在白雀家坐坐，就去了舅舅家。在舅舅家又坐了坐，就回镇上去了。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　白雀去镇上买雪花膏，在街上遇到了谷苇。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　谷苇说</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>去我那儿坐坐吧</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>?”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　白雀犹豫了一下，说</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>好吧。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”<br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　快要放寒假时，蒋一轮从桑桑手中接过一封沉甸甸的信。他好象感觉到了什么，就把门关上了。桑桑几次有意路过蒋一轮宿舍的门口，看到那门总是关着。直到傍晚，桑桑才看到蒋一轮将门打开。蒋一轮倚在门框上，双目无神，脸色</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>*</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>仅仅在不到一天的工夫里，就变得憔悴不堪。桑桑甚至隐隐地觉得，蒋一轮的脸上有干了的泪痕。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑桑不知道发生了什么事，但桑桑也陷入一种无名的伤感里。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　放了寒假，蒋一轮就回家了，一去好几十天，也没有到学校来。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　大年三十那天，桑桑去田野上找鸽子，远远地看到，河边上，白雀正与一个男的一起，慢慢地往前走。白雀穿着一件淡绿色</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>*</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>的紧身棉袄，头上是一块鲜红的头巾，在景色</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>*</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>萧条的冬季里，让人觉得十分温暖。白雀老低着头，一边走，一边不时地用手去抓一下金黄的芦苇叶。桑桑觉得，白雀的背影，白雀走路的样子，都格外的好看。桑桑知道，那个男的叫谷苇。谷苇虽然没有蒋一轮高，但后背与腰杆笔直，显得十分的英俊，一头的黑发，在河上吹来的风中飘动着。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑桑没有再找鸽子，就回家了。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　开学的第二天，白雀把一个干干净净的布包包交到桑桑手上</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>桑桑，这里面是他的信，请你把它们交给他。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>桑桑抱着布包包，犹如抱了一个沉重的悲哀。他把信从布包包里拿出来看了看，厚厚的一大摞，用红色</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>*</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>的毛线很认真地捆扎着。他在校园外面转了半天，才把这个布包包交给蒋一轮。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　蒋一轮一副很平静的样子，从桑桑手里接过这个布包包</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>谢谢你，桑桑。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　隔了两天，蒋一轮也交给了桑桑一个布包包，一副歉疚的样子</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>:“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>桑桑，还得麻烦你跑一趟。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'>”<br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑桑接过布包包。他知道那里面都是白雀的信。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　这天傍晚，天空轻轻飘着细雪。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　蒋一轮站在花园里，将那些倾注了他诗与梦一般情思的信，一封一封地投到了火里。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#171414'><br>
            </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#171414'>　　桑桑在离蒋一轮很近的地方站着。他看到纸灰与雪在一起飞舞，火光在蒋一轮寒冷的脸上，不住地闪动，并把他高高的身影摇晃着。</span>
        </p>

        <span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.5pt;font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif'><br clear=all
                style='page-break-before:always'>
        </span>

        <p class=MsoNormal><span lang=EN-US>&nbsp;</span></p>

        <h1><span style='font-family:宋体'>我的妈妈是精灵</span></h1>

        <p class=MsoNormal><span lang=EN-US><img border=0 width=554 height=738 id="图片 7" src="书籍素材.files/image006.jpg"
                    alt="https://gss0.baidu.com/7LsWdDW5_xN3otqbppnN2DJv/doc/pic/item/a9d3fd1f4134970a95e3218b99cad1c8a6865d85.jpg"></span>
        </p>

        <h2 align=center style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:7.5pt;
margin-left:0cm;text-align:center'><span style='font-size:21.0pt;line-height:
173%;font-family:"微软雅黑",sans-serif;color:#7B59C0'>一 我家发生了惊天动地的大事 </span></h2>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>一</span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'> </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>我家发生了惊天动地的大事</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>惊天动地的大事在没有发生以前，常常就像每一个平静的日子一样。这是我的经验。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>那天傍晚，爸爸在桌边打开当晚的《新民晚报》，我家的信箱太小了，每次邮递员总要把报纸叠得皱皱巴巴的，才放得进去。爸每次一层层地剥开它们，都说：</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'>“</span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>明天一定要换新的信箱。</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'>”</span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>可爸爸太懒，他并不去做。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>妈妈从厨房里把烧好的菜端出来，妈今天烧的是蘑菇炒肉片，最上面的肉片颤颤巍巍的。她对我说：</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>马上就好了，你先吃，吃了今天的蘑菇，你下次体育课会跑得比兔子还要快，因为兔子吃的蘑菇没有放油里炒熟。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>我从来不喜欢吃饭，因为我从来没有觉得饿过，可今天很着急，把桌子都准备好了。妈今天为了赶画《红与黑》的插图，烧饭晚了。而我要吃完饭才能看教育电视台的《成长的烦恼》。现在除了语文数学课本，美国的电视剧《成长的烦恼》，就是我们班上全体同学都知道的东西，我和许多人一样，最喜欢的是它的开头，</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'>—</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>张张照片叠在一起，一个人眼看着就从小毛头（婴儿）长大了，连他们的爸爸妈妈也是一样。我们都盼着长大，可以不要天天上课受苦。我是那么爱这部电视剧，以至也喜欢照相这件事了，我过生日的时候，爸爸妈妈送给我一个小的傻瓜照相机，只要一有空，我就自己拍一些照片。只是我的技术不好，拍出来的妈妈，总是没有影子，也很模糊，拍出来的小朋友，倒是很清楚的。</span>
        </p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>我在为爸爸倒酒，爸爸是外科医生，就是那种拿了一把刀杀人家肚子来养活我和妈妈的人：他每天回家时都是好累的样子，从来不用他的那套钥匙自己开门，他不耐烦摸钥匙，他永远是</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'>“</span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>嘭嘭</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>地敲门。走进家门来的时候，他的脸上总是留着一种受了苦的样子，好像我们班上最顽皮的天王知道要被老师臭骂了，一步一步，怕踩死蚂蚁似的走向老师的那种样子。所以他常常在晚上喝一点酒，然后他的脸会很快红起来，然后，就活过来似的开始说话。他非常仔细地读晚报，连中缝里的寻人启事都看，好像他家也丢了人一样。</span>
        </p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>他坐在他的专椅上（那是一把摇摇椅），哈嗒哈嗒用力地摇着，然后把报上的事告诉妈妈，妈妈总是顺着爸爸说话，爸爸一说报纸上的房产广告骗人，妈妈就说：</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'>“</span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>什么离地铁仅</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'>100</span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>米，要么最大号的翅膀的速度的速度是</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'>100</span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>米啦。</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'>”</span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>妈手里常常在赶画着什么白天没画完的插图，她是个自由职业的画家，在家里工作。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>桌子上有三个杯子，爸爸的杯子要倒黄酒，我的杯子要倒雪碧，因为我没满</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>16</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>岁，不能喝可乐。妈说可乐里面有一种东西，会沉淀到小孩的牙齿上，把小孩的牙变黑。妈说，女孩子不能有黑牙，中国古代的女人都长着黑牙，所以她们从来都捂着嘴笑。妈常说这样的话，爸爸一听到就会说：</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'>“</span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>不要瞎三话四（瞎说）。</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>妈妈的那个杯子要倒上可乐，她热爱可乐。我们家的三个人，每天吃饭都坐在自己的椅子上，用自己的杯子。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>就在这时候，我发现自己把爸爸和妈妈的杯子搞错了，等我反应过来，妈妈的杯子底已经被我倒上了一点黄酒。可它的颜色真的与绍兴黄酒的颜色差不多，我知道妈妈从来不吃酒，甚至也不吃醉虾。可杯子底的那一点点酒色，真的看上去一点危险也没有，那天我们体育课上跑了步，我的腿很酸，《成长的烦恼》马上就要开始了，要是我不赶紧坐下来吃，就来不及看开头了。我借着妈妈的杯子尝了尝，只是有一点酒味道，和可乐里的中药味道也没差多少。</span>
        </p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>爸爸在后面的大摇椅上大喝一声：</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>陈淼淼，不准偷喝可乐，牙要黑的。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>吓我一大跳。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>妈妈听到，也在厨房里跟进一句：</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>陈淼淼，不要偷喝。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>小孩子的灵魂长得不牢，是不可以吓的。被他们俩一叫，我马上把真的可乐哗地冲了进去。是怕他们发现了我的的真实小错误，还是什么别的，我不知道。小孩子在爸爸妈妈的一声大喝里，就会做出莫名其妙的事。</span>
        </p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>妈妈的杯子里倒满了真的可乐，我也不能把整杯可乐都倒掉啊，太浪费了。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>那时候我想，下次我一定注意。因为心虚，我特别把可乐大瓶子竖在妈妈的杯子旁边，证明里面全是可乐。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>这时，妈妈把饭盛来了，自从爸爸开始在晚上喝点酒．妈妈就坐在育爸爸最远的那一边桌子吃饭，她甚至不喜欢闻到酒的味道。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>妈妈喝了她的可乐。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>妈突然满脸一白，含着第一口可乐，推开桌子跳将起来。她的眼睛瞪得好大，惊慌地看着爸爸，然后又射向我。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>爸也跳起来，一把接住了妈妈。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>妈妈的身体在爸爸的胳膊里轻轻挂下来，像一块最轻的绸子。爸爸挽着蚂妈的身体就往他们卧室里去。在走廊里拐弯的时候，我看到妈妈垂下来的双腿像绸子衣服被风吹过的时候那样，飘了起来。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>像太阳从云里一点点爬出来，阳光一点点地在地上亮起蒸那样，妈妈那飘飘摇摇的两只脚一点点地变成了蓝色。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>我吓呆了，我以为是科幻电影，不是真的，只是像真的一样，就像《</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>ET</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>》。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>本来我想帮妈妈托住脚，可我害怕。她软软的脚又飘了一下，红色的布拖鞋从她蓝色的、透明的脚上滑了下来，</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'>“</span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>砰</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'>”</span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>地落在我面前，像不小心从桌子上碰下来的一个苹果。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>我大叫一声。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>我从来没听到过有这么尖、这么恐怖的声音，我都让它吓住了。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>在我吓得尖叫的时候，爸爸已经把妈抱进了他们的卧室。遥远的灯下，我看到妈妈的脸也变成蓝色的了，像一张蓝色的手帕，那么轻，那么薄，那么飘飘摇摇的。接着，看不清了，被蓝布遮了起来似的，妈妈的脸不见了。</span>
        </p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>妈妈成了一团蓝色的影子。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>我不敢靠前，也不敢自己在客厅里呆着，妈妈座位上的那一小碗饭，还在冒着一点点白色的热气，就好像妈妈马上就会出来一样。我拉着爸爸衣服，紧紧靠在爸爸的后背上。我的心好像很痒一样的，它不停地发着抖。我看到了妈妈的手，它们还是从前的那种细细长长的，可现在是蓝色的，紧紧地握着，上面布满了蓝色的细小的皱纹，它在我的尖叫声里慢慢地松开，伸出一只手指，轻轻地摇了摇。这是妈妈的动作。</span>
        </p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>别怕，陈淼淼，她是妈妈。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>爸爸这时腾出手来，搂住我。爸的手真凉，湿乎乎的全是汗。我这才知道什么叫冷汗，就是爸爸手心里的那种冰水似的汗。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>她怎么了？</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>她一定是喝下酒了，不能喝酒。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>爸说。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>她喝醉了？</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>我问，</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>快送妈妈去医院呀。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>我想起来了卫生课上老师告诉我们说，急救中心的电话是</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>120</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>爸爸转过脸来，抱着我，望着我，看了我半天，说：</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>陈淼淼你不要怕，你看见了我们家的秘密，不要对任何人说，爸爸告诉你，你的妈妈不是真正的人。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>我听不懂，妈妈不是人，那是什么？</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>是真的人以外的一种人，我们这个世界很大。</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>那又是什么意思呢？看爸爸那费力的样子，好像是很惭愧说出这件事。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>你是说，妈妈是鬼魂？</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>我想起来每年暑假都在中午的儿童节目里播放的小鬼魂盖思波的动画片。可它是动画故事啊，小魂灵生活在大森林里，和一大群会说人话的动物在一起，一看就知道是假的。可我，是一个真正的小孩子，在上海一师附小上学，会放很臭的大蒜屁，不一样啊，我是真的！可怎么也看见了鬼魂了呢。</span>
        </p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>不是另外一种什么东西。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>爸爸马上纠正我说，</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>另外的一种人。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>然后他紧了紧搂着我的手，有一点悲痛地安慰我说，</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'>“</span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>你别怕，她不会害你的，她不是你说的那种鬼魂。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>那是什么？</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>我问。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>是属于另外一个空间的人。我们这个世界就像蜜蜂的巢一样，有好多洞洞，住着不同的人。妈妈是另外一个洞洞里住的人，它们不害人。你说你妈妈害过人吗？</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>看上去它和人一样的！</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>我想起来妈妈平时的样子。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>可也不是真的人。你看</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>——”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>爸指指妈妈，他袖子带起来的风，都能把妈妈吹得摇晃半天。爸赶紧过去把门窗关紧，怕风把妈妈吹跑了。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>她那么轻，幸亏被子重重地压着她，看上去像是被压住的一个氢气球。气球散发出来的是橡皮气味，而她却散发着很浓重的黄酒气味。这真是奇怪，她连一口都没喝下去，只是沾了一点点啊。看样子，她也不会吃人，不像书上写的那些真正的鬼魂。她怎么能吃人呢，一阵风就能把她吹走。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>是我犯了大错误，好在爸爸没心思追查。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>爸爸说，酒里的酒精，是它最怕的东西，一碰就会叫原形。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>紧闭门窗的爸妈的卧室里，有一种从前我从来没有感到过的阴冷的寒气，像冰箱打开了门后散发出来的那种带水的寒气。那是妈妈的床上发出来的气味。当你仔细地闻，就能闻到里面的一种甜甜的腥气，让我想要吐出来。妈妈像是一块那样的冰。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>爸爸的身体很暖，他的肚子那里软软的，让我靠着，他握着我的手。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>我是它生的？</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>我问。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>是的。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>爸爸说。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>那我是一个人呢，还是那种蓝色的人？</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'>”</span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>我问。等我问出来，心里才害了怕，要我也是和妈妈一样的人，我怎么办？</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>爸爸说：</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:
"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>谢谢老天，你是一个真正的小孩。</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>爸爸看了我一眼。爸爸的眼睛在眼镜后面被放大了，被放得那么大，那么大的黑眼珠子，直直地看着我，好像里面还有许多马上就要说出来的秘密，一些可怕的秘密。从前我没有注意到，可今天我是为了看他是不是在骗我，所以用心地看他，眼镜后面的大眼睛，让我害怕起来。要是爸爸也不是一个真正的人呢？他什么都知道，可要是我不问，他就什么也不说，我怎么能知道他就不是蓝人呢？</span>
        </p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>我大叫一声，从爸爸身上弹了出去，我没有站稳，向妈妈的床倒了</span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'> </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>过去，我压在妈妈的身上了，可好象也没有牙着，我的身体撞在床板上，我听到妈妈的被子里发出了很细的一声呻吟，像小猫的那种柔弱而凄凉的叫声。</span>
        </p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>刺骨的凉气，还有一种腥气，真的是腥气，我在有一次和李雨辰一起杀死一条蚯蚓的时候也闻到过那种从土里来的腥气。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>我跳起来，夺门而出。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>后面有一条大大的黑影子罩了上来！是爸爸。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>我尖叫，叫得比救火车还要尖，还要响。可爸爸从后面抱住了我。爸爸的身上真的是暖的，而且有一种温暖气昧，爸爸在我的尖叫声里大声申辩：</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'>“</span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>我不是蓝人，我不是蓝人，我和你都是一样的人，真正的人。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>我们来到了客厅里，我想起来爸爸说蓝人不能碰酒，就点着酒瓶子对爸爸说：</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>你喝，喝了才能证明你是真的。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>爸爸拿过酒瓶子来就喝，马上，爸爸的脸红了，爸爸的额头红了，爸爸的脖子都红了，他的手还是暖的，他的脚也很重，爸爸不是蓝人，真的。这时我想起来，从我懂事开始，爸爸就是每晚要喝黄酒的。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>我也想喝，我也想证明我是一个真正的人，虽然我是妈妈生的孩子。可要是我变了呢？</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>爸爸把酒瓶子送到我嘴边，说：</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'> “</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>你也喝，别怕，你刚刚碰到了它，更得喝点。</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>黄酒是苦的，又辣，像放了辣椒水的咳嗽药水。我喝下一小口，它像一小条火，在我的肚子里熊熊燃烧起来。我的眼睛马上就肿起来一样，看不清东西了。发蓝了吗，发蓝了吗，我把自己的手举到长桌子的灯下，透过了灯光的手，是金色的，能看到里面细细长长的骨头。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>再喝了口酒，全身都烫了，连脑子里面都是烫的。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>撩开我的衣服，我的肚子在灯下面很白，一点也不蓝。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>我蓝了吗？</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>我问爸爸。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>没有，陈淼淼。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>爸爸说。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>可为什么妈妈是蓝的呢！那蓝色的一团东西，怎么是我的妈妈呢？我的心里真正难过起来，我的妈妈是常常说乱七八糟的话的好玩的人，是手指凉凉的，在冬天要碰我身体时，总先暖好了手的好妈妈啊，她现在哪里去了呢，她变成了一个让我那么害怕的东西。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>我哭了。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>爸爸抱着我，他说：</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>别哭啊，别哭啊。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>妈妈不是为了吃人来到我们这个世界上的，那她想做什么呢。她和我们看上去没有什么两样，多么奇怪啊。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>爸爸说所有的问题我都可以自己问妈妈，她明天早晨会恢复正常的。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>那么说，你从前也看到妈妈这样过？</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>我问。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>爸爸点点头，很惭愧的样子：</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>在妈妈生你的时候，她不要去医院，因为怕酒精。</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>都那么多年了啊，爸爸妈妈瞒了我这么多年！我一直以为自己是和别人一样的小孩！</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>爸爸说：</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:
"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>你知道为什么你的照片上妈妈总是没有影子，也很模糊？是因为妈妈与我们不是一种人，她从来都没有影子。而且对照相机来说，她不够实在，就像你一般拍不出很薄的云一样。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>爸爸深深地看了我一眼，说：</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>要让你这么早就知道家里的秘密干什么呢，你会难过的啊。</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>你怕吗？</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>爸爸每天和妈妈生活在一起，晚上他们俩关着门睡在一间屋子里。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>我怕。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>爸爸说，</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>但我没有办法。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>你不是说妈妈不吃人吗，你怕什么？</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'> ”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>我总觉得爸爸还有什么事瞒着我，所以一直多留了一个心眼。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>爸爸说他怕自己像许仙那样。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>对的，妈妈也像白蛇一样怕酒，一碰到酒以后就会现原形。原来神话故事是真的可能发生的事。那妈妈也会像白蛇一样又善良又有本事吗？会隐身吗？会飞吗？会想什么就变出来什么吗？可是妈看上去一直是怕爸爸的，爸爸说什么，她就跟在他后面说。有一次妈妈说戴眼镜的人都是为了自己的眉毛太短了，要用眼镜边来加长。爸爸说：</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'>“</span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>不要瞎三话四。</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'>”</span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>妈妈马上就很惭愧地笑笑不说了。妈妈从来都没有像白蛇娘娘一样神气过。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>我要小便，就让爸爸陪我一起去厕所，我已经长大了，爸爸不好意恩看我，就把头别过去看窗子外面。我小便的声音真响呀，嘘嘘地响。我也不好意思，可我害怕一个人。妈妈红色的刷牙杯像一只墨西哥大鸟前面，鬼鬼祟祟的。妈妈粉红色的洗脸毛巾，静静地吊在毛巾架子上，可好像自己就悄悄地动了一下，像一张马上要张开的巨大的眼皮。看着它们，我的心又痒痒起来，然后我又抖起来。妈妈所有的东西，好像一下子有了灵性，随时会变出别的样子来。</span>
        </p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>爸说：</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:
"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>你别怕呀，你是我的孩子，我会保护你的。</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>我不完全是怕，还有一种奇怪的激动。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>隔着客厅和走廊，我看着卧室里的妈妈，她还是蓝色的，看不清楚脸</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>,</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>静静地被她的花被子压着，可是我觉得她的身上有一种奇怪的东西，好像是在求我不要怕她，她还是原来的妈妈，一心对我好的那个人，我不知道这些话是怎么到了我的脑子里的。我看到她满是蓝色小皱纹的手动了一下，我想起了妈妈平时的手，她很喜欢摸我的身体，我觉得心里有一点暖暖的，像从前妈妈把手伸到我的衣服里，摸着我后背的什么地方一样。</span>
        </p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>然后，那蓝色的手指动了下下，有一点微微闪光的蓝色像一个小蛾子一样朝我飞过来，它飞到我面前的时候停了下来，原来它是一朵蓝色的绣出来的小花，是一个法国牌子</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'>“</span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>梦得娇</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'>”</span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>的商标的小花，我想起来，妈妈从来就是穿这个牌子的衣服的，我从小看着它长大。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>我刚刚张开手，那朵小花就落到了我的手心里。它又湿又凉；像一块冰。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>我惨叫一声，把花从手心里甩出去。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>爸爸因为多喝了酒，眼睛也睁不开，听到我叫，从椅子上跳了起来。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>那朵小蓝花，落在地毯上，化成了一大滴水渍。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>那天晚上，是爸爸在我的小房间里陪着我，我才慢慢睡着的。半夜的时候，我好像听到有人开小储藏室的门，那门不常常开，所以一开；声音就特别的响。我抬起头来，见爸爸靠在我的床边上睡得像昏过去一样，他呼出来的全都是黄酒的气味。我把头塞到爸爸的后背里，一动也不敢动，要是妈妈想要吃我的话，得先把爸爸搬开才行，可搬走爸爸，也不是件容易的事。爸爸浑身都散发着酒气，象一大团酒糟。</span>
        </p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>在睡着以前，我在心里骂了自己，我真的是一个自私的人，古代的小孩，为了保护自己的爸爸，就自己去喂老虎，可我呢！太不像话。</span></p>

        <h2 align=center style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:7.5pt;
margin-left:0cm;text-align:center'><span style='font-size:21.0pt;line-height:
173%;font-family:"微软雅黑",sans-serif;color:#7B59C0'>二 感情是世界上最黏的胶水 </span></h2>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>二</span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'> </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>感情是世界上最黏的胶水</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>等我醒来，太阳深深地晒满了整个屋子。楼下的南京西路上传来汽车的声音，还有那个站在路中间的警察嘴里的哨子声音。他是全世界最厉害的人之一，只要他的哨子一响，再心急的人也只好停下汽车。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>妈坐在地板上望着我。她又恢复原来的样子了，有一点瘦，眉毛淡淡的，里面藏着一粒红色的痣。她穿着一件很大的</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'>T</span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>恤，当然是</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'>“</span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>梦得娇</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'>”</span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>。白色的大</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'>T</span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>恤上，绣着一朵浅蓝色的小花，那种蓝色，就是昨天妈妈变的颜色。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>我赶紧抓住自己的被子：</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>爸爸快来！</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>我叫。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>爸爸还是睡着没有醒，他一定是昨天晚上喝得太多了。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>你别怕我，陈淼淼，</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>妈说，</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>我不伤害人的。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>她拍拍自己的手给我看，手里什么东西也没有。指甲的长短也很正常。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>可这并不真正说明什么，就是狼也懂得先装成一个外婆呢。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>她又伸出舌头来给我看，舌头上没有滴着血。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>妈妈说：</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:
"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>我说什么你才能相信我呢厂她想了想，说，</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>我们身上是凉的，有一点像冰激凌的意思，不过不甜。可人的身上是热的，特别是喝了酒的人，酒在他们的身体里到处着火，我们遇见人；就像冰激凌遇见太阳，只有我们怕人，怎么可能吃人。所以你真的不要怕我。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>妈妈是另外一种人，就像爸爸说的一样，他们是那种蓝色会飘的人，住在另外一个空间里的，和故事里的仙女、人鱼住在一起。他们是一种比人还要脆弱的人，风都能把他们吹跑。可是平时我们人不能到他们的地方去，而他们，在一天里的一个特定的时候可以到人间来，他们会走，也会飞。说起来，他们比人要高级一些。</span>
        </p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>所以妈妈他们是那种比我们真正的人要高级，可是也要脆弱的人。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>真的？</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>我问。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>真的。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>妈妈用力点着头，</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>你也是我的孩子，我为什么要骗你呢！我都不能再说</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'>‘</span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>真的</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'>’</span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>，因为骗人的人最喜欢特别再说一声</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'>‘</span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>真的</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'>’</span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>，所以我不说真的，可是！我说的都是真的。你可以看我的眼睛。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>妈妈把她的脸伸到我的眼前，她的眼睛是棕色的，像一只睡着了的小熊一样温和和诚实。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>她这样看着我说：</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'> “</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>我的孩子，你千万不要怕我。我会做许多事，那是别的妈妈不能为孩子做的，我都能为你做。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>你会什么？</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>我问。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>她伸手往前一抓，再把握着的手一个手指一个手指地在我面前张开来，妈妈的手里面，出现了一个我一直吵着要买，可是爸爸不同意给我买的电子小鸡。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>怎么样？</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>妈一脸既小心又得意的样子。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>妈把电子小鸡递给我，起身到抽屉里找了一张上百块钱，把钱叠成一只小小的纸鹤，她把它放在手心里吹了一口气，说：</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'>“</span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>天皇皇，地呈皇，到淮海路上白色和蓝色的大百货店里去一次吧。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'>”</span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>说着，她把小纸鹤往窗外一扔，钱做的小纸鹤顿时就像剪刀一样扎向前去。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>妈转身对我说：</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>不能白拿人家伊势丹的东西，不劳而获和偷没有什么两样，都是不好的。我是一个好人，就是别人不看见的时候也不做坏事。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>我紧紧地捏着手里那滑滴响着的小鸡。从前看《阿拉丁》，看到他有下个神灯可以帮他，看《木偶奇遇记》，皮诺曹有仙女帮着，心里真的是羡慕。没想到我也有下天发现自己有个这样的妈妈。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>妈妈坐在一边，突然没有声音地笑了出来，比人们说的那种微笑要笑得更厉害。她的脸上全是笑，眼睛在闪闪发光，脸上在闪闪发光，淡淡的眉毛像马一样地飞围两边，她美滋滋地向我闭了闭眼睛。她一定猜出来我心里正在想什么，她一定是在为我心里想的那些念头高兴。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>忽然，妈妈把手伸到自己的眼睛上，往里一抓，她的眼眶里就开出一朵蓝色的花来。她手上的眼珠儿变成了卞小团蓝色的橡皮泥，她把它放在手心里捏捏软，然后揉一揉，搓下搓，拉一拉，做成一朵小小的蓝花，可我看到，花蕊里长着一只眼睛，正在一眨一眨，妈妈说：</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'>“</span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>天皇皇，地皇皇，到静安寺那里的小学校里去一次吧。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>那朵花就飞走了。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>妈妈说：</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:
"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>有人在一个大房间里把青蛙切开来，许多孩子在看，，青蛙有血流了出来，很凉，很新鲜，像最好的冰淇淋。</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'>”</span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>妈响亮地咽了一下口水，</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'>“</span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>真想不到，你们也这样对青蛙。</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>我说：</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:
"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>不是我们，是生物课的老师。将来一定会有无数青蛙的灵魂来找他，杀死他。我最恨杀青蛙了。</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'>”</span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>妈妈也知道，我最喜欢的小动物，不是狗，也不是猫，而是绿色的青蛙。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>妈妈看着我，不再说下去了。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>过了一会儿，妈妈又说：</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>你那小朋友李雨辰正在做英文作业呢，我的天，她怎么咬铅笔头！</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>我说：</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:
"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>那是因为她做得心里恨死了。</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>李雨辰算是我目前的好朋友，我们住得近，天天一起上学和放学。她和我不是一个小组，却一起坐在第四排，所以，我们中间只隔了一条通道，等于是同桌差不多。她是个瘦小的女孩子，我发现她的眼睛像是小兔子一样，眨得飞快。我虽然不能说是她的知心朋友，可我知道她这样做是什么意思。她虽然是班上的好学生，可也不喜欢做作业，她和我一样讨厌那么多的作业，可我们不得不做，</span>
        </p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>所以，她的铅笔头，全都被咬得像漏斗一样凹进去了。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>那她一定是个天才，被学校的功课压制住了，天才的力量就从牙齿里面跑出来，只好咬铅笔头。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'>”</span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>妈妈说，</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'>“</span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>她怎么还是那么脏？</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>她的爸爸妈妈离婚了，她跟她爸爸过，所以跟没人管的孩子一样。其实这也是我目前和她比较要好的重要原因。从前我喜欢和班上最出色的同学做朋友，我总是发现他们都很自私而且很容易看不起人。所以我要找一个倒霉蛋当朋友，我想这样的人应该是自卑的，对我的关心，肯定心里很感谢。然后她就对我忠心耿耿。我很希望帮助别人，只是想要帮一个对我真正忠心耿耿的人，我才能信任，才会放胆和她做朋友，不会在帮助她的时候心烦，不会老想着：凭什么老是我帮你，你就不能帮助我？我从前就一直老这么想的。</span>
        </p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>爸爸妈妈离婚的小孩都是这副模样的。</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'>”</span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>我说。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>那要是你的爸爸和我离婚了，你也会这样？</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'>”</span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>妈妈说。她那留在脸上的眼睛静静地看着我，又像玩具熊那样，又软，又暖。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>你们不会的。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>我说。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>要是会呢？</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>妈妈坚持问。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>不知道。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>我说着去推了推她，</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>不要说这种吓人的话。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>妈妈叹了口气，又说：</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>你们王老师烫着脚了，她在帮你们班的小朋友热袋装奶，热水一下子溅到脚上，她一只脚在地板上跳。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>我这才意识到，原来妈妈的眼睛飞到我们班上去了，她在家里就能看到我们班上所有的事。这真的是太奇妙了。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>于是我问：</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:
"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>你能到男厕所里去看看吗？</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>妈妈吓了一跳，说：</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>千什么？</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>我说：</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:
"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>不干什么，就是觉得奇怪，我从来没看到过男厕所是什么样子的。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>妈妈摇摇头说：</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>陈淼淼，你是一个下流坯。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>我忍不住笑，学校里什么地方我都去过了，就是没去过男厕所，我真想知道里面是什么样。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>妈妈说：</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:
"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>一长条像水沟样的，白色的瓷砖，矮矮的木头门。</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>和女孩子的差不多。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>妈妈严肃地说：</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>男孩子要站着尿尿这样的事，是不可以叫以告诉你的，女孩子一知道这种男孩子的事，马上就会变成大人，就再也不会长高了，我可不想你是个那么矮小的人。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'>”</span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>说着，妈妈哗地眨了一下眼，脸上的花就又变成了眼睛。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>妈妈真的神了！和皮诺曹的仙女，阿拉丁的神灯一样。而更好的是，他们拥有的是宝物，坏人要抢，宝物是没有感情的。到了谁的手里，就为谁服务，而我有的是自己的妈妈，要是她真的是不吃我的怪物，她会永远向着我，不会被抢走。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>妈妈看着我，脸上全是笑。她的笑容像一块抹布一样，一把一把，把妈妈的脸擦得闪闪发光。这时候，我才发现妈妈的脸原来是有一点伤心的样子，她的脸像好久都没有擦干净的玻璃一样，有一点灰灰的不爽气。这在从前是看不出来的，只有现在，妈的脸明亮得在闪光，才能发现从前不是这样的。就像是那种灰灰的玻璃，它也是透明的，可当你把它擦得发光了，才会发现原来看上去透明的玻璃，其实也是脏的。</span>
        </p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>妈高兴的脸，是多么好看啊。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>那你还会偷着做什么和人不一样的事呢？人家小鬼盖思波不光会变东西，还会飞。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'>”</span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>我说。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>妈冲我眨眨眼睛，就冉冉地升了起来。她的脚浮到桌面上来了，又浮到大吊灯那么高了，我这才意识到她是开始飞起来了，一动不动就能飞起来，而不是像小鸟那样，得使劲拍翅膀。妈妈升到了天花板那里，微微笑地看着我。然后在空中翻了一个跟斗，平平的，像敦煌仙女一样静静地浮在我的头顶上。</span>
        </p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>我大叫一声：</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>爸爸！</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>妈对我</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:
"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>嘘</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:
"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>”</span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>了一声，制止了我。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>她像小鸟喝水一样从空中凑近爸爸，很近地看着爸爸睡得死死的脸，对他的脸做了一个大大的鬼脸。那是在爸爸醒着的时候绝不可能发生的事，可现在爸爸只是一脸诚恳地对着妈妈的鬼脸深深地呼吸着。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>我笑出来。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>妈妈先很深情地对着爸爸的脸亲了又亲。再装爸爸的样子闭着眼睛很陶醉很害羞的样子。爸爸醒着的时候，就是妈妈，也从来不敢这么放肆。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>我笑死了。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>爸爸动了一下，妈吓得一抽，像烟一样升到上面去。</span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'> </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>她用手指指吊灯，说：</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>又有那么多的灰，我的天，今天要擦灯了。</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>我赶紧说：</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:
"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>别。一点也不浪漫了。</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>听到我说这个，妈妈的脸笑开了花，可是她还是忍看笑，对我吐了吐舌头：</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>陈淼淼，你可真是个懒虫，将来不知道你自己的家会有多脏。</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>妈满房子飞着，像真正的飞机一样，还会俯冲和上升。可是她嘴里不停地说窗帘箱里有蜘蛛网了，要打扫了；又说画镜线里装满了灰什么的，太像一个烦人的妈妈。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>于是我说：</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:
"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>妈，你能带着我飞，才叫本事呢。</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>妈这才停下嘴来，她看了看我，飞过来抓着我的手，她的手指现在是温暖的，太好了。她把我抱在她的怀里。她的身体像最软的鸭绒被一样包围着我，她的身上有的不再是昨天的那种冰箱里的腥气味，而是一种从前的那种切开的黄瓜气味，虽然是凉凉的，可是不冰，</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>而且很清香。我心驻一下子高兴起来。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>渐渐，我发现自己的小床变得小了，而且窄了，我看见睡在床边上的爸爸像一个大虾。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>然后，我惊奇地发现自己居然能看得见大橱顶上的东西，大橱顶上有一些灰白色的灰尘，还有妈妈画坏了、却舍不得扔掉的画。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>接着我看到大吊灯那些向上张开的白玻璃灯罩里真的全是灰，最后我的头被什么东西顶住了，硬硬的，再一看，那是我家的禾花板啊，我这不是在飞吗？！</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>我是在飞。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>妈妈带着我穿过走廊，我摸着天花板一路向前，我们像两只乌离开了鸟窝一样，离开了爸爸和我的小房间，飞过客厅，飞过客厅的桌子，那里还有昨天闯了大祸的那瓶绍兴黄酒。昨天我还吓得要命，我多傻呀！</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>我们在爸爸妈妈的房间里飞来飞去，我和妈加在一块，是很大的一块东西。一不小心，就碰到大吊灯。它就吱嘎吱嘎地摇晃起来，妈马上惊叫：</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'>“</span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>别把它碰掉了！</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>我可不管。我喜欢看大吊灯被我碰的摇摇晃晃的，然后灯绳上的灰，像吃馄饨时候爸老要撒的黑胡楸面一样撒下去，一直洒到妈妈的大床上。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>妈在我身后心疼地大叫：</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>你这孩子怎么是这样的啊！</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>我能像小鸟一样的飞吗？</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>像鸟一样飞在我们这条南京西路上，</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>哗</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>地飞到东，叉</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>哗</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>地飞到北，看看美发厅的霓虹灯上脏不脏。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>从气窗里看下去，帮着到我们大楼下面南京西路和陕西路交界的地方，那个吹哨子的年轻警察正笔直地站在路中间的圆台子上指挥交通，他看到一个会飞的女孩子会怎么想？前几天我飞跑过马路的时候，他还对我们大叫：</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'>“</span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>小人不要命啦！</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>然后过来一把抓住我的书包带子，像拉羊一样把我拉过马路去，所有的汽车全在他的哨子声里停下来，看我示众。现在如何，</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'>“</span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>小人</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'>”</span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>在他的头顶上飞！</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>我说：</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:
"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>我要飞到外面去。</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>妈妈说：</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:
"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>不行，不可以。人家要看到的。</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>我说：</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:
"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>妈妈！</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:
"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>妈说：</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:
"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>真的不行，在人的世界里，就得像人一样生活，不能让人知道我们是不同的，这是我们到这里来以前宣过誓的，要不就不能来。</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>说着，妈轻轻地把我放下来，我又回到了地面上，原来会飞的人，也是有规矩约束着的，所有的世界上，投有什么人是真正能想做什么就做什么。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>妈也下来了，咚地一声坐到地上，看着我，很遗憾的样子。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>我看着妈妈，她是奇妙的，是我的，虽然她不能做所有我想要的事，可已经很了不起了。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>妈妈望着我说：</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'> “</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>我也爱你，陈淼淼。你救了我。我一想到你，心里就开始冒胶水出来，那是世界上最结实的胶水。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>什么？</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>妈说：</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:
"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>你要知道！这种从心里流出来的胶水是人的世界里最好的东西，透明的，黏糊的，让你的心越来越结实的。你们这个世界的人把它叫做感情。这是我们的世界没有的东西。你给我那么多，还有你的爸爸。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>妈妈那个空间里的人，因为从来不会生气，也不会高兴，不会吵架，也不会爱。因为他们没有感情，所以他们不用说话，也没有语言，他们整天就在天上飞来飞去，他们的风全是流动的音乐。不过对他们来说，等于是风，没有什么好喜欢的，因为他们的心里没有爱，也没有恨，他们的心是用最轻水晶做的，什么也没有。</span>
        </p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>他们那里的人，都是为了找到一种感情来到我们这个空间的。他们党得我们人间的感情，是胶水，把一个个人，都紧紧地黏合在了一起。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>妈妈也是为了要把自己和我们黏在一起，来到我们这里的。妈妈说：</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>所以，我们坐班车到人间来，要来这里的人很多，我等了好多天，来了以后，我们大家都躲在没人的红砖老教堂里，那里很安静，虽然不是为我们准备的，可也合我们的胃口。教堂里的小天使也是我这样的人，我们总是要在那里适应人间的强烈的热气，大多数人都变瘦了。</span>
        </p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>我们在黄昏时候出来，太阳下去了，我们就飞到</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>外面的大树上玩，在没有人爱上我们、或者恨上我们以前，我们怕晒太阳。不过，许多时侯，人总是先爱上我们，再恨我们，恨比爱要复杂一点。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>黄昏的时候，我们大家拉着树叶子荡秋千，唱歌。树下的人听不见我们唱歌，也看不见我们。只以为是树</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>叶子在风里响。那就是和我们没有缘分的人。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>要是有人抬起头来找，或者停下脚步听，那些人要么是诗人，要么是想要爱上什么人的那种心里寂寞的人。这样的人在里面能听到隐隐约约的歌声，不过这种人是对自己的感觉最怀疑的人，他们其实是感觉最好的人，可是他们永远也不敢像最蠢的那种人一样，一张嘴就能肯定自己感觉不错。所以他们犹豫着，看来看去。</span>
        </p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>而我们，就在树上看他们那若有所思的人间的脸，评论他们里面谁是好看的人。这是爱上一个人的前提。我们常常就爱上了那几张迷惑地望着树叶子的脸，因为迷惑就是一种感情，它们会像箭一样向我们的心扎过来，</span>
        </p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>然后，我的心就会有一些黏黏的东西流出来，把感情一点一点地黏住。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>我就是这样爱上了爸爸。那时爸爸还是一个大学生，每个星期六大学放学的时候站在大树下面等车回家去。他上的是第一医学院，可却学着写许多现代主义的诗歌。爸爸那向上望过来的眼睛，是世界上最黏的东西。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>妈妈说着，脸轻轻地红了，那种红色，一点点地盖住她的脸，她的眼皮，她的额头，就像昨天蓝色盖住了她一样。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>这是我第一次听到爸爸妈妈是怎么好起来的，我觉得他们真好，我做他们的孩子，真的是很幸福。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>妈妈的心重了，就从大树上落了下来，变成了一个人间的女人，她在大树下面的车站上认识了爸爸，然后就恋爱了，就结婚了，就生我了。妈妈的心就更加黏了，因为还有我，我有时觉得自己比总是很严肃的爸爸更爱妈妈，我常常要紧紧地抱着妈妈才行。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>妈妈的这些话，让我想起安徒生的人鱼公主，在故事里，她也很想当一个人。妈妈说她从前漂到大海深处去的时候，看到过人鱼公主，她现在也没有朋友，因为她最后还是没能得到一个人的感情，没有人爱上她。人鱼公主现在生活得不那么快乐，比起来，妈比她要快乐多了。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>那棵树在哪里？</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>我问。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>在</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>49</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>路终点站，教堂的前面。以后我带你去看看，那是你的爸爸妈妈相爱的墓碑。</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'>”</span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>妈妈微笑着说。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>不要瞎三话四。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>我学着爸爸的样子说。妈妈实在是不会说我们的话。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>这时，我听到身后有声音，是爸爸站在门口，他严肃地看着我们。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>妈妈看着他，脸上的笑一下子就没有了。</span></p>

        <p class=MsoNormal><span lang=EN-US>&nbsp;</span></p>

        <span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.5pt;font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif'><br clear=all
                style='page-break-before:always'>
        </span>

        <p class=MsoNormal><span lang=EN-US>&nbsp;</span></p>

        <h1><span style='font-family:宋体'>疯丫头杜真子</span></h1>

        <p class=MsoNormal><span lang=EN-US><img border=0 width=395 height=554 id="图片 8" src="书籍素材.files/image007.jpg"
                    alt="http://www.kfzimg.com/G06/M00/35/77/p4YBAFqbQtKAGBEWAAEAdUfQESw327_b.jpg"></span></p>

        <h2 align=center style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:7.5pt;
margin-left:0cm;text-align:center'><span style='font-size:21.0pt;line-height:
173%;font-family:"微软雅黑",sans-serif;color:#7B59C0'>疯丫头来了</span></h2>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>一遇到马天笑先生对马小跳笑得不是那么自然，还</span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'> </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>带着讨好的意思，而马小跳的宝贝儿妈妈又做出格外温柔的样子，不停地问他吃不吃这样，吃不吃那样，马小跳就知道，他们肯定有不好讲的话要对他讲，而这些话，马小跳听了可能会跳起来。</span>
        </p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>马小跳，有一件事情</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>……</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>唉，还</span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'> </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>是宝贝儿妈妈讲吧！</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>马天笑先生一直叫马小跳的妈妈</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>宝贝儿</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>，所以马小跳也一直叫妈妈为</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>宝贝儿妈妈</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>是这样的，马小跳。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>宝贝儿妈妈挨着马小跳坐下来，手就在他的脊背上摸来摸去，像对付不好对付的猫一样，希望这样能把马小跳安抚下来，</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'>“</span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>你姨妈要去美国住半年，杜真子要来我们家住半年。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>我坚决不同意！</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>马小跳果然跳了起来。杜真子是他姨妈的女儿，是他的表妹，比他小三个月。杜真子的爸爸在美国做访问学者，开始说访问一年，到现在已经访问了三年，还</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'> </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>不回来，说要把一个尖端课题研究完了再回来。结果，姨妈隔三差五地往美国跑，把杜真子一会儿寄放在她奶奶家，一会儿寄放在她外婆</span>
        </p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>家。她的外婆，也是马小跳的外婆。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>她为什么不去她奶奶家，不去外婆家？</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>宝贝儿妈妈说：</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>她奶奶、外婆都管不了她。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>马外跳，你是杜真子的表哥，也许你能管住她。</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>马天笑先生的这句话，马小跳爱听，但是他确实不喜欢杜真子。在这个世界上，马小跳最讨厌两个女孩子：一个是他的同桌路曼曼；一个就是他的表妹杜真子。如果杜真子是夏林果那种类型的女孩子，别说在他家住半年，就是住一年、三年、八年，就是一辈子住在他家，马小跳也热烈欢迎。</span>
        </p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>杜真子有一样东西，可以动摇马小跳那颗坚定的心。杜真子有一只心爱的猫，这猫很怪，它会笑。她走到哪儿，就把猫带到哪儿。她的奶奶、外婆都不喜欢这只猫，说它是猫精、猫怪。马小跳却对这只猫特别感兴趣，他怎么也想不通：这只猫为什么会笑？</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>杜真子会带那只猫来吗？</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>猫？</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>马天笑先生也知道那只猫，</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>那只会笑的猫？</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>马小跳松口了：</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>如果杜真子把那只猫带来，我还</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'> </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>可以考虑考虑。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>她肯定会带来的。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>宝贝儿妈妈说，</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>杜真子跟猫，比跟她妈妈还</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'> </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>亲。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>第二天，杜真子就来了，风风火火地来了。她一手抱着那只会笑的猫，一手拖着一个大轮箱，一进门便大呼小叫。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>最最亲爱的姨妈！最最亲爱的姨父！</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>可一看见马小跳，眼睛一闭，嘴巴一撇：</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>讨厌！</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>马小跳有一些时候没见到杜真子了，今天一见她，突然发现，杜真子原来一张圆圆的脸，现在怎么变成了一眯短短的猫脸？还</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'> </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>有，她原来的眼睛也没有现在这么大呀，还</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'> </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>闪着绿光。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>杜真子，你越长越像猫了！</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>杜真子一点都不生马小跳的气，她说爱跟谁在一起，就会跟谁长得一样。她爱跟猫在一起，自然会越长越像猫。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>你会不会像猫那样长出一条尾巴来？</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>马小跳，你想气死我吗？</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>杜真子尖叫着朝马小跳扑去，马小跳躲闪开，杜真子一头栽在沙发上。如果是别的女孩，早就哭鼻子了，或者去向大人告状了。杜真子可不，她像什么事都没发生一样，一本正经地问马小跳：</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'>“</span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>我住哪儿？</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'>”</span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>马小跳说：</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'>“</span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>沙发。</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>杜真子可不买马小跳的账，她拖起轮箱就往马小跳的房间里走。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>干什么？干什么？</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>马小跳追了过去，</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>那是我们男生的房间，女生不能进去！</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>从今天起，本小姐住这个房间了。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>杜真子把她的轮箱横在门口，</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>女生房间，男生免进！</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>砰的一声，杜真子关上了房门。</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>宝贝儿妈妈，杜真子把我的房间占了！</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>马小跳，你是男孩子，杜真子是女孩子，要有点绅士风度嘛！</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'>”</span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>马天笑先生拍拍马小跳的肩膀，</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'>“</span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>你做表哥的，就把房间让给表妹住吧！</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>如果不把房间让给杜真子，就没有绅士风度。马小跳怕落个</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>没有绅士风度</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>的恶名，只好把房间让给杜真子住。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>我睡哪儿呢？～沙发。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>马小跳顿时觉得他在这个家里的地位，一落千丈。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>宝贝儿妈妈赶紧说：</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>如果你不愿睡沙发，睡在书房里也行。</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>马天笑先生却说：</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>如果你在灯光的照射下也睡得着的话，你就在书房里睡吧！</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>马天笑先坐白天在玩具厂当厂长，晚上在书房里搞设计，经常搞到半夜。书房里亮着灯，怎么睡得着？马小跳说：</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'>“</span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>我还</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'> </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>是睡客厅的沙发吧！</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>嘭！嘭！嘭！</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>有三大包东西从马小跳的房间里被扔出来，一包是马小跳的衣服，一包是马小跳的书，一包是马小跳的玩具。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>杜真子，你把门打开！</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>马小跳使劲地拍着门。拍不开，又推。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>门一下子开了，马小跳扑进房间里。</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>出去！</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“‘</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>这是我的房间！</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>…‘</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>现在是我的！</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>啪的一声，杜真子把二张写着大字的纸，贴在了门上：</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>女生寝室</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>男生免进</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>有这样的表妹，马小跳只好自认倒霉。他安慰自己</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>好男不与女斗</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>，从他的房间里退了出来。</span></p>

        <h2 align=center style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:7.5pt;
margin-left:0cm;text-align:center'><span style='font-size:21.0pt;line-height:
173%;font-family:"微软雅黑",sans-serif;color:#7B59C0'>好男不与女斗</span></h2>

        <p class=MsoNormal align=left style='text-align:left'><span style='font-size:
11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#333333'>好男不与女斗</span></p>

        <p class=MsoNormal align=left style='margin-bottom:11.25pt;text-align:left;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:宋体;color:#333333'>自从杜真子住进马小跳的房间，马小跳就再也没有进过他自己的房间。只要马小跳想走进他的房间，杜真子就会指着门上贴的那张纸，问马小跳：</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'>“</span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#333333'>你不识字呀？</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'>”</span></p>

        <p class=MsoNormal align=left style='margin-bottom:11.25pt;text-align:left;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:宋体;color:#333333'>马小跳当然识字，那纸上写的是：</span></p>

        <p class=MsoNormal align=left style='margin-bottom:11.25pt;text-align:left;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:宋体;color:#333333'>女生寝室</span></p>

        <p class=MsoNormal align=left style='margin-bottom:11.25pt;text-align:left;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:宋体;color:#333333'>男生免进</span></p>

        <p class=MsoNormal align=left style='margin-bottom:11.25pt;text-align:left;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:宋体;color:#333333'>有个女孩子在家里，马小跳的生活变得别扭起来。马小跳习惯睡觉的时候，只穿条小裤衩。有一天晚上，马小跳只穿一条小裤衩，抱着衣服从卫生间里出来，正遇上去卫生间的杜真子。</span>
        </p>

        <p class=MsoNormal align=left style='margin-bottom:11.25pt;text-align:left;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#333333'>啊</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>——”</span></p>

        <p class=MsoNormal align=left style='margin-bottom:11.25pt;text-align:left;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:宋体;color:#333333'>杜真子发出一声尖叫，双手捂住眼睛。</span></p>

        <p class=MsoNormal align=left style='margin-bottom:11.25pt;text-align:left;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:宋体;color:#333333'>马天笑先生从书房里冲出来，宝贝儿妈妈也从卧室里冲出来，他们以为发生了什么事。</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'>“</span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#333333'>杜真子．你的眼睛怎么啦？</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'>”</span></p>

        <p class=MsoNormal align=left style='margin-bottom:11.25pt;text-align:left;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:宋体;color:#333333'>杜真子的手还</span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'> </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#333333'>捂着眼睛：</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'>“</span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#333333'>我看了不该看的东西，眼睛会烂掉的。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'>”</span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#333333'>马天笑先生问：</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'>“</span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#333333'>你看了什么不该看的东西？</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'>”“</span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;
color:#333333'>马小跳的裸体。</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#333333'>马小跳奋起自辩：</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'>“</span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#333333'>我穿了内裤。</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'>”</span></p>

        <p class=MsoNormal align=left style='margin-bottom:11.25pt;text-align:left;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:宋体;color:#333333'>杜真子还</span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'> </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#333333'>是不肯把手从眼睛上放下来：</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'>“</span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#333333'>你为什么不穿睡衣？</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'>”</span></p>

        <p class=MsoNormal align=left style='margin-bottom:11.25pt;text-align:left;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#333333'>我从来不穿睡衣。</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'>”“</span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;
color:#333333'>我在这里，你必须穿睡衣。</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>”</span></p>

        <p class=MsoNormal align=left style='margin-bottom:11.25pt;text-align:left;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#333333'>我就不</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'>……”‘</span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;
color:#333333'>马小跳，要有绅士风度。</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#333333'>宝贝儿妈妈又护着杜真子，</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'>“</span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#333333'>你就穿上睡衣吧！</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'>”</span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#333333'>马小跳还</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'> </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#333333'>是不肯就范。</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'>“</span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#333333'>喵</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'>——”</span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;
color:#333333'>杜真子带来的那只猫叫了一声，它的两只眼睛闪着绿光，一直在对马小跳冷笑。</span></p>

        <p class=MsoNormal align=left style='margin-bottom:11.25pt;text-align:left;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:宋体;color:#333333'>马小跳倒吸一口冷气，全身的汗毛都竖了起来。他知道这只猫会笑，但不知道这只猫还</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'> </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#333333'>会冷笑。</span></p>

        <p class=MsoNormal align=left style='margin-bottom:11.25pt;text-align:left;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:宋体;color:#333333'>尽管马小跳热爱一切有生命的小动物，包括这只会笑的猫，但这只会笑的猫一直对他充满了敌意，因为他老和杜真子吵来吵去，会笑的猫当然会站在它主人杜真子那一边。</span></p>

        <p class=MsoNormal align=left style='margin-bottom:11.25pt;text-align:left;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:宋体;color:#333333'>马小跳不是怕杜真子，他是因为怕这只猫，才心不甘、情不愿地穿上睡衣、睡裤。当然，是一边穿，嘴里一边嘀咕：</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'>“</span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#333333'>好男不与女斗。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'>”</span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#333333'>天快亮的时候，是马小跳睡得最香的时候。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'>“</span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#333333'>啊</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'>——</span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;
color:#333333'>。杜真子又在卫生问里尖叫起来。</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#333333'>又怎么啦？</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'>”</span></p>

        <p class=MsoNormal align=left style='margin-bottom:11.25pt;text-align:left;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:宋体;color:#333333'>马天笑先生打着哈欠从卧室里出来。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#333333'>马小跳解了小便，不冲马桶！</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'>”</span></p>

        <p class=MsoNormal align=left style='margin-bottom:11.25pt;text-align:left;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:宋体;color:#333333'>杜真子一手捏着自己的鼻子，一手去揪马小跳的耳朵，把他从热被窝里揪起来。</span></p>

        <p class=MsoNormal align=left style='margin-bottom:11.25pt;text-align:left;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#333333'>去，去把马桶冲干净！</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'>”</span></p>

        <p class=MsoNormal align=left style='margin-bottom:11.25pt;text-align:left;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:宋体;color:#333333'>马小跳睁不开眼睛，他还</span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'> </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#333333'>没睡醒。马天笑先生说：</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'>“</span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#333333'>我去冲，我帮他冲！。</span></p>

        <p class=MsoNormal align=left style='margin-bottom:11.25pt;text-align:left;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#333333'>不行！</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'>”</span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#333333'>杜真子态度坚决，</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'>“</span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#333333'>我最讨厌解小便不冲马桶的人，我一定要马小跳亲自去冲。</span>
        </p>

        <p class=MsoNormal align=left style='margin-bottom:11.25pt;text-align:left;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:宋体;color:#333333'>马小跳在睡梦中，他根本不知道杜真子在说些什么。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#333333'>马小跳，你起来！。</span></p>

        <p class=MsoNormal align=left style='margin-bottom:11.25pt;text-align:left;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:宋体;color:#333333'>马小跳睡得太死，杜真子揪他的耳朵，他都不觉得痛。可是，尽管他是闭着眼睛的，他也能感到有一双眼睛正瞪着他。</span></p>

        <p class=MsoNormal align=left style='margin-bottom:11.25pt;text-align:left;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:宋体;color:#333333'>马小跳睁开眼睛，那只会笑的猫就蹲在他的枕边，两只绿光闪闪的眼睛正瞪着他。。你</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'>……</span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;
color:#333333'>，马小跳拉上被子，蒙上他的眼睛。</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#333333'>喵</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>——”</span></p>

        <p class=MsoNormal align=left style='margin-bottom:11.25pt;text-align:left;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:宋体;color:#333333'>会笑的猫伸出爪子，拉下被子。马小跳又看见会笑的猫在冷笑。</span></p>

        <p class=MsoNormal align=left style='margin-bottom:11.25pt;text-align:left;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:宋体;color:#333333'>马小跳全身的鸡皮疙瘩在紧急集合。他从沙发上滚下来，然后跑进卫生间里。哗！哗！哗！</span></p>

        <p class=MsoNormal align=left style='margin-bottom:11.25pt;text-align:left;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:宋体;color:#333333'>马小跳把马桶冲干净，回到被窝里，却再也睡不着了。一闭上眼睛，就觉得杜真子带来的那只猫，在向他冷笑。马小跳毛骨悚然，不敢再睡。听到宝贝儿妈妈已经在厨房里做早餐，便悄悄来到厨房里。</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'>“</span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#333333'>宝贝儿妈妈，杜真子什么时候走？</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'>”</span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#333333'>。才刚来一天，怎么就想人家走？</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'>”</span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#333333'>马小跳大放悲声：。我快活不下去了。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'>”</span></p>

        <p class=MsoNormal align=left style='margin-bottom:11.25pt;text-align:left;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#333333'>怎么会呢？</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'>”</span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#333333'>宝贝儿妈妈根本不把马小跳当回事儿，</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'>“</span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#333333'>杜真子就住半年，半年的时间很快就过去了。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'>”</span></p>

        <p class=MsoNormal align=left style='margin-bottom:11.25pt;text-align:left;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:宋体;color:#333333'>才来一天，马小跳就有度日如年的感觉。半年是多少天？至少有一百八十天，这日子怎么过呀？</span></p>

        <p class=MsoNormal align=left style='margin-bottom:11.25pt;text-align:left;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:宋体;color:#333333'>马小跳在台历上，把过去的一天画了个红圈。马小跳的心情好了一点，他想，画完一百八十个红圈圈，他就不会再有度日如年的惑觉了。</span></p>

        <p class=MsoNormal align=left style='margin-bottom:11.25pt;text-align:left;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:宋体;color:#333333'>早餐的时候，马小跳习惯喝半杯牛奶，吃一个鸡蛋，再吃两片面包夹花生酱，再吃一根香蕉或一个苹果。</span></p>

        <p class=MsoNormal align=left style='margin-bottom:11.25pt;text-align:left;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#333333'>马小跳，你怎么可以才喝这么一点点牛奶？</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#333333'>杜真子的眼睛睁得又圆又大，在她短短的猫脸上，几乎占了一半的面积。</span></p>

        <p class=MsoNormal align=left style='margin-bottom:11.25pt;text-align:left;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:宋体;color:#333333'>马小跳朝杜真子翻翻白眼：</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#333333'>我喝多少牛奶，你也管？</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'>”</span></p>

        <p class=MsoNormal align=left style='margin-bottom:11.25pt;text-align:left;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#333333'>我怎么能不管？</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'>”</span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#333333'>杜真子说，</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#333333'>你知道人家美国男孩子为什么长得那么高大，那么漂亮？人家每天都咕咚咕咚地喝牛奶，要喝几大杯呢！</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'>”</span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#333333'>杜真子也跟她妈妈去过美国，她最爱拿美国的男孩子跟马小跳比。</span>
        </p>

        <p class=MsoNormal align=left style='margin-bottom:11.25pt;text-align:left;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#333333'>人家美国男孩子喝牛奶喝成小牛，跟我也没关系。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'>”</span></p>

        <p class=MsoNormal align=left style='margin-bottom:11.25pt;text-align:left;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#333333'>怎么没关系？</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'>”</span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#333333'>杜真子大呼小叫，</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'>“</span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#333333'>你是我表哥，你长成这个样子，不是丢我的脸吗？</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'>”</span></p>

        <p class=MsoNormal align=left style='margin-bottom:11.25pt;text-align:left;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:宋体;color:#333333'>马小跳气得要死，宝贝儿妈妈和马天笑先生却开怀大笑。杜真子不由分说，给马小跳倒满一大杯牛奶：</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'>“</span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#333333'>喝！喝完它！</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'>”</span></p>

        <p class=MsoNormal align=left style='margin-bottom:11.25pt;text-align:left;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:宋体;color:#333333'>马小跳哪里肯喝？正准备反抗，那只会笑的猫跳上桌来，马小跳又看见它在冷笑。</span></p>

        <p class=MsoNormal align=left style='margin-bottom:11.25pt;text-align:left;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:宋体;color:#333333'>马小跳在心里说</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#333333'>好男不与女斗</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'>”</span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#333333'>，端起那杯牛奶，咕咚咕咚</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'>……</span></p>

        <h2 align=center style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:7.5pt;
margin-left:0cm;text-align:center'><span style='font-size:21.0pt;line-height:
173%;font-family:"微软雅黑",sans-serif;color:#7B59C0'>那只会笑的猫</span></h2>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>马小跳被他的表妹杜真子逼着，不，应该说是被那只会冷笑的猫逼着，咕咚咕咚，喝下了一大杯牛奶。他从来没有喝过这么多的牛奶，整个上午，他的肚子都咕咕地乱响，坐在他前面的毛超都听见了。</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'>“</span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>马小跳，你是不是要拉稀？</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>马小跳恶狠狠地说：</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>都是被那个杜真子害的！</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>杜真子是不是你的表妹？</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>毛超还</span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'> </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>记得马小跳给他们讲过杜真子，</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>就那个疯丫头？</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>”“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>烦都烦死了。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>马小跳说，</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>她现在住到我们家来了。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>烦什么呀？你不知道，家里只有一个孩子一点都不好玩。</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'>”</span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>毛超凑近马小跳，</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'>“</span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>马小跳，她长得怎么样？</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'>”“</span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>不怎么样。</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>不跟夏林果比，跟路曼曼比，怎么样？</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>夏林果是班上最漂亮的女生，路曼曼没有夏林果漂亮，但看着还</span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'> </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>顺眼，只有马小跳看她不顺眼，因为她老管马小跳，跟杜真子一样。</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'>“</span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>差不多。</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'>”</span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>马小跳没好气地说，</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'>“</span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>她长着一张猫脸、一双猫眼，长得跟她带来的那只猫一模一样。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>跟猫长得一模一样，一定很好玩吧？</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>马小跳一想起杜真子折磨他的种种事情，心里就不舒服。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>杜真子一点都不好玩，可她带来的那只猫很好玩，会笑。</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'>”“</span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>猫会笑？我不相信。</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'>”</span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>毛超问坐在马小跳后面的唐飞，</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'>“</span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>唐飞，你相信不相信猫会笑？</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>谁的猫舍笑？</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>唐飞对这些事情最感兴趣。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>杜真子带来的猫不但会笑，还</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'> </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>会冷笑，还</span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'> </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>会大笑，还</span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'> </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>会</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>……”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>马小跳，你在编故事吧？</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>唐飞，我不骗你。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>马小跳就怕别人不相信他说的话，</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>那只猫对我总是冷笑，对杜真子总是大笑。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>唐飞恨不得马上就能见到那只猫。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>马小跳，今天下午放学，我们去你家。</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>去我家干什么？</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>．</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>唐飞说：</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:
"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>去看那只会冷笑、会大笑的猫。</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>毛超说：</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:
"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>还</span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'> </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>有你那个长得像猫的表妹。</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>马小跳、毛超、唐飞和张达这四个男生，是四个形影不离的好朋友。唐飞和毛超都要到马小跳家去，张达也得去。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>张达不喜欢猫，因为他怕猫。在他小时候，猫曾经抓过他。直到现在，他的手背上，还</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'> </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>留着猫抓的三道伤痕。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>猫</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>……</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>猫有什么好看的？</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>唐飞说：</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:
"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>那只猫会笑。</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>毛超说：</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:
"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>马小跳还</span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'> </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>有一个表妹，叫杜真子，长得跟猫一模一样。</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>下午放学后，四个人来到马小跳家。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>那只会笑的猫从马小跳的房间</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>——</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>哦，现在是杜真子的房间里跑出来，它以为是杜真子回来了，所以它满脸笑容。但一看是马小跳，还</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'> </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>有三个它不认识的人，它脸上的笑容一下子就消失了，那模样也没什么特别的地方。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>唐飞说：</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:
"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>这猫哪里会笑呀？</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>毛超说：</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:
"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>我看见它刚从房间里跑出来的时候，脸上好像在笑。</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>唐飞大摇大摆地朗猫走去：</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>喂，你对我笑一笑！</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>猫瞪着唐飞，眼睛闪着绿光，唐飞本来已伸出手去想摸摸它的脸，手便在半空中停住了。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>喵</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>——”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>猫的耳朵动了动，嘴咧开了。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>看，它笑了！</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>马小跳说，</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>是冷笑。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>那冷笑的猫，样子十分可怕。四个人身上的汗毛都竖了起来。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>你</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>……</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>你别那样笑啊！</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>唐飞挤出一脸讨好的笑。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>那猫脸上的冷笑不见了，也挤出一脸讨好人的笑。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>这种笑叫什么笑？</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>毛超说：</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:
"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>媚笑。</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:
"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>哈哈哈！</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>四个人一起大笑起来。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>那猫眯起眼睛，咧大嘴巴，它也会大笑。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>这猫不简单，它会模仿人的笑。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>还</span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'> </span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>有什么笑？</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>他们搜肠刮肚，想有关</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>笑</span><span
                lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>的词语。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>苦笑。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>苦笑怎么笑？</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>毛超说：</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:
"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>苦笑就是你心里想着痛苦的事情，脸上却要笑出来。</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>我知道我知道，苦笑是这样笑的。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>马小跳心里想着杜真子折磨他的事情，脸上却要笑出来，大家都说马小跳的苦笑很标准。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>马小跳对着猫苦笑，猫皱皱眉头，咧咧嘴，它也苦笑。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>看，它苦笑了！</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>那只会笑的猫，笑得还</span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'> </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>真苦。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>傻笑！</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>唐飞说，</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>我来傻笑。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>你本来就傻。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>唐飞现在没有心情跟毛超打口水仗，他全部的心思都在这只会笑的猫身上。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>唐飞对着猫傻笑：</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>嘿，嘿嘿</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>……”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>猫歪着头，斜着眼，咧着嘴，它也傻笑。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>那只会笑的猫，笑得还</span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;
color:#333333'> </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>真傻。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>狂笑！</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>”</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>毛超说，</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>我来狂笑</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>——</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>哈！哈！哈！</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>毛超笑得浑身乱颤，那样子像触了电一样。那只猫笑得更狂，笑得全身的毛都竖了起来，背也弓了起来。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>猫好像很喜欢狂笑，笑起来就停不下来。</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span
                style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>这猫的笑神经太发达了。</span><span lang=EN-US
                style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>猫终于笑累了，不再狂笑，但它脸上还</span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'> </span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;color:#333333'>带着一种笑。</span>
        </p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>马小跳问：</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:
"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>你们看，这是什么笑？</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;
font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>”</span></p>

        <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:16.9pt'><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>张达说：</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:
"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>“</span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>皮笑</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:
"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>……</span><span style='font-size:11.5pt;
color:#333333'>肉不笑！</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.5pt;font-family:
"Microsoft Yahei",serif;color:#333333'>”</span></p>

        <p class=MsoNormal><span lang=EN-US>&nbsp;</span></p>

